user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Eddy Ball","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4tbfv2I_k2nFYNmn-uaSY14-u_FtTeF47ZRlcmjqixDGX3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I paid extra money to get pineapple and sausage added to my pizza. No sausage was added at all, and very little pineapple. How much pineapple can $3 buy? A whole lot more than these cheapskates added.

Even worse, the pizza was burnt all I could taste was the burnt cheese and crust. Somehow they also managed to make it soggy.  Definitely don't get anything here, even if you're desperate.

On a positive note, the salad was great, but it's not a salad restaurant, it's a pizza restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0mfNh31aZSuvE7Bet2FoAGsGwyQoNvYg7uvx1&fid=0x0:0x36093c14bf1cc313"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Tatyana Ayrapetova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhKy-98t6ZdKhPzAFPxODP0Ie3Uo94lXS45JQrA-ha8UeYbax-0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The cafe smells like toilet, furniture looks like a cheap gas station cafe. Ordered a small prosciutto pizza that is overpriced(24$), thick american type. Expect to be served by a frustrated person. Overall the place has nothing Italian about it, & too expensive for the quality provided. I don't recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObCpbvO4VRkc9D7jVLM252ZaPzChEktNmiGsWx&fid=0x0:0x36093c14bf1cc313"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Kate Here","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0CTVj7gnWo18oxjAYI_tx-jt-W1b25ekrrXTVKIIIr4cU1inM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All my coworkers go here for sandwiches. The lasanga comes baked fresh in a tray big enough for two normal meals or one heavy workday meal. Both the lasanga and the garlic bread are mouthwatering. 10/10 would take an overtime shift and not pack a lunch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mircea Rye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKESDSTPdoyWHQqgI8IAr4gWDG--9ipHyxsI3Wmo68vhlGZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the prosciutto panini for lunch and it was actually life altering. Tasted almost as good as a drunk cig 11/10 will be returning asap if not sooner","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYlZYc4Vi-MogaUHxy2uMVWPY_chB7ynTjcCjO&fid=0x0:0x36093c14bf1cc313"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Chris Tong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrCvAPoHhLbRr6CTfxCUB2FctcrCbTmjBej7AFnRQSJ3z94nwc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great hidden gem tucked away off just off Broadway & Arbutus. In my interactions with the family that run and own the restaurant when I pick up my orders, you can tell they take pride in their dishes and bring a staple in Kitsilano for residents for many years.

Being pasta lovers, we always order their classic baked spaghetti and lasagna dishes. Not only are they delicious, but their focaccia garlic bread that comes with your meal is amazing. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Django","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXnHSn86529191IMMy1TUzhbVX-epqK3pP7Fr8Oh4u2OBXig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My daughter is super sensitive to cheese and gluten so we tend to have a hard time going out to eat. We came along this spot walking down to the fireworks  and wow let me tell you they really make people feel at home. From the moment we walked in they were so sweet to the kids and dealt with all our allergies perfectly. Washed all the utensils for my daughter‚Äôs allergy. Will be recommending to all my family and friends. Also have super late hours for a shop in kits so another plus to the great food and service","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Tam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5eyhtWlAt7gYeZIPy4U5BaEI_ruwvlE0InpE6KNu_zVITpjY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Amazing pizza! Ingredients are fresh, and the closest thing I can find to Montreal style Pizza in Vancouver. Only giving it three stars because we usually order wings with our pizza and they always suck. They always show up with black stuff stuck all over them. Like the kind of stuff you find at the bottom of your barbeque when you scrape it after cooking. I called the restaurant to let them know, and the girl who answered said it‚Äôs because they roast them extra long. I happen to work in the food and beverage industry and that‚Äôs complete BS. I am also insulted that she thinks her customers are stupid enough to believe that. They need to change the tray in which they are baking their wings more often. Too many burnt bits from previous orders of wings. I would never let food leave my kitchen looking like these wings. I tried to clean off the black stuff with a Scott towel, but my son had black stuff all over his teeth from eating these wings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDStG0lhmWTsCfnDtV9uXSoR65ZEPdJfM1WACy&fid=0x0:0x36093c14bf1cc313"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Erica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZBkN4BxKXFj3jq1FxJL-jojchc6LtKnZbzzms0L15OoGL7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We used to order here often, but they‚Äôve become stingy now. The pizza size is so small, and the add-on options on Uber are ridiculously expensive. The coupons that came with our Uber order were all expired (valid only until 3/30/2024). I would kindly suggest reviewing your pricing, portion sizes, and any materials provided to customers before offering them.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Justin Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqn2vD0E5uq0fG2YxWJjNd1TsCaZwtTBVhm85oaOYUa1rEBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I go here I always get spicy chicken patties and regular chicken patties and they were always so good.

I dont mind removing it off my burger but if this was another person who‚Äôs actually allergic to something, it would be really bad.

Please fix this behaviour and dont be lazy and do your jobs!

On top of that its way too expensive for  burger 15 for a meal is absolutely crazy, its almost a full hour of someone‚Äôs Hourly wage.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjqQCOiucr_qQ6iWH7DiB9bDCPSVPCRnlXF1ZP&fid=0x0:0x622aac2934e320c8"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Merle Langlois","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZnruGVXm60ftapBuESQGQtjZaF1P3OYbvdZyq6WrVWTjNEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to this Wendy's since ancient times. I once saw a cabinet minister here. I ordered a salad once and they gave me a free frosty. Today I ordered chicken strips and it took forever and they offered me a free frosty.

The managers who have been here for a long time are super efficient and professional.

There are some individuals here due to the bus stop though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOKMhcgsMkjPZTPsa5k-F6xTCEpV7KocF1HGZ5&fid=0x0:0x622aac2934e320c8"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Shawn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjDFHDIcbtV_DjbplKljLcAMOcHcimjCyqMXoLTCCbOhYL58Lu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"On the side of what is basically a highway is a Wendy's where the food is barely average and the staff let their machines beep endlessly. Eating area is filthy and the drink fountain area doesn't include straws nor forks.

Video attached doesn't properly show how loud these beeps are, but they can be heard from even outside the restaurant.

What a joke.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPamxa4jruVp1D5_Ba2wgemfJj3gXrmTMO3zb1-&fid=0x0:0x622aac2934e320c8"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I gotta be honest, the burgers are way better than McDonald‚Äôs. I rather come here for jbc‚Äôs instead of McDoubles. Plus the baconator is quite impressive and addicting. Service can be a hit or miss here.

But Wendy‚Äôs coffee doesn‚Äôt stand a chance. There‚Äôs always coffee grinds in the hot coffee. For the ice coffee‚Äôs they have a weird after taste to them‚Ä¶ maybe it‚Äôs the cream or syrup‚Ä¶

Plenty of parking all around. This one has a drive thru. Unfortunately it‚Äôs not a 24 hour drive thru.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4QqmmQyWBy26TMrsRGfG2RsVr7ff5sgBd6v5_&fid=0x0:0x622aac2934e320c8"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Evamae Bennett-Doerksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLC2x82OWI32IGJ-lmd2V8iN8-wx2st1ytsecq0ow1x4Ma2lA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I only the grilled chicken wrap combo but it doesn't look like the photo and thay chep out on the cheese","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9By33M7sb9OlJZ7ynzknoiqgOvy_8K5WuYnsJ&fid=0x0:0x622aac2934e320c8"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Dylan D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs93jszeFFscNEtx5h0QN63fK2LAK9Y2edFkGxRs9jp39yXCE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I usually don't review, but I've been going to this location for about 2 years and just recently, at 11:40pm. The plate was huge and itself alone could feed 2 people full. Would order again!

The yellow one is the Mexixan cornbread, and it was way sweeter than I expected.

Overall, authentic Mexican cuisine! (At least in my humble opinion)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfNW6SKO59Ij_pOfGacMGeXcUjR2kqRSIpE-9G&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Norma Camacho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUwCF6WIbRjm4YhYZG-OMjcfOuU_GxQOzPdcmW8bkyhvbqmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"100% recommended to go to Sal y Limon. We will be back soon. üôåüá™üá®üá®üá¶
Norma & Jason","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXOcp4s9XoODB2iwcUZrf5N5GB20HSNQ1PZqoj&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Susana Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmCd7SeHDyGnxkl5sTM18zT60w1nIWHA2fZEbi6JkwCR5gDkY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Love coming this place for tacos, delicious and fresh ingredients, and good amount of food for the price. It‚Äôs a nice spot to hang out with friends or family, comfortable, friendly and clean environment. Best highlight to it is that they provide a self serve sauce station so you can explore to your tasting whatever salsa to your preference. Waiters and owner always carry a big and welcoming smile that makes the experience even more pleasant. Highly recommended and I usually go get my tacos after work with my bestie","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODXvgV7N02dpch-11SWnhleNni91zzwy0AtrXY&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Max M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjYNXpFmuJ5Mo3urIUy-gBQyfjedCSyECEsd75iy93lKJGKIBb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A pretty good Mexican restaurant. It's not too fancy, but the service is great, and the staff is supportive. The food is excellent, and the restaurant is very clean with fresh decorations.
Definitely recommend a visit! üòä","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNegPz1xd052AhBA5PHGHgdObJQDVW8lZykXQO2&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Jesus Brea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8ayN6Qkpli-JC6uL9EhldNKUFlmHyT7tje8vC-QnIeirc1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been a frequent client for Sal y lim√≥n for years! Their recipes and taste have not changed even tho they have many locations now. Their employees always greet me with a smile and customize my personal preferences for my order. And price is good for a whole meal. We love Sal y limon","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuRvKDF0linwDJJipPGdwB5z0MUqzEe4IMQvI&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Nancy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWA4ejh4lO-tY_eoGTxmCCJv76K8jBUalBI7YiJcE-rigM7HxeT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend for family and friends to visit. We had beef, lamb, pork tongue, and fish tacos. All very tasty and delicious. I personally love the fish and pork tongue the most. We also order the burritos very filling and delicious.

Will for sure go back to try out more dishes. It‚Äôs a first come first serve seating, no need to book. They have lots of non alcoholic drinks to choose from and also Mexican beers. Also have different kinds of chilli sauce if you want extra flavour

Easy free parking at the front. Very reasonable prices and portions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAUrDFpGfZITxrxJ-fp04TU9bSTMVwySvPlHUy&fid=0x0:0x4f2deef2ed5e8d84"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Nikki c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTEI07jnFTAEaLsFO0c2_mPPfnmG0XKKHuolSSFqT8Xlgj-nIi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is great! [{"Name":"Young Joe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUckGyj1ucBAvjUpUCyYvK0Q5cvhsgDAq-EeIl_wzsZVWt0V5L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vera‚Äôs never disappoints when you‚Äôre craving a burger. I really appreciate their consistency in offering solid, good burgers all these years in the neighborhood‚Äîso delicious!

I did cheat on them once by trying a flashy new burger spot nearby, something with ‚Äòhawker‚Äô in the name. It was terrible and overpriced for no reason.

So yesterday, we went back to Vera‚Äôs, and it was such a comfort.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUCIELH3vfAMw9GjyKAH2uO0ygrxV1wJusQJNi&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Andrew Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNZ_pvkQlgvJLQf8OH0R8SwU4mnsFF1lvTcdlboJ-4DK-Pr7bb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vera's Burger Shack offers a delightful dining experience with their mouthwatering burgers that are cooked to perfection. The menu boasts a variety of options to cater to every taste preference, from classic cheeseburgers to gourmet creations. The ingredients are fresh, the portions are generous, and the service is friendly and efficient. The cozy ambiance of the restaurant adds to the overall enjoyment of the meal. Whether you're a burger aficionado or just looking for a satisfying meal, Vera's Burger Shack is a must-visit spot for delicious food in a welcoming environment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0KAy7qMsISIKvUkpjB0TYIwrQpnZuRnqV9z-a&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Phu Phillip Trinh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaIr_hA9ineHMoNk0ZKoAr2M72jghcTVAP-VsiNb3ihO_zsJT3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not sure what the fuss is about, I‚Äôve been here over 3 times and I always see the same chef there cooking and I know he‚Äôs all about the art of the burger.

Every time I dined here I‚Äôve thought, ‚ÄúMan it‚Äôs the best burger I‚Äôve ever had.‚Äù But it continues every visit!

Def an underrated spot","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcdydDEM7AqH73i5ONjIDJh-lCfB1OUXb7uqm_&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2023-11-20"},{"Name":"Tony Sebastian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiWqdXCEwpIVB9StmiemuyGnyCJmr0IdMdtYRQU_cWFPEJXoA8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pretty good burger spot on Main street. Juicy patties. Good options too!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP47VMhMiLWA6nxtijvVYdxy-KtBVSRSBHZUJug&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Sam Elliott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDPY4XjjWmRecrxhC5qvZDr_KHwcqUlKCs6Ko4Mt0dqpXwYzs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here on my way to the VanDusen Festival of Light. I got the BBQ burger. You could tell that the meat was of quality and it tasted great. The fries were home-cut and possibly even better. 4/5. The two staff were friendly, polite, and helpful. The food was on the table in about 15 minutes. Service: 5/5. The place was very clean, including the bathroom. You wouldn‚Äôt expect the bathrooms to be so clean. Ambience 4/5. You really get your money‚Äôs worth. Overall I would give Vera‚Äôs a 8/10. Will go again if in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFyIVNoUNUnOg3gZTUzzIdN5WxYIV3m8NaBcNt&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2023-12-16"},{"Name":"Clay Puppington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtpFCIqrikLxN6Ct6RSok_LLWr_hUIJbRZm7oO4sT6L1fXyFk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôve been going here for about two or three ish years, simply because the cooks behind the counter have made this a memorable place you can‚Äôt miss on Main for delicious burgers!
Every time I go they do not disappoint, other than I wish they added more salt to their fries no complaints. The atmosphere is nice and open, very inviting. Would go again and have every month","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZk7nGvnW5sTdojCa85d3pn1IlGja8q6LlUbU&fid=0x0:0x32cd7af8fb8d278e"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"aftab ladhar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVV7-hiYe9eI73rY0N5a28qtNgjwDgJmunjFACRTxBof8KqdqX_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a burger! [{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic restaurant with fresh, juicy burgers and crispy, delicious fries. My husband visited the restaurant for the first time with a friend and came home raving about the food. The next day, we came together and loved it.

We both ordered an Ultimate Burger & Dip. With each Ultimate Burger, you can add bacon or a sunny side egg. We both chose bacon. You're also served a large portion of fries and your choice of a dip. The dip is huge! Picture a Dixie cup full of may. We tried Jamaican Heat Mayo and Garlic Mayo. Jamaican Heat Mayo wasn't very flavourful, but Garlic Mayo was delicious.

We also ordered the Deep Fried Pickles and dip. For this dip, we tried Scallion Green Mayo. This was our favorite dip. The Deep Fried Pickes were solid. Tasty, crisp and heated all the way through. The sour pickles were a welcome level of flavour complexity.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVNQk4Lz10JGkW555W5aiqy20odH5wbzZbaHdw&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Jeff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQZz_649NB_JyYe86JWDuPg37viSZRSwMS0pmnjIWCdiNwgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place for delicious comfort food.   Visiting from  Chicago and don't have local poutine places.  Fries were fresh, gravy was rich and flavorful and the cheese curds were squeaky good!.  Order at the counter and they give you a beeper to pick your food up at counter when it's ready.  Nothing fancy, but a good lunch or snack!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlFxwVdx2YOPFrDwuvV4Zpr5CdfFsDYGIJsEQD&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2022-5-20"},{"Name":"KS B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKqq0ZtAALrLMssgmfCwo9aWLa4qTSgRyC34h7DL55r3d75RjV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"What was I thinking... had a burger in a fries joint.
Was particularly unimpressed with my burger. Plain. Ordinary, slightly well done burger...
I‚Äôve had the poutine here many times, there. Is an extensive menu, add ons and a decent enough atmosphere.
Will I go back... yes . But not for a burger.

So I went back. It close to my residence and
Needed some hang over food and what better than a great Canadian treat poutine !!!!

Loved it!!! Just look how good it looks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_7EpHh3KbiVlrK-6nOnY88oPFgqPVPzzHaAiw&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2019-3-27"},{"Name":"Adam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6N4PuUho6CqZtyOpzb8lhtXmrL2q8sMmlmyAJgvEPqvC7TI0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best classic poutine I've had. Served hot and fresh. Adequate portions for the price. Fries were crispy and amply topped with gravy and squeaky cheese curds. Gravy was surprisingly good for a vegetarian gravy. Also ordered hot wings which were juicy but lacking any real heat which was disappointing. Great place for poutine and a beer!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyR-piI9ZGDgNl3WMJA0x8Y8abguU2Cu37lycF&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2022-2-14"},{"Name":"Bruce K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWd0BKk0GS4eNlMzvlugB1neEK2VNPshjAFBKounZE39buNi6tqgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I asked the Internet for the best poutine in Vancouver and it brought me here. After finding some ultra-convenient street parking for the Sprinter van, I was inside and smelling that delicious smell of fried foods. A quick study of the menu - 18 different poutines available plus hot dogs and sandwiches and burgers - I made my choice.

Ten minutes later, I'm digging in to number 14, the "Smoked Beef" which is a Montreal-style smoked beef on top of classic poutine. And for those who don't know, poutine is Canada's gift to the world. French fries topped with cheese curds and gravy.

I was "good" and chose the medium because anything more than that would have been pure gluttony. The toppings? Perfect. The fries? Oddly done with a crisp outside and it seemed like underdone inside. Still, delicious and four stars good.

The poutine went down well with a beer - is there a better combination than fries and beer? - and I was stuffed. Thanks, Belgian Fries!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmHzc7t0cfu9jJdp4iXFcFayVd9Brxmg9XatNd&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2023-12-8"},{"Name":"Denny Hui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuGFgsc9U61TCKDV21ZHXILH-aGrlI-hjZswBeAYg3LhKf97Y3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Belgian Fries for dinner. My sons wanted poutine n burgers.

First time visiting the restaurant. Its big, open and clean. No AC but windows and doors open so it wasn't too bad. Staff was very friendly and helpful!

Self order and pick up, including cleaning up after yourselves.  Keep that it mind!

We ordered couple Works Burger  they come with a huge helping of fries. No option to substitute like salad. Burger was juicy, not salty and very flavourful.  Big enough for 2.

Ordered Divine Poutine, large size. Enough to feed 3 or 4! The Devine Poutine sauces were very flavourful but not salty as well. Also ordered the chili dog. That too was a nice size dog that was packed with flavor as well.

Very happy with our meals. We'll definitely be back when we have another craving for poutine n burgers. And after we've worked off all the calories too!

Next visit, we're going to try their deep fried ice cream. See attached picture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJ4BgSry13qkrzMCWEf59KpiMPTi2Gz1reM72_&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2022-8-8"},{"Name":"Doc Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIuKyF7wkNlPzYqNijmgn5Gkom607dWAey_Y6D7nukvJ4ALOg8ZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Just came in for poutine and drinks...counter order service which I'm not a fan of... and the waitress got our order wrong anyway. The requisite television sets surround the room and it seems like the sound is pitched to keep staff awake. One order of routine and two drinks (a beer and a soft drink, clocked in around $30 which seems kinda steep to me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Lancaster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVE38dqjtuRJChAOMVI_7IqNjXFYLRT0xJq7CE5ag7K1zbEHsg-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Well date night came with decent food, it had great sandwiches, but the fries were lukewarm the dipping sauces brought it home. Good local beers on tap, as well as some good domestic ones behind the bar. The staff was friendly and knowledgeable.The deep fried Mars bar was served up warm with some ice cream on the side. Which was amazing, a recommended place for friends night out, or a good first date place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwZEuMXiRen7wa_I2XXItqzVo4Mr_XP99F9lei&fid=0x0:0xf82130bb3c05e747"],"When":"2021-9-6"}]

[{"Name":"Timbo Yuen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHAGMrxbZ5FGQPTt4buk-DBF02oPfWRdAjYIUNtb_J6DcNNUbtrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This Donair is unbelievable but what's keeping them from getting 5 stars is the meat portion. I had the lamb Donair and beef Donair. It's balance and overall flavors are great. Juicy. But then it's too salty for some reason. The lamb didn't need any salt. The beef didn't need any salt. By having zero pickles and salt, I think this would improve overall taste and allow this to be an extremely good Donair product. The price is very good. The saltiness which we experienced was the ones where you make a face expression like too sharp in saltiness. Hope to try it again in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEG2-jIelWsa1MUHG771tq2H-3VJRA8HPvbwGR&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Blane S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQXZCHBWqL70gvvZMn3CLpCRz0hZUzm2TPmU4djMDNTUfZ6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow the food tastes fresh and are delicious!! Owners are friendly too - double thumbs up for the customer service and amazing donair/shawarma!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNSpZazkno_alMNPkJe-_nLdBBPEq_X4WrSXIs&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Joey Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh43jqcwo-gKdZYQAoJ0Z1JoqMz73Gqj18nnQRJ3BI8gvMAlOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little place for some fresh food.
The man behind the counter was friendly and the wrap was prepared in less then 5 mins.

Protein was moist and flavourfull.
Wrap did not fall apart and leak all over my shirt (a win)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4MMTCKGWMkgJUxgDdKSyzeWd20UdTkqKYgDoB&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Danny Ngo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJycDvRl8As2RWTbKjPYq5Ycd7jO6sGzliFXO6t8Xw6eVclYkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was good. A little spicy so request no spicy if you don‚Äôt like or sensitive to spice.
Each platter came with 3 bread. Nice to use it as a pocket to make wraps. Poutine was good as well. Definitely need something to drink to go with the meal.
Beef option seems pretty hard to come by, so call in first to see if they have beef available if that‚Äôs what you want.
Business is bright and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx76XdvCFj3qkjX2FQ8X4pc1XfqegLyXuwarel&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2024-3-4"},{"Name":"Brent Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYSM0_7rmQIvuRgwYvvqbzjo_qKvSImbFN7n8plIZlijT85g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good new Donair place!

I've tried both the chicken shawarma plate (13.99) and the lamb shawarma plate (13.99) and both were stellar.

The chicken is juicy and well seasoned but I'd say the lamb is the star here ! It's got the perfect blend of flavours and is super juicy after being freshly grilled.

The owner is super nice too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp9mF5jPJ2wja3bI-ZwXjo2rd9Gj_zx4kRh4XC&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2023-12-23"},{"Name":"Omed Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqo1EPfYBmsn0_pWm5DVcXKffta1jMsPsqi9WlKLQrEHZLWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today at dinner tried their mix plate and the taste was amazing, great timing and very respectful staff , will try definitely other dishes too , reasonable price within area , love the restaurant!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNa-mDtJlshTc98wAR-1x90gybEZ9v1_axTEIdM&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"P Cho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYpqZl0QdgyGKqddwQHa-7-E_YzR-3F5N0QWNoWwJUTu4Gt_QA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here on a Friday night.  The place was clean and welcoming.

Foods pricing and portions were on par, plus we noticed the meats in our wraps were very moist and juicy.  The sauces were very fresh too.

We ordered gluten free pouting on the side and didn't notice any surpluses oiliness or grease that some other reviewers complained about with the fried food.

Overall, the food was excellent and we would come back.  We also recently ate at zam zam grill and Sher Donair's offerings are better in every way.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTuCp20iZosJlQUCp9UcJiN9v0MRwct7VHQ2dQ&fid=0x0:0xdb86fc07bce15dd5"],"When":"2023-11-25"},{"Name":"Ivan Pontacana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKrp9lgVb5VeUrXsIQKv_6aL1k477eiGm4jrYcLL-8Ru0WVVds=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't understand the bad reviews from this place. I‚Äôve been in this place a few times now and the food doesn‚Äôt fail to amaze us. I was doing laundry at the place next door with my girl and we decided to try it and it was fantastic. We had a chicken donair and it‚Äôs moist, juicy, tender, seasoning was a bomb, the veggies are fresh, you get a good crunch from the lettuce. Overall the food amazing (despite being inexpensive) and would recommend to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Andrei Lauren Nu√±ez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKm2dC2e73IFck9VUBz-XVzXEJPYv9NFPUpH0bIC5Mh5VsYRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was looking for a good place to eat near my hotel and this place has high google review. It did not disappoint.

Good variety of meat and veggie pizza available for slices. I love that the dough was just the right thickness. Nice texture and crisp outside. Pizza was not oily, it was a good balance of the sauce and toppings. Add some chilli flakes for a perfect bite.

Their lasagna though was not that good. It has too much tomato sauce, less meat and pasta.

So visit this place for their pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxFM_7GuoUABJWSgmM6BH19V4TDayN0aGoi5j0&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you‚Äôre wondering why this hole in the wall joint has such high reviews just keep scrolling. This part of the Granville strip has been known for affordable downtown pizza slices. When your bar hoping your gonna need something to soak up that alcohol‚Ä¶ for more alcohol. Don‚Äôt worry, that‚Äôs Sundays are for. To roll over and recuperate üòÇ

Service is friendly, efficient, and fast. This place pumps out so many pizzas it‚Äôs unbelievable. Great wholesome no frills joint that gets the job done.

Oh btw they have squeeze bottles of sauces and shakers if you want to jazz up your pizza slices.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ0SQqNZFdA7tsWQVb9JetBpeVVYsJsyrS9_W-&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Anj S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqc6Qk6ZPVGaDCNS9MIwNWBRPHLg6ObcnkgbolZEp2_WZQOFbRXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Giving 5 stars for the value for money and great selection of pizza options especially for vegetarians unlike any place in downtown. Usually pizzerias don‚Äôt take too much effort other than regular cheese or a margarita or one or two other loaded veggie pizza. But here I recall atleast seeing 7-10 on display each time!! (Thank you!!) Looks very fresh and a good place for quick grab and go slices. Almost visit here every week. Really friendly staff and quick service. Can‚Äôt wait to visit again soon!

A slight sprinkle of salt on the potato may help make the flavors explode better during the cook, but you can always add some to your liking if you wish like I do from the spice rank/condiment bar.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMl0vqqMiL-4cliOfgSMexZ9Ai66CjjeNdNw_Lo&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Shane Mahendran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD32nTOGZDrcGEcO0nogQjQEwve7bhkO4jwoo8X_T6-TbPJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizza on the Gran. Pizza tastes amazing and is not overpriced like some other shops in the area. Good deal on Tuesdays as well. They also have a washroom here. I like the chicken pizza. Is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOeN_Ud6HgQ2Y6NUS5n-Q3N3n0jpBEO2mVkQHZ&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"MAUREEN MITCHELL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7ybYJ2ul029Z-pHch_9hVGEeXeHlfQy5fMRDb7nh-bDtFj4qe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This review is for Danna she as well as Adriana they are the best girls I have ever meet. Im so glad to always know that my safe place will be always at ROMANO‚ÄôS to have a very nice pizza. Gracias por tanto Romanosü§çü§ç and for hiring such amazing stuff","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNWPRyQiFKhlbwNsms8XHcg57WCj8pvf52fhzd&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has the flavor!, there are a lot of pizza vendors between granville and davie street, the pizza slice here is good, the sesame seeds and the crust is delicious, the staff was very friendly!, without a doubt here every pizza is made daily and constantly during the day with fresh ingredients","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNR3bcHy9qi1LNP3iCa31OcO_aFuJnVf4_KKpBc&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Valerie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9cu87ZocLPoLFMrOcZZDaNbWlFC2ZlEbrE_5Cit0_Ced44g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's 11:30 p.m. on a holiday Monday and I'm sitting amidst a still bustling Granville Street at a tiny outdoor table and chairs, with music pouring out the door into the traffic, sipping my beer and eating my pizza (with extra sesame seeds) ($7.50 + tip), and I'm happy. I don't really drink beer or eat pizza too often and I've never had it with sesame seeds before (and they added a few more when I said I liked them), but I live not too far away and it's a pleasant walk on a warm evening, and, for a woman on her own, it's a great low-key, get-out-of-the-house kind of thing to do with my trusty attack poodle. I'll probably do it more than a few times in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLsd4nYucoWNpDXx0BuQHmDbiFp5r043kHBXBo&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Ryan Ross","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxbDlhVenJX4nGQzNLn3JyLXDgKUYiH-a3lBo-VWu7_cthLUW_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pizza here is incredibly fresh and super delicious and a nice variety of interesting toppings. I really enjoyed the pizza here. The atmosphere is... well it Granville Street which is always kind of electric. I did however find the music just a touch loud as it was hard to sit with my partner and talk comfortably. That's my only complaint if you can call it that. I would DEFINITELY eat here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkFtilTpdJC0Agwg0CmegSxrLQThdYY4tqD0W3&fid=0x0:0xce790ac55a613de5"],"When":"2024-8-15"}]

Unaware the Big Mac in the box and paper bag as:  Unbelievable for this happened. How can they give me the Big Mac without the right top bun without sesame. Top and bottom bun bread are the same. Food was fantastic!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZ_irA5B7h79L7TlMR3zKo6l-GMIq-UHiAUDse&fid=0x0:0x34c4cd0844c8b48c"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The new renovation looks great.
Ivan the manager is doing a great job here.

As for the corporation I‚Äôm disappointed.
Your prices have inflated wayyyy too fast. It seems like every 6 months to 10 months prices are hiked. I question how other fast food corps can have better value and better prices than McCorp.

My family and huge extended families come to McDonald‚Äôs because of the memories we‚Äôve had. When our mom use to pick us up after school in the elementary years everyday and there was a McDonald‚Äôs across the street. When our grandma had some money left over to take her all her grandchildren out for a mcd day. We would talk about anything and have big smiles on our faces. McDonald‚Äôs at that time was special and nostalgic. Over the years we‚Äôve collected memorabilia like the bed sheets and shower curtains .Many more Memorabilia that I won‚Äôt even post online.

I‚Äôm looking at the current generation of families that cannot have these new memories without questioning their spending because of the menu prices. Every family I see coming in are not buying combos and I see mothers feeding their kids first then eating their left overs when they had enough‚Ä¶these are not mchappy memories.

I recently just got back from a trip from Washington state. It‚Äôs actually worse‚Ä¶ even though they have the 1,2,3 dollar value items.
Lots of signs saying bathrooms are for customers only. Not one single person I saw ordered a full combo. Not as many smiles dining.

This is a message to the McDonald‚Äôs Corp.
Yes, you will still have customers. Some of the time who don‚Äôt have time, who are lazy, and who believe your French fries are the king. Yes you will still have customers who love your summertime dollar drinks and ice cream cones. Yes you will have people who are devoted to your brand all over the world‚Ä¶
But as all that is going on you missed out on what‚Äôs going on now. That these families who cannot afford or have value from your brand is now creating new happier memories and getting better value from other fast food chains. Memorable moments with their grandparents and loved ones. Tailgate meet ups at other fast food joint parking lots. More affordability which means it‚Äôs not a once a week or month occurrence.

This is just my opinion and from what I‚Äôve seen. I am the few that luckily can afford this brand. During lockdown I am an essential worker working LONG hours everyday and I literally bought this brand everyday for 2 years non stop because I had no time to pack a second lunch or make a proper coffee. If you don‚Äôt believe me ask management all along marine drive to marine way market crossing. Along with this location on knight. This brand gave me comfort in the most uncertain times. I and a few other in the drive thru also paid for the person behind us just to make their day happier. We didn‚Äôt have to but we followed a movement that was on social media. It created a mchappy memory‚Ä¶

Now my final question to the McDonald‚Äôs food corporation. Can you make better prices and value so that your customers who want to be like a second family would want to continue bringing generations to your brands consistently? Because they are making memories elsewhere. You haven‚Äôt been affordable nostalgia for a while in case you haven‚Äôt noticed.

Update after 2 weeks of posting.
Even your coupon booklet isn‚Äôt reasonable for families.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGlYJXdQZqJ63KCRLrfAhJNvTNFMT3DwrJ-h2k&fid=0x0:0x34c4cd0844c8b48c"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"Jeanne M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLOWBH8NGqqsl5I8s_Iw6M9jwENQkw814Drzz2sFzuQGsiaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôm confused by the poor reviews. It‚Äôs not an easy role & I appreciate the time they take to say good morning and general pleasantries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dropped in for a quick bite and had to wait for a decaf coffee to be brewed which is fine. Be respectful with your customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnqI87ufMVWM7u9UYMKkV6RkkHxuOHvUR5T55W&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This homey and authentic joint is awesome! Mediterranean food by far is incredibly underrated and absolutely delicious.

I got a few Falafels to go for a light snack. Very reasonable fare for fresh, crispy yet super light and soft in the middle yummy falafel pucks.
Support local businesses!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtFM6qsoNTk8sjuvLzZj5tuLN02BriRpjN5r3f&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"Amanda Murphy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxcf7wijOMQ178k9n9pGU8lN8BtsYrtwrmHD7Rw4bBdnWJsgdL4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The quality of the food seems to have gone down significantly. I thought last time was a one-off where the chicken was dry and cold, but I tried again today and it was even worse. The Tabbouleh salad had mostly brown parsley, and the chicken was so dry and chewy, it tasted very old.

The baklava was still great though.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Carr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4uxa-qU5MId4bNs3nE5XJEEmluarCVMbCpsa6WPQYZ8eWCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very happy to find this place open after 10pm on a Monday eve. Young man working on his own there was friendly and served us a delicious lamb/beef donair/shawarma plate. Next time on the Drive, will consider going there again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFJ8p2yH69Q6k7X9N4-xEWjnsccs-bwMBNqeag&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Mark Lui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs4xB0NqrWAxxVdtZfx0PPgJ6rp3zr-S59b3NmYRouHeiCFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered delivery here, the wrap came soggy.
The chicken was dry and the rice itself was a bit bland.
I was more disappointed that they forgot the pita wrap with my chicken platter, with no bread at home I just threw the humus away.
No cutlery and napkins were provided despite ordering quite a bit of food

The Tabuli was pretty good, and the Jamaican beef patty was really tasty, I would probably come back again just for the patty, however, everything else was a bit disappointing.

overall, food was just okay (except for the beef patty which was good) and presentation was very disappointing especially with the missing pita bread and the lack of napkins and cutlery for a pretty decent sized order","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOP-UBFa9S_AX1E9pSRKVR_V1mp19dXObaU00N8&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2021-11-6"},{"Name":"Fiona Bratvold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkKVshxGxVMEEGCFFS3gcEVu3bxn4uRZ1N7p-__IzVtiTHsl7bdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had the chicken schwarma plate which was good. It was big so we shared it. Their baklava was very good as well. Some indoor seating. Quick service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNieOyMooacPcRVeMq_jt3MCb2v3W_KMYRZ32Wr&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2022-7-5"},{"Name":"John Pozer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe0BvqmYZVSdl8vMzkjfI5nnnXlGPCIuhLYzs9LnFZvwXYyqQh7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our ‚Äògo to‚Äô spot for chicken shawarma to go. Flavourful offerings overall. Dolmas are good.  So are the desserts. Your choice of baked or fried falafels (we get the fried). Pleasant folks behind the counter. Best Falafel on the Drive serves up consistently good takeout.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPVPIXjUunhykfzeK4kqR23HKmAxZbpUhZZEpU&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2021-7-30"},{"Name":"Reese Rahman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWICCjWdp8WYPeYO6pbcSOB-xxL-u0GIR7tROouV2sVezq20ary6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to the Best Falafel restaurant on Commercial Drive with a friend who's never had Middle Eastern food before.

Tried the Beef and Chicken Shawarma plate. They were REALLY GOOD!! Wow! Tastes amazing!
The Garlic sauce was soooo gooood! I asked for extra garlic sauce and they had no problem giving it to me.

It's a subway style restaurant, they ask you what you want in your shawarma (chicken, beef or lamb) and then vegetables and pickles.

The service was really good, they were very friendly and courteous and the food, like I mentioned, was top notch!

I'm definitely coming back here again.

I would definitely recommend this restaurant to everyone! A++++","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhQ1peTRNdQW_-z6tBIRfSzKwFdnpe_dDVD-3C&fid=0x0:0x26ede6d268ce3b9a"],"When":"2018-4-14"}]

Next time im getting chicken or something fancier.  I dont remember the kingsway location i use to go to taste like this. and the bread i thought was lighter.  Will not return unfortunately.  Bahn mi Saigon and 88 Supermarket has hands-down the best consistent subs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuFIG1IsHN3kgqIQSRTV3ww6i-W049jO109BcP&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Selina Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkhYkD3SpMETmescS1PYdIbdJEawmCXCZQlnmigsplBzK04eI7SA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 banh mi with nice service and a cute atmosphere. The bread is so delicious as it is warm and fresh. Unlike a lot of other banh mi places, they accept card and tap here which is really convenient. It‚Äôs reasonably priced and there is space to eat inside. I can‚Äôt wait to be back and try other things on their menu","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCM0gpUViCJe3NETo9c7_SGFwD84WJait_vpZj&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2023-12-21"},{"Name":"D S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiwZP5uC5CzBgSahQQVkTqGSd5rHWgB0GVCkCWen4FIy1S7JRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the Classic Bahn Mi and it was absolutely delicious! One if the best I've had, perfect tasty pate and had jalapeno and cilantro like a classic should!
The coconut smoothie was also nice and coconutty! The Thai Green tea was not too sweet either.
This place makes one if the best Bahn Mis I've tasted!
Keep up the great work.
Treat yourself and visit now!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjuTCwcNDSnBs-MLlFcM4jXLAyJSmOwO0_y97D&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2024-2-12"},{"Name":"Angela Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgU359Dev9tceZMdK-W_jXN8y0TQSEb9-IOLDnCR1DHt7zaMRcfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're looking for a delicious and affordable Vietnamese sandwich spot, definitely check this place out! Stumbled upon this place and I'm so glad I did!
Ordered the #7 The Deluxe Classic and #8 The Classic, and both sandwiches were absolutely delicious. The bread was soft and fresh, and the meats and veggies were fresh as well and not soggy.
To complement the sandwiches, I tried the Vietnamese coffee which was perfectly brewed and the Mango Smoothie which was an absolute must-try. The smoothie was made fresh with real mango bits and my boyfriend, who is a smoothie lover, absolutely loved it!
Pricing is very reasonable, and the service is to par. Overall, a fantastic spot for a quick, delicious, and affordable meal. Highly recommend giving it a try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv7gYVYcJ4DJl4be_DT0BhotOKM5h3oN5AwGcb&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2023-4-10"},{"Name":"Sayani Chowdhury","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjD34o3DB1ZpRQF82FIyI7sLdx6aLu5umEaHn-Fepbek1_K2P0gQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Banh Mi I‚Äôve had in Canada! My friend and I both ordered the lemongrass chicken Banh Mi and I was so impressed. The chicken was so flavourful and the sandwich had the perfect ratio of veggies to meat. It wasn‚Äôt dry and was not too saucy either, it was just perfect. The items on the menu were also reasonably priced and given the size of the Banh Mi, you will definitely get your money‚Äôs worth. I would definitely recommend this place if you‚Äôre in the area. I know I‚Äôm definitely going to come back here to try their other menu items!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTn7FF4yuynFw7hLHRs6_KtUY_KuRFUhBqX8jI&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2023-2-21"},{"Name":"Marcus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVpAqx3Judbzb0iuJXzx52iIPBZjNV225UkWQ26P-4HM5WbcSiFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the lemon grass chicken and the satay beef. Both were very tasty! I really enjoyed the ingredients they tasted fresh and there was a little bit of spicy in the satay beef. I would definitely come here again, or order from here again highly recommend trying this place out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXpvznkiSybQ-iklKFPIavFkHwavAB2pRGnEDA&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2021-5-28"},{"Name":"Al May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURsEKydI6yFDWfeEuJUm_zojUlbRJUnS2y7j3NZKmrARii_3iYLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm not much of a sub or sandwich person until someone gave me a really good Bahn Mi last week. Now, I crave it regularly. I've been looking for a good Bahn Mi place and decided to order from here based on the rating it has on my delivery app. I love the fact that you can customize your order, like getting veggies on the side. It's great for picky eaters. The fact that you can add a fried egg to any sandwich is a plus in my books
I love the portions. They definitely don't skimp on the filling. I'll be ordering from here from now on. That Beef Sate sun is excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSTPkKki0FnCdoWG21QWxEctP0WLUmG1ClR5w_&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2022-9-25"},{"Name":"Kit Yee Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUy4hyLjXryzPjKJf4N3DUJBAsHtZSSuk76pvxFtVmwfHSV1Gtd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered a deluxe cold cut banh mi through DoorDash. I received an email and text confirmation quickly that the restaurant received my order. It was quite fast. When I got to the restaurant and picked up my food in 15 mins or so, the banh mi was ready for pickup. The restaurant was quite efficient.

It was my first time to try the banh mi here. The deluxe cold cut banh mi tasted delicious. The bun was crispy outside and soft inside. There was a lot of ingredients as well. It was great to eat it fresh!! It was big enough for me that I had to save some for the next day haha

I would recommend this banh mi restaurant to others. I know there is competition in the neighborhood but in terms of quality and quantity this one is QUITE GOOD!! I had some banh mi elsewhere. The bun was big and had less ingredients or it was cheaper elsewhere but the quality was not good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrUw6rWVuoBodJxWdvbKb_qjqXQmqlcuGcDOvK&fid=0x0:0xab569ff9888224d9"],"When":"2022-1-9"}]

[{"Name":"Edward Morgan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlCdKVa5JRpIwPRgKv6NNGwpeGpzREQZR8ZT02GyKWsnAcP6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"One of the worst food experiences of my life. On the bright side- great location and views.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcMUOMo7TrK7_-QUVgd2YACx1ndTq9p8kPhAxW&fid=0x0:0xc6fc08f9b003f1bc"],"When":"2023-9-6"},{"Name":"Wan Ming Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwNlRFQz1VdbZPr8e_ll_ehCUEStZLojP_qGYBHGN6qBI3UA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always like this occasional breaking of restrictions of diet

Fish and chips are Soo tempting. Freshly made. It a "must" to enjoy.

Then a big cookie, + ice cream cone, or ice cream sandwich.

Fresh air, blue sky, mountains, sea, yachts, kids..,

HEAVENLY God's creation. FREE..

Who needs to go to Switzerland.
(I had been there!!)
NO CONCESSION STAND BY swiss LAKES.

We had Europe, Hawaii  right here in our back yard..+ Fish & chips/hot dogs","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh0iI6z9T3XP9qBejCw583rhjzRSLWqfR6ixKc&fid=0x0:0xc6fc08f9b003f1bc"],"When":"2018-6-22"},{"Name":"Affan A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLrM1LQYBsViBSZx78fpcohHxqSb34Funvp0-nxL1Ij2zSzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I regularly visit this place and bought a scoop of ice cream (vanilla) which gave me stomach pain. Would not recommend their ice cream. As I  eat ice cream on regular basis from other shop(s) and never have such stomach pain.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzWpxN7dQOjyf925QLIP6KlWKBxzoQDIDMXvP1EyvoqxWwlrRd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First the good news: This cafe is located at Locarno Beach Park, which includes a beautiful sandy beach and grassy area in Vancouver BC. The views are magnificent, with the giant cargo ships in the bay and the North Vancouver mountains. Unbelievable these days, parking is free, but the number of spaces  is limited and tend to fill up early in the day.
Second, the bad news: A number of typical fast foods are available, but I made the bad decision to try the fish and chips. While the serving was large, the fish tasted like old, burnt, cooking oil. While some like crispy batter, this one was well beyond crispy. You had to battle through it with firm stabs of the provided wooden fork. If the word ‚Äòfish‚Äô had not been on the menu I would not have known what that white stuff inside the batter was. Zero taste. A bland, underwhelming taste of nothing. The fries were just passable, by which I mean only arguably edible. Thank goodness there was an unlimited supply of ketchup, vinegar, mustard etc. Having attempted to eat the food, I can see the need for unlimited access to condiments!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phil Davies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfLb1D8MDBOtzug8AzffJQIiix-nC5Bs7PigxNbqp4KdqwfuLj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Fries were cold and expensive. [{"Name":"Tejas Borse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6TtXC_z-K3cC-HpGsmgyxF1iymAI-gnqx6sMAAh4eHqsm6dtRzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best places to get good Indian style street food. The crispy batter they use to fry paneer and spring rolls gives it a unique crunch which doesn‚Äôt go soggy until the last bite.

Sauces are tasty, flavors are balanced. The menu is mix and match of few basic ingredients which are done very well.

Masala Lemonade Mojito is my all time favorite and must try. I would recommend this over the lassi they offer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMFZvZT1umHvEylahb2oeAJAHxH7wdDiVfBN1A&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Priya Katoch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgsUGlsGkjDHpnjsybHy3se942oeGjhGKjBQQIW2kQewiTMhE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered their Kulcha (hot) on Delivery.

I was really craving for an Indian desi chilli Kulcha and they were good to my expectations.

I would love to visit this place in person next time and would definitely try other items.

Thank you for the amazing food.

Just a suggestion: if you could also add onions and tomatoes to give it authentic taste.

Anyways it was good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMg9sGDRfmAdYLF-QiQh8FjeBYQUpgJevQBMjQx&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Mr. Surya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBrn9nd1HcDRdmtXAMfMXUvo9HXV6arQCmsPAMeCB7UNfrsdPy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The taste of the food was good, though it took some time to prepare, it was worth waiting once I got to eat it. However, there were a few aspects that left me slightly disappointed.

Firstly, the quantity shown in the picture menu didn‚Äôt match what was served. This was particularly noticeable with the ‚ÄúChole Kulche‚Äù ‚Äì I was expecting the usual larger white buns as kulchas, but instead, they served smaller bread buns. It was a bit of a surprise.

Another downside was the customer service. When I asked for ketchup, they gave me just one small packet. I found this frustrating, especially considering I was spending nearly $30 there. A little more generosity and customer focus would have made the experience better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRzcv_xd89cgLmyAyYaN9pPAvd1uwHwkNAib9U&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Liver Gol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWGm5l482jrOhrHHAESl--Lf9jpRdpeU_ZN_8myALJcC33NA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, greate service!  I really like Anushka‚Äôs hospitality. Definitely try it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhvbNltISzEVzo14Jj33AKN1Z6y8gXby0ubaVI&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"Savan Brar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIZ732pPrbeF_6nZ_O5bUQsPAaCL08DX1zR25a0Cll1G52RLM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here today around 1 pm. A girl named Tanya was alone at the store and it was quite busy. She handled the store well and served the order within 15-20 minutes of ordering. I really really liked her service, the food and the the way she greeted everyone with a smile. Just loved the experience and will visit againüòä","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luckman Bin Karim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe8RkNgeDn37D2jo3OQCVbDlw0wevZ4eq7orymsdObF7OjXqC0qA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried Noodle Tikki Burger, Mixed Frankie, Chaat fries (must try) and Bhelpuri.
.
Top marks for price, quantity and quality!

The orange mojito was also good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvkSo4K9G6EvSHH4DPVv0JFdyzCq5sVgLZcmR0&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Jessica Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOeC5VCbc6g3HH3dxXpDS9bE993HEKMDVI3SjHX2aNdHbQOJHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the noodle burger here so much I'm happy this was the first place I ever tried that after it being recommended to me. I tried the paneer version and loved it so much because of all the flavors; perfect amount of spice for any person and age and also a delicious touch of fresh green mint chutney.. it was better than any other kind of burger I've had and but found out afterwards that the aloo tikki version is actually the original so I can't wait to try that one too!! The service was so great and unbelievably fast and the price was cheaper than I would expect too, I wish this place was right beside where I live.. will be dreaming of this nice clean place with refreshing orange colored signage on their exterior (that matches the color of the exterior of the paneer üòä) for a long time.. Oh yea I also loved the way they spelled my name ü•∞","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEe4fKfmMaH5zByis8ne-1v9PEzqLJnVfhrWUY&fid=0x0:0x531502ed402dd483"],"When":"2023-12-11"},{"Name":"Yuvraj Jain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN-3NiA3Yd9giGlh4rWJ-qMAUnCaZIkhUvbaJbZrN_VK9RgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An employee whose name I regrettably cannot recall, possibly Sukriti or similar, demonstrated exceptional dedication and customer service during my recent visit to the restaurant. Despite the store's imminent closing time, she graciously welcomed me in, took my order, and ensured I received my burger promptly. Such dedication is a valuable asset to your restaurant. The service and food were both excellent.

Thank you for taking my order. I made a special trip from North Vancouver specifically to dine at the restaurant with my family. We appreciate the efforts of the Desi Rasoi team.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I also ordered their Hong Kong style milktea and it was good!! It tasted exactly how I remember it when I visited HK couple years ago! it I Overall, I had a positive experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN97GlrvJrYukqXvowHcXoiqVCvMwrVRyjVzucU&fid=0x0:0x4a5b13cc31a39fa3"],"When":"2023-8-17"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This location of Bubble Waffle Cafe is tucked away in the back corner of a mini mall on 49th. The interior isn't much to look at and seems rather tired.

We tried a bubble waffle, homemade squid, and a bowl of laksa. The homemade squid had a sweet soy type sauce but was rather chewy. Laksa was ok (does the job when you're hungry).

Really more of a place to go to when you're just looking for convenience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOklENDxEClDl1kTVGqbmmU0qC3TewnF2e3Ejs_&fid=0x0:0x4a5b13cc31a39fa3"],"When":"2022-12-14"},{"Name":"A\","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAtFvT66BrPzDsAuvVTADb_6b1z0bZi7KvVADur_sNdRd0RHNC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Had the angus beef for take out. The beef was dry and tasteless, the potato tots were soggy, and the rice was mushy, gummy, and was as tasteless as the beef.

This is the kind of week-old rice that you throw out, not serve to paying customers. Especially with barely any sauce. I couldn‚Äôt eat more than two bites of it

If you can‚Äôt get plain white rice right, what are you doing running a chinese restaurant?

I do not recommend coming here for food but the milk tea was decent","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPcnAkJ-3a1CaPzLO5iQX04ussACa8slf2AuPm&fid=0x0:0x4a5b13cc31a39fa3"],"When":"2022-12-3"},{"Name":"Howie Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXD4mFYNLrhmouUG8HDSxtKZr3rHrib8bLXPruDpfwlU6cD46WXcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place like your typical Hong Kong cafe where you can choose two protein, a noodle and a soup. My go to is their watercress chicken soup as it is the most cleanest from all the other soup.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAHzReF9bGw6mPrS4GyukbwGFMeIDdGC4mfdSI&fid=0x0:0x4a5b13cc31a39fa3"],"When":"2018-5-7"},{"Name":"Alfred Hou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxRYfQDO0EsWS7dlsuuAhjN34jihWDFNU2nmj2V08l3qoILQM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff coupled with great service. I have had A&W in Calgary about 3 yrs ago and had A&W years ago in high school on a branch in the Philippines. I had good memories with this fast food chain but the food is now different. It seems like a regular burger with nothing on it. The poutine fries seemed inedible for me. I have had fast food but I would never try A&w again. I am not sure if its just because it is within the food court and the other A&W establishment is much better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMg7LPx-EAFuHa_X08kDIGKyY_TVb7lbWCuONrd&fid=0x0:0xc748b0e466274f76"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"tanish mahajan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItXC0j9qmM1ffVC752JPWZiYXCSOyPcJJYojyoX8VK8sqh5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The customer service I experienced today (August 8) was disappointing. I've been coming to this location for the past four years without any issues. Typically, I receive excellent service and enjoy the food. However, today's visit fell far short of my expectations.

At around 13:05, I ordered a Chubby Chicken Combo and requested extra onions, tomatoes, and spicy sauce in the burger. The girl serving me not only entered the wrong order but also didn't seem to be paying attention and lacked any friendliness.

Even after I corrected her, I still received the incorrect order, with no tomatoes or spicy sauce in the burger.

Unfortunately, I didn't have time to return my order and ask for it to be fixed since I was on my break and couldn't afford to wait. So, I just ate what I was given. I don't understand why she seemed to be in such a rush, especially since there were no other customers in line behind me.

I get that she might have been having a bad day, and working in a fast-paced environment can be tough, but it's important to serve customers properly and not ruin their experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A&W is awesome and the best fast food joint across Canada. I used my app discount for a dollar coffee, super great value for a semi good cup of joe in a really convenient location.

[{"Name":"Lynda Anvieh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRCmcjbTOWKz4070AKM_k900uORtnzvaz0BgTsInPhDjl2Tn4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really cozy and nice restaurant! Easy to get to and easy to find. The service was great but the food was amazing. I had a smoky bbq burger (I think) and my friend got the mushroom burger. We both loved our meals. The side of poutine was huge and chips weren‚Äôt mushy- they were still crunchy. I had the yam fries- really delicious too. It was a great meal! Really tasty! Thank you Blaze!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOizPR9auETqyy2eRe_OeJ1Yx7qSEVnldCkjwP9&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Bruno Rodrigues","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhILuyIb0LIP6MudwbcSE2BAlE-f9U9SKRT2p9lsRwJ4hM0FgDLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ridiculously good sandwich. I can only imagine what's like dining in. Amazing buns and juicy meat. The sauce was delicious and proportionately adequate to the ingredients. Burger came still hot and well-packaged. Definitely will order again; huge shout out to the people at the kitchen!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyhtY4O0G4RSJ5mh0TpratiFRzpN1SXw6FOLRg&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Charlotte Ahern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIPiozrQvoE9VHwHlHplLKf8CwHn2sxLmtNEQA3XBtEU3mCI2D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was here for a media brunch, the room is gorgeous they have really gone all out with beautiful Christmas decorations! I had heard good things about their burgers, but we were there for brunch. I loved the Avo toast, it has pomegranate on it which adds really nice freshness to the meal. I also loved the Spicy beef totchos they were most delicious!!! Im not a vegetarian but i enjoyed trying their offerings, it felt very inclusive for vegas and vegetarians. They also have really good coffee! Loved it, and can't wait to go back! Also forgot to mention the Tirimisu, yummy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiztaGdmyaNHn8unYvLM7oZMCguYtexkAsw_60&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"N Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKf1tjsbO0IVlG6oW5arzFngLpWhdrUq3fEkqtAlTTt6fUqtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I don't often have burgers, but was struck by a craving and decided to get delivery from Blaze, which had been more than satisfactory in the past.

... but not today!

To their credit, the flavour in general was good, and they clearly labelled my gluten-free burger and wrote "contain gluten" on the box of twisty fries.

But my Smoky BBQ Blaze burger did not come with any of the crispy onion frites, and my boyfriend's had maybe half a teaspoon, which was even more insulting in a way.

Also, the yam fries box looked half full??? I've ordered them before and I've never had such a sad serving. Thankfully, the twisty fries box was properly packed, but what happened to the yam fries? It was enough to briefly make me wonder if our uber driver had stolen some before remembering that the bag had been stapled shut to prevent such theft.

I know food costs are stupid everywhere these days, but if I'm paying $16 for a "gourmet" burger and $11 for yam fries, I don't want to be wondering where parts of my meal are.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPG0bIYagrJkL7frlp_PgMdCeKo4IMMsxjKk5ii&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Fuzzy Nemo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhjGNDhI-RZYgIiVRXnRDEQCiyyP-dsVjb7EhBkcymNr9MvYi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I said this place was amazing,  it would not be doing it justice at all.  I have tried a lot of burgers and this one is definitely my favorite.  It does not taste commercial at all and the prices are VERY reasonable.   This is almost like a hidden gem that I stumbled upon.   The truffle fries are very good as well.  The onion rings are not outstanding,  but still very good.  If I lived a little closer,  I would be back and try all their other burgers.  BUT, I would definitely make sure to go back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON4ELaiOHBNY5Xd0AFnX2cWo8S-7EYYju0gZGR&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Kaveesh Kukreja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyGM5Wur1OIcPaIKHk8y8hADl72LlmzqOApRwMvp0cKEQAxid2PA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Blaze was a place I was very much looking forward to visiting. Now I probably won't visit it again solely because I am not a fan of chipotle and all chicken burgers have chipotle on them but it wasn't bad at all.
I like the fact that their chicken sandwhiches don't have a monstrous piece in between making it super messy and impossible to eat.
My vegetarian friend however, absolutely loved her dish so for veggies out there definitely check it out.
We also ordered the crispy chicken poutine which was probably our least favorite dish.
Service is phenomenal but they don't service alcohol which kinda sucks.

Worth a try out once for sure","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpuuYGGNnEtNHO3t4TyXsXyccqQbFhU56NFGXt&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Sash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsEN8LESXHdVUHALQ4S3DxVR2gfd5knlpOhRGZTjLzMJeMHtuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the plant based burgers I‚Äôve ever eaten. The patty and the ingredients are really fresh and go well together. My friend really enjoyed the same burger on a gluten free bun (yay for celiacs).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYV2XenX0TX9HdylcZUxLV8MBMXHQTrPZUHD0y&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Hye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULQQSi1mhNFty7n8ZPesKkMpD31jiIGazltx_wRmE-swaOwr4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was pretty curious about this place because of their good reviews and had a chance to give it a try. I was going to have a beef burger at first, but I suddenly craved a juicy chicken burger and ordered the 'Chipotle Chicken Blaze' with a side of onion rings.

The onion rings were not that hot when they came out, but I liked that they were very crispy. I was a bit worried that the chicken might be a bit dry since they used chicken breast, but it was pretty tender. The burger had jalape√±os and crunchy pickles inside, but somehow I was eating a burger with only chicken, lettuce, and chipotle mayo. I felt like it could use a bit more kick, like hot sauce, or freshness from tomato. I liked their brioche bun, though.

Including a diet coke and tips, I paid $30, and I was pretty shocked by Vancouver's prices again. I paid double what I would at McDonald's, and I wasn't sure if the experience was worth the price. The service was very casual, and it was a good place for dining alone comfortably. If I have another chance, I'd like to try one of their beef burgers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQBdTl-Q_k5URxTN00NHYy6W4hk_2cxbRstJ4&fid=0x0:0xe62244d7842806e4"],"When":"2024-7-31"}]

The staff called Simran was polite, friendly and fast, but staff can‚Äôt go against managements wishes.

Maybe it's procedure for staff to do this, to delay a walk in customer order midway for a food delivery service order, but it felt very inappropriate.

I couldn't eat the second half of my sandwich, because the bread had returned to dough form. Three sandwiches (meals) were about $60. It seemed a mistake spending that much money on that experience. I asked myself "What's the point of coming to a fast food restaurant if the food is really slow? What's the point of cheap restaurant food if the food isn't cheap?" If it had been cheaper and faster I'd forgive the apathetic service and fall-apart bathroom fixtures... maybe even the soggy sandwich.

I also asked/told the lady who took my order a few times i just dont want jasmine rice and to substitute brown rice instead. And she confirmed thay yes they can do it. My order came in like 2 minutes which was nice since I need to go to a meeting. But Im not coming back here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBA6Q6Vzv5WIh-7UGzS5BAzRuSinhs9z_vG0EI&fid=0x0:0x73f56725d01c495b"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"violeta cobo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6wgC3mWSh0Kf2wMY_fEmEq8a-W46X6C_bgSDd2k_oy9FUccjz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so surprised to see this place has Bad reviews, my partner and I absolutely loved it.

- The food: top quality, and incredible flavor. Best burger I have had in a long time. GREAT meat.

-The service: friendly and fast (maybe because there was not a lot of people but still: friendly and fast).

- The ambient: incredible jazz relaxing music perfect for conversation‚Ä¶ and digestion!

We will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNngt50MMuTznqC9ekAcAU_tIDoj3InUQwr7iVw&fid=0x0:0x73f56725d01c495b"],"When":"2024-2-3"},{"Name":"Mia Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGOq27m5S-AFQ5o99BINjtIuuJESD44KI2k4LTBAQqMOddKsc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came in for a salad and juice.
