It has fresh spring mix, cherry tomatoes, corn, white onion, taco bite sized pieces, bite sized avocado. I got chicken and it‚Äôs shredded chicken pieces or bite sized. Just the right amount of dressing.
4-6 people seating.
There is music playing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNemgaxwrqW5EWeIZ1ik5DeXz04XaNYD4CVlLB3&fid=0x0:0x73f56725d01c495b"],"When":"2023-11-27"},{"Name":"Adam Durante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoeaVsK-bN-3a6oaiIu_JEPHIuWPh6m_NNo6rT75BjgXtkQ6c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great find today. I‚Äôll be back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8NNB-hWqb8V5-rlW4BqpEZLSOamOg-8IJkPiZ&fid=0x0:0x73f56725d01c495b"],"When":"2023-11-28"},{"Name":"Anonymous A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIC45f9XZqvVXq7IFMyb_6YuWoo35F9HKet-ojaiF0Y7jQTCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst burrito I‚Äôve had in my life! The pricing makes no sense. You can build your own but you cannot select an option on the list and make any alterations. Then they charge extra for the same products you would get if you built your own. Overall bad service and bad tasting food","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terahn Harrison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZhFtd3wWQf9pal0mjRsV4WZgJVXlVEScSsAeBoPOOgpzZxYRi5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Hungry Guys used to be a great lunch spot for build-your-own burritos and salads. I came back today after a couple months and now it has completely pivoted into a burger and milkshake place.? Am I wrong in thinking this is a bit of a scummy move? Alienating your existing customer base solely to increase their own profit margins.

They‚Äôre basically a different business that is using the same name as the old business to benefit from the existing reviews which are no longer relevant. They also haven‚Äôt updated their description on Google Maps nor their own website.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQW0GIztMTg2rY26ctunVqvAl5yK5FBReHK4lj&fid=0x0:0x73f56725d01c495b"],"When":"2023-11-2"}]

It's just not worth it anymore.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ah Dairy Queen. Definitely sure brings back memories. If fact back in my second year of high school, I use to use to work with dq and orange julius.

I recently downloaded the app and got an offer for a $1 small blizzard. Lemme tell ya, the prices weren‚Äôt like they use to be that‚Äôs for sure.

It was 2:30am in the morning and I had a hankering for ice cream. I didn‚Äôt know this location was open till 5am! So I went for a drive. I never tried the strawberry cheesecake blizzard before, ever. It‚Äôs definitely my new blizzard favourite now. Generous chunks of cheese cakes. Mixed with chunks of strawberries and syrup. Man‚Ä¶ it really hit the spot. I‚Äôm usually a Oreo or chocolate guy but this one really impressed me. Thank you for the cool treat! I wish I took a better picture but it was so good I gobbled it up so quickly!

As for service I mean‚Ä¶ what do you expect. It‚Äôs graveyard. There were 2 guys hustling away stocking and cleaning. One guy at the cashier had a negative tone taking my order. He probably had a check list of duties going on from his boss. Or perhaps he has another job or problems at home. Second guy made the blizzard. I was wondering while he was making it if he was going to hand it to me upside down, like I always did when I was a teen. To my surprise he did, and with a smile. üòÄ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBtdboEf85sihGD4pcpfK7hrBW0pDJDiKfzNZg&fid=0x0:0x2bed4d4499a86380"],"When":"2024-4-6"},{"Name":"Rodel Lavarias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK33jQzZLhkCsZO5Bkc9Qn94KDbG2JocChILQYPHxqzjar-GA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"08/10 12:25noon, no customers dined and a grumpy and very unprofessional service crew. Beware of this place, it‚Äôs not worth going here anymore.","Images":null,"When":""}]

If you like subway","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Conrad Fitz-Gerald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1wWwAqLyy8-EABwo-AWs5siP1-alF6rl2EGQxzG_0Y76rBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Washroom has been out over 2 weeks.  Their excuse is no key but it just happens to be locked inside. Being a worker in retail before you put Ina service order right away.  I remind them daily and they have failed to even put in the order today. I'm a paying customer and when I ask for hot water with my food they ALWAYS give me it in a single thin plastic cold cup. Having worked for Teavana I know what they are trying to do. The paper cups cost more, but not as much as reputation or already dedicated customers. Overall I'd say this place should be turned into an express with a sign that clearly states no washroom.  For all the reasons above I give this location a 1.

*Edit*
Later went to see if the bathroom even had a sign for out of order.  It didn't so tried the door and it was hard to open, but managed to get inside and found there was no key.  Used the washroom and no leaking.  The employees are blatantly lying to their customers saying the key is lost or worse that the key is locked inside which by my photos proves to be a lie. [{"Name":"Eric Rosales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTf95sVgha95pfV66waRgSTtWkiY6o3kR6NstOoHsjnSEESQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ive eaten Vietnamese subs for years in the Vancouver and San Jose California area and thought I've had mostly good and a few great subs along the way. So, when I ordered Viet Sub's "Special sub", I was pleasantly surprised that it actually tasted especial--because it was delicious!!! Id say it was one of, if not the best Viet sub I've had as far as I can remember in my 20+ years of Viet sub eating experience. The bread was perfectly warm and crusty without being too hard and dry. The fillings, especially the pork, tasted and looked fresh and juicy.  I think the pork and bread set it apart from the others. Just delicious. It's hard to fault it...maybe a little too small?

When I'm in the area, whether or not I'm craving for that sub, I'll definitely want to return to have a taste of it again.

The place was just a little tight so it may be a bit hard to eat there during busy periods tho I've never really been there during a busy period.

Nice friendly service. No upselling, just straightforward.

I rarely give 5 stars but based on my experience, I can't give Viet sub anything lower than a 4.5, so 5 stars it is.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuMZqpd585GyVZdMBxatPPL9kW0bUQfxegRG4c&fid=0x0:0x7841c3ab476168bc"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Deanna Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAIMuiZXNoLL-0mgGkxcsbbha_YGCdK_P3PUPvdJtUCcYnOe99=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Already dug in before I took a photo üòÇ I don‚Äôt usually do reviews but I really do love this place. [{"Name":"Abraham Jose Arencibia Carrero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ3MrO6qzFAuJsvL0GeVfVlTJvcIZUy_04Q1d1kDaisk1f3Ns=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered, we paid and among our food there were 4 ice creams.  They forced us to get them even when I stated at the checkout that I didn't want them for the start of our meal.  but another employee brought them and she told us that otherwise we would lose them.  She placed them on the table and this was the result.  we lost them in the end.  Report the complaint to the manager on Friday afternoon, exactly at 8:10 p.m.  She is a girl from the East.  She told me that he was required to receive the entire order at the time he received the burgers.  I didn't agree.  I think that in this restaurant this female manager lacks a lot of empathy and Christian values ‚Äã‚Äãof respect, consideration and kindness.  I hope this complaint gets where it needs to go.  I will also complain to consumer services.  Of course it's not the price of the ice cream, it's the poor customer service attitude.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLx5v6qvL8IoYwAp5AmCXRjpDNTMcuN7AjiQYA&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I pulled into this location just after the breakfast time deadline, which wasn‚Äôt a problem. My issue was that I noticed a lot of young people who park in the ordering parking stalls outside and walk across the street. Some got sushi, some got Chinese take out, some were delivery Uber drivers. It‚Äôs really unacceptable. I originally wanted to order in my car and drive somewhere to eat it. Since no spots were empty I decided to park and eat inside instead.

While I sat and ate next to the parking stalls I saw what was happening‚Ä¶ totally not fair. Students parking in these stalls and grabbing food elsewhere. This has to be controlled somehow. If I was a tow truck driver I would make thousands every hour.

As for the food, no issues.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkSLhdKh0i8cQEcvl12AggTIQO4exqu_02njEW&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Chris L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlo27yi0c3tMg1MEFW8gltVROJwlBrQGtk927fnMS7KkAAA0UJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Let's face it no one comes to McDonald's for outstanding food. We come here because it's FAST and as much as I would like to say inexpensive, that is no longer true (for the most part). The service was great, the gentleman at the counter was literally running to take orders and go to the back (kudos sir). The food was typical McDonald's. We ate inside the tables were gross, but once again McDonald's....what do you really expect here? Lots of parking as we came in late. The only issue I have is the people in the front parking lot of the entrance openly smoking drugs from a pipe. But I guess we can thank the city for that (guess this would fall under a different review lol). 4 stars for the service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkis4CGHIWYsEByrPS8as0PqRL3IBjPjV9Efz5&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"rwpow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMZHZZy8yLkw6tffki855GmumW3XF5y9VuOp9bQBP0R4GbNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was our first time visiting the location at 2909 Grandview Highway, so we ordered 2 McChicken Meals, 10 McNuggets, and 1 McFlurry and spent $38.01. I always ask for extra chicken sauce on the side for my sandwich and I also like to mix it with ketchup on my fries. I asked for three packs of McChicken sauce after paying as I had forgotten to ask at the till. The staff refused to give them to me, saying "We charge for extra sauce here. You need to line up and pay."and then abrubtly just turns away like I dont exist. I've been to McDonald's many times and never experienced such rude behavior from an employee. I waited and asked the manager or possibly supervisor, and got the same response. I had to wait in line again while my food was getting cold. I was disappointed that I had to pay for extra McChicken sauce. The approach could have been a lot better. For example, they could have said, "Sorry sir, we charge for McChicken sauce at this location. In the future, please pay at the till, but here is your McChicken sauce for today. Sorry about that."

OR POST AT THE TILL WE CHARGE FOR EXTRA CONDIMENTS??? CHEAP FRANCHISEE...

When I tried to get a Coke, both Coke machines were broken. The restaurant was out of CO2 and ice, but they were still charging customers for soda and not informing them of different options when you pay. THE SIGN DOESNT HELP AFTER YOU HAVE ALREADY PAYED TO HAVE COKE AND SHOULD READ SODA IS WARM, OUT OF ICE AND CO2 SO YOUR ONLY OPTION IS NESTEA...This was very disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWs9fTtzb9K_VI-mFVDqdebPJ1wmlHurzWvddS&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Val","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL56X75_5GhDC92ZZtK8vJ5hxr952_6qXAOBYpg77KeUE8I6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst. Took nearly 15 minutes just for a wrap and they forgot my side. The wrap was terrible, they couldn‚Äôt even wrap it up properly. When i tried it at a different location it tasted good and was wrapped nicely without rips in the tortilla from someones nails. Somehow the food was still cold and the hash brown tasted like it was sitting there for a while. Terrible food and service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOulvyxVbysEGw1VyEu9kZ7MI_37SVPnteNu64r&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"mimi d","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqIP2rCmimV685J_9PvvFYBGSnPQx-DcpjwtM0YUuJSfD3tz1lLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Probably the worst McDonalds location in Vancouver. The workers prioritize UberEats orders instead of customers that are patiently waiting in the drive thru/in the restaurant. The food quality and service has gone downhill in the past few months. I will not be returning to this location after dealing with rude employees and now finding a long curly hair wrapped around the fries. Ruined my family‚Äôs appetite.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZFS40qfo4HJ4_dWwnUFLIbNgCst1icOBVEd0I&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"karlee schinck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOUlDC5ZWZZYqyQNCRgpgxLb56MyU5FDD6fBsaLL2xjjUtOc8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a medium drink. they said they ran out of cups and that i still received a medium. Got home, found this old cup i had from the other day to see they‚Äôre clearly not the same size. the lady at the drive through window tried arguing with me when i told her it looked smaller. I don‚Äôt know why i keep giving this location a chance there is always something they screw up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhFFOMVpj-mau8VD7k8uZpEfvfaIJKZ5L4P1T3&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"phung pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPbfrHCpvzKVUr-D7nEtzNxkvlcXQr_EbAjiww4SBYRwVFAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service is fast and the food served is always fresh and hot. The self order checkout are easy to use and are always clean. The crew their is friendly and make sure that we understand what food we need and sometimes gives suggestions of what is better option. The dine in is cozy and wide especially in the sunshine it looks fabulous.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTvM1GB4lm00SA6xlRQqeRwXWvQJGVOWfBUoPN&fid=0x0:0x16951bac60d2aa3b"],"When":"2023-9-26"}]

At least here it is better quality non-medicated meat.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"silveryfeather208","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIV1DAc6oAZcKGUjDYKQfX3Js6BWSD-KkYIFsB6AYpaKFALg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm not sure if giving this one star will get the attention and I understand maybe they can't do anything. However I hope some managers see this.

First shout out to Simran (I didn't get a chance to get the spelling). she was a small woman (about my height too, and I consider myself small) I just simply wanted to use the washroom, but if I wasn't able that's fine..

Someone was in there for a long, long time. She knocked on the door telling then to get out. They didn't. Anyways the other washroom was broken and couldn't lock. So she stood by the door and let me use the washroom.

She went over and beyond in my opinion. Some would have said sorry can't help..and that would have been totally fine.

Anyways the place should fix the washrooms and also find a solution so that people don't stay in the washroom to do other things...","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aman Preet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWcfYcNGwVASRfWBeuODCGdxy8SxNydGrxv0z-KoRjifqqIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today me and my friends visited this restaurant to have our food . We ordered fries first and was thinking for the next order to place. When we were talking with the girl attending us at the front counter her colleague asked her to listen to another customer while we were talking to her and in very rude way . When we talked with the manager she was much more ruder. Instead of solving the problem she asked us to leave the store cause the team member is not comfortable with us. Means what ?? We are not the customers in ur store. We are paying for our meal so why showing us attitude.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Jaime Libby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWcuQUZBXxCRF5-27cV4MrzyteNpvh8tPhlqiQSMkU18wPjoAf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tacos are freaking amazing started with 4 of each kind had to get two more to try them all.
So freaking good!!!
The guy at the counter was so nice gave us water and cleaned up after us right away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPa-Rv7TmsmOO28limP0dDRaGe1qDWnlq10jR1k&fid=0x0:0x1425b0315edc6c06"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"AJ Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsu0-zLfdBIi0BMvFkmCrQ7LvpDpcqpsmyMO44b1viyR7y0ygy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An outstanding taco experience for sure. Decided to grab some tacos before the Weezer concert the other night and love the idea of Korean flavours in that format. Turns out, unsurprisingly, that it works really really well. The Korean flavours combined with the delivery of a taco was an experience That I will definitely, definitely do again!

I tried the Tako Taco and Gangnam Taco and both delivered with big flavours!

Also grabbed a Corona while I waited for my food cause it is busy being at the steps to the skytrain and right across from the arena!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMArRTOEJIiRszjFLgCEA4OoBwmJN73C6y0K9YQ&fid=0x0:0x1425b0315edc6c06"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Ryebread the White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYI7riSNbXzxJTj16rHlDS_OZW-ptOhXUz30OebmywxJ6z7_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Immaculate vibes. Wasn‚Äôt too busy when I went, staff were chatting and joking around with each other when no one was at the counter so you know they have fun at work. Food was delicious, pretty decent prices, and convenient spot by the skytrain. Will be back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObU2-Cpak7f_V8iCHywb2EsLTbCP5TyxDspZEU&fid=0x0:0x1425b0315edc6c06"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"A L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDuox32jyJxnkzAm48h5i9Ht66Z7AvtkXQcQV08flbS_JcS1Q6eQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A nice little eatery, conveniently located across from Rogers Arena and right next to the sky train station. The service was stellar! Very friendly and attentive staff.

The chipotle chicken burrito bowl was REALLY good! The spicy pork and beef short rib tacos were lacking an element - a sauce of some sort would take it to the next level. The spicy chicken taco and fried shrimp taco were significantly better than the other two.

I'll definitely be back! Perfect meal pre-game or pre-concert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlCRIy0m04ppJJ5NKb6AemtPXwq0GySUoJdJOW&fid=0x0:0x1425b0315edc6c06"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"Melina Faraone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGhWF6SDip0uRHcGmkbqvOFFL9wrSZJxAX1vssrjjh_8lBuKut=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place has great service and friendly staff, the cashier even brought us waters to the table even though it‚Äôs a fast place. The food is interesting but not bad. They had plenty of vegetarian options; there was at least one vegetarian option in each section. The tofu is sweet though, it‚Äôs the same type used for inari. I think the burrito & bowl would have been better with a different type of tofu. The quesadilla was fine but I couldn‚Äôt really taste the kimchi, and it has mushrooms too which was interesting but not bad really.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWvg5rcNNUekJW3FNSzy8_cu8zUv1eJWF-WEiy&fid=0x0:0x1425b0315edc6c06"],"When":"2023-7-12"},{"Name":"Angie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsm7lUHZmUGaGdcX8lFwvk_tgCxCRZArqbngkcHl5FANnfbBEm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Soo good. Only had the rice cake skewers (so far), but will definitely buy again! I was a happy camper. The chicken was hot and crispy. Juicy af inside. They counted the pieces right.

Thank you. I worked 16 hours straight and some other location couldn‚Äôt even count 4 pieces of chicken correctly and it was cold..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_0tsEGvyKVc62g04E3C1c8BVs-oFlsGPVhiR6&fid=0x0:0x26b48e437a501134"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Victor Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpnZPh7heLHnvp3JcjErTq9VzUaFB6LA67FBNyLyGHNyq0kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was the Church's Chicken I grew up with. I have fond memories of grandma walking with my sister and I to this restaurant to pick up a box of fried chicken.

The exterior has had a face-lift, but the inside layout has not changed. The booths are gone, and the framed picture of the audience eating Church's Chicken at the filming of Rocky is not there anymore.

I picked up some fried chicken and fries. It's just how I remembered. I told my childhood story to my little one as we munched on the chicken tougher. Grandma would be happy to know I'm keeping the tradition alive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONg-LmMJYdyqlEXNQrhhn2rfDPAomiMDNO7dOh&fid=0x0:0x26b48e437a501134"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"VAI N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKl2tExvfM-zR39DXNqefS2F9zaLSF3RPNblVO4wWjjsIBKsYZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The experience here has been terrible. The drink was lukewarm rather than hot, and it didn't have much flavor‚Äîalmost watery and lacking that rich chocolate taste","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shane Zwicker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaCQEJyGH7QxDCbzqSWBRvYrFswSlI7pb4-us8lO0AiWdEUNrV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Understaffed for how busy it is, and paid almost 10$ for a 6$ breakfast, just cuz I wanted hot chocolate in my coffee, and lettuce and tomato on my sandwich. And apparently 'regular' lettuce at this McDonald's is one half wilted leaf..

They were nice enough to provide me with proper lettuce after I complained, but there should really be some baseline standards.

Lotta people complaining about the homeless, but they mostly don't bother you if you don't bother them. Might get one asking you for spare change on your way in/out, but that's no diff than anywhere else in Vancouver. It's an issue with our society, not this McDonald's. But they do need to focus on food quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTuBah1fYNyu7QNNp3bHrdpv1IIBtc5veLZhL8&fid=0x0:0xfa4e2ebd3629478f"],"When":"2023-8-27"},{"Name":"J. Au","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK35GdM6kuQCV6VM_jE-3a56cYJvY6OqgV28tMgxT3m98_ErA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Pick up orders only after 10 which is fine, but I looked at the employee straight to the face and asked if there was a straw in the bag. They have good deals on the app in the ‚Äúoffers‚Äù section, I just wish they didn‚Äôt take out the 3 piece chicken tenders meal from the ‚Äúoffers‚Äù on the app.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Agnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyqJcbJDbElC-RwU1sBP46by6tVeVGdJmv6s9B0kjpjwDghjdVVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The only location that's in Vancouver area. We had a pulled pork sandwich and buffalo chicken sandwich. Sandwiches were good, lots of filling and meat wasn‚Äôt dry. I wish the bread was toasted(?) or toasted more if it was. The bread and meet here is very unique and taste surprisingly good. I'm not a huge fan of pork and beef but here its seems a lot lighter and it taste good. All and all my friends and I really enjoyed this place it had great people working there a great modern environment and great food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM485j53Rd-zLYjuIlwk287H34166sMf4QszTRS&fid=0x0:0x52ea3321a3400e5e"],"When":"2018-7-25"},{"Name":"candy L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgq2OgnXFRsC1icGye-CTgUf_6kEV0cPoOgzI7ANMes5eDT-Xz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great first visit to Meat & Bread for a quick lunch. They offered a variety of sandwiches, and the Porchetta looked particularly tempting. However, since I recently switched to a diet that only includes white meat, I opted for the Buffalo Chicken sandwich. The staff was very patient and helpful when I asked about the ingredients, and they were also friendly and nice. The chicken was tender and flavorful, and the bread was fresh and soft. I also had a small kale salad with a light, but tasty dressing. The restaurant had a simple, but pleasant decor and was spacious. I will definitely be returning to Meat & Bread again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBrQD6DCXxCunPwBtFjA4uNlzRIkP6XGyIcb8N&fid=0x0:0x52ea3321a3400e5e"],"When":"2023-1-7"},{"Name":"Moj Noroozi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXugascUb1Fko0SBjm9NLiM6IJLmrr73V93pNQAUcsSq60KoCcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Meat & bread is like a gem in Vancouver ! The Porchetta sandwich is an absolute delight ‚Äî the flavors are rich, and every bite is a savory experience that leaves a lasting impression. Pairing it with their hearty soups, especially during the winter, is a winning combination that warms both the body and the soul.
The bread, consistently super fresh, elevates every dish to a new level.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNu2Fz2_OHEywQR22A4rceJaGhy_qsdrPJ1uVZN&fid=0x0:0x52ea3321a3400e5e"],"When":"2023-12-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Bilal Ittiq","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmM3Tz8zf6lCUcrlwScQdw4OJc7hGY3PEyol7xYyX0QgESJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderfully tasty food, incredible service, and casual ambiance!

We got some double slap smash burgers, tandoori chicken burgers, fries, and a BBQ chicken pizza. The smash burgers were some of the best we've had anywhere! The patties were surprisingly large for a smash burger and we liked the veggies to brighten it up. Tandoori chicken burger was vibrant, flavorsome, and texturally diverse. And speaking of textures, the sesame seeds on the BBQ chicken pizza crust was a welcome surprise!

Would highly recommend all around. Plus it was made by someone who was very passionate about the food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJMFo2GCRj3VtHtEIpCA8XcqsjfiRURNOFS0Al&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Holly Woosey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV2lbZeCEe9uk_tp5v5HeEBpd05cOkWx2bWGKGCFJqdBVjRakcIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place! We had the smash burger, chopped cheese and fries. All of it was so delicious and huge portion for the price! Would really like to come back and try the pizza. Staff was so friendly and helpful and I love to see a place doing a good clean of the fryer air vents, shows they're really thorough because the rest of the place was spotless! Will definitely be back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFA_6hIhYnmJm-o6WZB6lms4cHVJtYG4YBg2LO&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great fast food joint. The double smash patty burgers were absolutely amazing. Large side of fries. Will be visiting again to try the philly steak sandwiches and pizzas next.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1g9MVRFSOXNC9TTIaaUD0POYaJxjfm1v-IHJQ&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Robert Caron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_EpFhprcf3SG2KOeJLn_ZMvns4ZouCijKUxtpaECokzRyVf_o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An outstanding experience. Food looks superlatively good. It's good, too. Service is all-star. A top spot to have a bite. Maybe they could cut down on salt--50% less salt would be plenty of salt--but it doesn't take away from what a cool place that is.

No toilets so bring your can.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBMTdobGrC53LfZyAhZuBhh0UZyJHF3zLlXY8L&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Asif Isma'il","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxLUnk5V8QOVNW7l2QfoX-wuZT96kaVDaH_-0nbv_f3LT4G5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good food for value. The burgers were juicy and the pizza had a great thin crispy crust. Fries were a bit too salty but were still fresh and crispy.

Service was over the top, Ahsan was amazing. He was very helpful in suggesting what to order and had great product knowledge. He made everything from the scratch for us and his customer service etiquette was top notch.

It was very hot inside and since the main door was kept open, it was very noise. Otherwise, a great place to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMY_QRWl6WE0LCisqgqG5NQyviSfzQYewJFUjIi&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Emmanuel Mor√∫a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVgDDr7Bq5maIJYTC_on0x6OlVE8ViM6rt1o7JGzQMU2HdiVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff is super friendly, place is spotless clean, variety of food is great and smash burgers are DELICIOUS and super cheap comparing to most of other ones in the surrounding areas. Can‚Äôt wait to come back. 10/10 easily on smash burgers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPN8jfpVA-LeSxfrzD7G0Wr5VBjKKRUAYi5uqTj&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Ken B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi0UHEqvrtK9b7zXvBSni89V4qdFRQmlmzKuNqGFJ9iPTWGGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the double smash burger and cheesesteak. The cheesesteak was good, meat and veggies were perfectly cooked, the bun was warm and steamed. They added a lot of beef to the sandwich. I would definitely come back for the smash burger though. Everything is as expected for a really good smash burger, Pattie‚Äôs were thin and crisp but still wide after being cooked. Cheese perfectly melted, nice warm toasted buns. But what makes this place unique is the burger sauce, it‚Äôs almost like a white donair sauce but not garlicy, just a nice rich and creamy taste. They do also add greens which slightly cuts the richness and saltiness of the cheese so it‚Äôs well balanced.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOodFqMrite7Lte3kDpKX64_mApFWq03xePEQT8&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Joey Carter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVxJhmegLxZTiNK1kFjGHgDdGo3bbkfdT-9_i2VmsPV6_ZjTD9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered a single slap burger...
DELICIOUS....
Food is tasty and the selection is not too big which is great..
They'd do much better if they utilize what space they do have...
Great food great location and great service..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIw1pcCYq5Y39U6pzjDQ8k9lnR_d5rNtPkCQKN&fid=0x0:0x40deb8562d998000"],"When":"2024-8-28"}]

[{"Name":"T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuLCrwKa9NLpGvoI7KXeamb10EWAoAmRoPxgdu96hyYHG6mtPkhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had the Felix. It was very tasty! The sausage was nicely cooked and the sauerkraut was very good. I added a little bit of Caesar Ketchup to mine. I found the portion size to be a bit small; the sausage itself wasn't very big and there was a small handful of chips provided. Otherwise there was a nice variety of sauces to choose from, and the bun I believe was steamed? It was a nice touch. I opted to take mine to go. The neighborhood is a bit rough, so it wasn't a great environment for sitting inside and facing the windows looking outside while eating lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMukv6WxuTBPCVZ-zxWLrqP8L1c6WdAxg9AJsFs&fid=0x0:0x5c1dae8b81414831"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a small bratwurst restaurant that sells tasty fusion hotdogs. The owner was very friendly and we loved the cozy but fun and quirky atmosphere. I don't think they have a bathroom, unfortunately, but they did have a sink where you can wash your hands because they will get dirty. The hotdog is filled to the brim with sauces and toppings with fantastic bratwurst sausage. The potato chips also give a nice crunch and texture which I appreciate. We also tried their pretzel and the garlic aioli sauce. They were good but we couldn't finish because the portion is quite large and the food can be a bit heavy. If you're looking for some delicious bratwurst with some modern twist, this is the place for you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvjznguN6hWu1FxIMKIs38OXoSSWzpweOIo1co&fid=0x0:0x5c1dae8b81414831"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Braeden Tang-Munn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnFfxhsHu8UCok_-GHb8K7ZblJL3rC8F4AOFCTF1XyKzAStFIS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"100% would go again! Everything is $14 each and the brats were awesome and the milkshake was SO good!!

They also offer multiple combos so it‚Äôs a perfect spot to go with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYultn6gw16oaSOZKnGvk5NLefmXbHPQRVT4NL&fid=0x0:0x5c1dae8b81414831"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Emilio Dalmasi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbw4uhSmcLTsHVoZjn_wtU8fOgBACpODae6DJaJpfCNwHGj90=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best hot dogs that I have been try ever.
Amazing!!
Also the shakes.
The place is really friendly, perfect for a family, a couple if you wanna have a fun date, or just a single one. They also have a game machine like pac man too.
Love it","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melisa Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhlFUkHJtdvNfxN4zXzQ_tF66YFk9ySyx_Fe6dkHmy02nmbTl5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been here twice. The staff is friendly...will definitely be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjErnBKSucldt7LDnCi2MRHC5GKyl9iVwtz3Zn&fid=0x0:0x5c1dae8b81414831"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Lawren Medina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDSFY-GkR4z1Vh0GsrkX1b_BqzeGeZ6snXO1OwyDWlqFLkKTo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best hot dog I've had in all of Vancouver, honestly I was so surprised at how fresh everything was and the place is beautiful with excellent service.

The milkshakes are amazing, I think it will be my new favorite place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Â∑ùÂè£ÁïôÁæé","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5bP7WQuYrhbfX171aDiOMc96eEPSGPErtU-velHIH2y3-iA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had Felix, Robin and Pretzel. [{"Name":"Max Wei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVV4V5LOJincdLvSBEOpEdMPwxXtLcYa8ZnIBqIVLI1U-SOrk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great price for tasty Japanese food.

The freshly fried Katsu slices were thoughtfully laid on top of the curry on top of rice so each piece was half soaked in curry flavour and half crispy deliciousness.

Pickled radish were a super tasty complement as well. By the end it felt a bit greasy but for the price it can't be beat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPw-OrCC909ckZkLMsK_QLIJZKCH6IXDIOxKz4&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Justin Tai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmjoRldcLvxYOLF_D--KetVrYfTM9h1TH-SST5ofi51r5ypg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simple and tasty takeout place with some seating for dinning in. I had the chicken teriyaki bowl and it didn't disappoint. The chicken with skin on was very tender and the mayo (or some white sauce) added a nice flavour. It's not the cheapest takeout but the portion and quality are good. They don't have tons of options on the menu (which isn't always a bad thing) but they also have some small grab-and-go snacks available. Service was efficient.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUmINrLg9Yg8xguTQs3wVBz6_hlmRGb8CmLJQF&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Dana Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQIw-0oOUNgoyniYugTscGkgpKJS8tpx4V0tAajn3ZGkNIfqEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Japanese fast food featuring tempura bowls and curry, also some desserts. In general I don‚Äôt love deep-fried foods but sometimes I like tempura, so I gave this a try.
Ordered the ten don - prawns (4) and vegetable (green beans and 1 pc sweet potato) on rice. The batter was light and crispy but on the oiler side for tempura. I personally would‚Äôve traded one of the prawns for more vegetables, but I was happy with the portion size. Overall nothing memorable but not bad.
I also grabbed a pudding cup (from Cake Ya, a local producer of Japanese desserts), which was good - their desserts are high quality and taste fresh even though they‚Äôre packaged.
Service was okay - reasonably fast. The restaurant including the washroom were very clean. I like that they use real bowls for dining in even though it‚Äôs kind of a fast food place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMP0cBWOVHveu5-LUu60XZqzPmHZzaIr7MFus6S&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Boe Didiet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdBK1PLnUOoZ3JtuVrLyCfOSB8_Dbyru9eZVBLWZvVixPptnft=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place. Most authentic Japanese curry in this area. I recommend this place! And best part is NO TIPPING!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3YbFQh9MTMVvW-6PpBMwy2MPLevLl56qIJBE3&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Mehr Poulad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnMmsASCmXLOvaFhR1RoQ03vxNx7oVUBdwy_npEYvb7k7uZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located right across from the central library. Busy at lunch time and they have a few premade options for cheap, $4.95 a bowl.
I ordered the double meat curry. Overall decent amount of food and value. There would have been more sauce on the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTyw86DlrC3uWVwtB9Z60rg51H5-MhCjZ2qHGW&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"tchanrosewood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC64U64VrSCF27_m6UWKr2pkewS1XLecdgQJR_wnS4fgKAclE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick bite before going to caps game. Pork katsu and octopus ball was good. We were able to sit at a table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfXO12zsANibhKprPUNeoBC93flNwAWeoRUSCX&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Liya An","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQysOJkxkiiOntvX-KisSfKBFDI83H1lePmSWHEXGVgxMHu7Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got a take-out order of yakisoba, and the taste was so bad. The vegetables were too salty, but the noodles had no taste at all and were too bland. I have no idea what kind of yakisoba this is, and it really didn't taste good. I don't know about other dishes, but I don't recommend this dish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB2aJzp6-W_dnnvVSsT-TxsIuDHvho4YapP35F&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Robert Caron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_EpFhprcf3SG2KOeJLn_ZMvns4ZouCijKUxtpaECokzRyVf_o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cutlet of choice. Very good, good presentation, good service. The meat was super crispy and tasty, the rice was excellent, and the curry on the side was succulent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_CX39FJJ6jMOtixX_DL4GE7KTmVpJJ4sEQtGJ&fid=0x0:0xb8c6c0d820f60e24"],"When":"2024-10-18"}]

[{"Name":"alice w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfBFd5-MCz0iWhHQjADA6mFZoHPhSAyoSlVDQe971OUgYbxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good just little be busy the girls is little be rush from downtown one not like west Pork Road one anyway still very good üòä or the tables is not so clean may be because they are too busy for orders","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPd5sjsKBTukMviVbtvCLmA0rMbwvCLd4jTmIdI&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Shubham Negi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnhh2wk9ebN6O61plkpRyfS8-KTAHB_891ukmoshNsHWSRsXGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Popeyes during my recent visit. I was there to pick up an order for a friend, but since I don‚Äôt eat chicken and wasn‚Äôt familiar with the menu, I wasn‚Äôt sure what to get. Fortunately, the employee Gurleen was incredibly helpful. She patiently walked me through the menu, explained the different options, and made sure I chose something that my friend would enjoy. Her friendly and knowledgeable service made the whole process so much easier for me. I really appreciated the effort she put in to help me out. It's not often that you come across such dedicated customer service, and I left the store feeling very satisfied. Thank you, Gurleen, and Popeyes, for a great experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNwyS1NYr9HDEONHuklsdPKym08VJ0gv7fZ9va&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Octavio Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULTqViu9lDQGaaJM8w5vXMYgPZ-NnCcvjO2ukbusXrWuFeXErJ3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Popeye's is one of many fried chicken chains that have recently opened in Vancouver lately. They are expanding in a market that includes many styles (Japanese, Korean, etc.) and, therefore, flavours. But the demand for fried chicken is obviously there, so they will probably do well in this city. This location, in particular, is right on the entertainment strip on Granville St. and this guarantees foot traffic. This time, I tried their Blackened Chicken Sandwich and Cajun Fries combo. It's not cheap at $14, but there's nothing cheap these days. Overall, it was a decent meal. The chicken is flavourful, not overly greasy. The fries are crisp and very tasty. For drinks, they are limited. Only your typical 5-6 soda flavours in the machine. The service was friendly. My order was served within minutes of placing it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgiPbinX5H_J9jIC_JCSLaeqqjpsqoz7VziTEy&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Prabhjot Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKs6pUhqTFsrFygVQlzBLUiRjOh5G3qsyArHHJfXfdh_63yQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I visited Popeyes for the third time with my friends, and I have to say, it was a bit of a mixed experience. The front counter girl (unfortunately, I didn‚Äôt catch her name) was doing her best to handle the rush on her own. My friend had placed an order, and it seemed like she needed some help, possibly from the manager who was busy making burgers. It was unclear whether she asked for assistance and got denied, but she was clearly left to handle the front alone.
After a while, a Sardar gentleman stepped in to help her, and honestly, he did an excellent job. Both of them managed the increasing crowd with impressive patience and efficiency. I could see how stressed she was, and she even apologized for the wait times, but really, it wasn‚Äôt her fault. The poor girl was doing everything she could, and I commend her for staying calm under pressure.
More power to both of them for managing the rush so well despite the lack of support from the management. It's a shame that the manager wasn‚Äôt stepping up to help, but at least those two crew members made the experience much better than it could have been. I‚Äôm giving 3 stars, and it's really more for those two staff members‚Äîthank you for your hard work and dedication. Management definitely needs to look into improving staff support, especially during busy hours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zephyr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi0Xbpfu6tRkPw0IoGrJ0CmwuI_fq3bZplujLoTo1QVvPthPHi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"There are many homeless, people smoking tobacco and marijuana, and people with abnormal behaviour lying around this popeyes location.

The environment in the store is acceptable, and the two waitresses were very enthusiastic in introducing us to the meals in the store.

However, when I was about to order, a male waiter with an unfriendly attitude and a particularly cold expression (from my personal opinion) took my order, so the ordering process was not very satisfying. In terms of ingredients, the surface of the fried chicken is very crispy and the chicken is juicy, but there is a smell of oil consumption that is not very fresh.

Overall, I would give two stars for the quality of the fried chicken outside and inside the store and the service of the service staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcnyR0R6bi2Ij3tOVcURxKOZR3-I5ktl2AirWu&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"sally kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCHzN-w99DgNXkVusEbH18VwLXtLVrHqCtM2TMEnP5zlSB8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful place! Food was delicious I recommended the strawberry cream cheese pie so much!! Service was amazing fast and efficient! Love!!! üíû","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgiPdCccE_VdFpKBY-xiRY69_h9TFq7WRqwbFs&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We like popeyes but this location is one of worst, we ordered 12 boneless and the chicken wasn‚Äôt crunchy, bland and the sauce was in the corner of the plate, the location doesn‚Äôt helps as well, thankfully there‚Äôs a security guard inside the restaurant, but a man that was drugged come in and start to yell, sadly is very common to see this all over granville street.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPU1S4RIx-vxZ4tuPsvlEkg2E9qPHMjP5IL9tLd&fid=0x0:0xe2ec76441d7944ba"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Phiebie Ancheta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFr4BoYmI704lH4BkWTbTBCKutNkzQS53m4Pslf1sxlh4HbUEkRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Popeyes Louisiana Kitchen recently. The food was hot and freshly prepared, with the signature crispy chicken living up to the hype. The staff was friendly and efficient, making the ordering process smooth and quick and I was pleasantly surprised by the exceptional service I received from one of the staff members named Simret. That girl at the counter was not only friendly but also incredibly attentive even at the rush hours. It‚Äôs clear she takes pride in her work, and her positive attitude really stood out. I left with a smile and a delicious meal, thanks for the outstanding service. This kind of customer care truly makes a difference! which added to the overall positive atmosphere. This visit definitely left me craving more!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Greg G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGCjvgLeSqHFdj_hNub_-erIP2qYUnonMeEG5i2akrj6InP0xqig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I placed an order via the app at a location by my work. The location says it's open at 0700.  I arrived at the location at 0715, but the lights were off. The lights came on at 0720, and I approached the counter. A lady from withing yelled "0730" ... I inquired about my order, she said "0730" ... I took this as her saying they weren't open. I said that the app indicated that they were open, she replied "no, the foldcourt hours aren't the same as ours".... I repeated that the McDonald's app said that there were open, she said I was wrong.  I walked away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3RhlIgl7sfnt8eNbvLiRxJfrkCr6N8K_JYsrx&fid=0x0:0x2eeb89f07c710dc8"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Geng Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5NGNe35D-FNwVhkS-BITODotekcdfkMaGBLfAB86fJ0ymkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went to pick up my mobile takeout order and was handed off a tray, I asked the order to-go and the woman looked at me with a sneer in her face and told me that I didn't "punch in" a bag, oh, I didn't know that you need to pay for a paper bag in Mcdonald's nowadays. You got me right there girl, I am happy that I made your day with the amount of proud and provocation I saw in that face you were making we almost looked at each other for a good minute as if you were expecting me to make a fool of myself for that paper bag. I am sure you will do just as good in the macdonald's of your home nation when your student visa expires, keep up the good work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ravinder Chaudhary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKhmXK2pWGpbybeljvPO3YuTKzKIJO-qeuNlo9HsY9wffFXg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited this McDonald‚Äôs frequently,  i usually place my order through mobile app but recently my app was not working and placed order by visiting , if i am not wrong manager name HARVEER shouted badly on one of the cashier and girl on till was about to cry at moment control emotions and completes taking order , managers should be respectful arleast towards their crew members , its important to work efficiently as a team.
Coffee also taste like a water.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cosmo Kwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJB4JsBwE0uCK4wKlZRN8M9a3Yh3TUSvDluKgY2A2xaYEGmCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Peach Pie is amazing good! Especially when its cold ( fridge for few hours ). Very peachy fillings and tasty. Loved this pie!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Ao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkBvZ6ce_zHnWsLqA5ojfX0nMQ_CDE0WIX5k8yhZ46T8a1BLiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"If you're looking for a quick, cheap meal, McDonald's is a decent option. The french fries were okay, but the chicken burger was actually pretty good. However, the sodas are really flat and there's no option to get a refill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVaAI4itPKWRK4E6G3Wpb08pQEwOw3iSOaFSqE&fid=0x0:0x2eeb89f07c710dc8"],"When":"2023-8-27"},{"Name":"Jim McDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrSPJ6-hPNlFv7xM1mxcBlq3c1uYOsonwfSRyKMMDsF2ELLMs9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I work on the block so I am here pretty often. It's a Food Court McDonald's so the bar is already pretty low and I have come to terms with that being part of the arrangement on convenience.

But there is only so long you can line up and just accept that you will get what you get.

I've noticed in the last several months, they have prompted their cashiers to start peppering the customers with questions. Are you collecting points with the app? NO. How many ketchups do you want? NONE. How many napkins? TWO. I don't blame the cashiers, I don't think they have a choice, but now, asking me what type of pop I am going to get? What difference does it make? You are handing me an empty cup, you can press whatever button you want, it doesn't matter. Unless you are going to come around and fill it up for me, you don't need to know. I might take one shot of each of the pops, I might eat the cup, who knows!

The straw that broke the camel's back for me was tonight though. I have had too many warm cokes because they can't keep the ice machine running. I'm standing there, like an idiot, pressing my cup against the handle waiting for ice and nothing. I asked the supervisor if they have anything back there, ice in a jug, crushed ice, anything that would save me from a warm drink. NOPE, apparently they have to truck the ice in from across the food court somewhere and she needs to find someone to go get it.

What a mess. This place was already circling the drain on service, but now I can't even depend on them for ice. I suppose this is a positive for me, I'll put in more steps walking somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"waiseelay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJ2XykLfvOzPJLYfcQwvC7J29VBlgXDbnhih3JP-D9YOvMT6SleA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This location is super convenient, and they're fast. But I often get frustrated with this place because the app never seems to work at this location specifically for some reason. Also, I tried to use one of the coupons here today and they simply told me they can't take it cause there's a system issue. That's not their fault, but really? The manager can't do ANYthing about this? No solution, just simply nope, try again tomorrow. Wasn't too happy with that.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mariena Bui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6Nw1jeBXne8haJacgZytBHrMEqU2gmOMAF3l5QWK0CwO3rXPJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were quick and efficient with making the food here. I only had to wait for like 4 minutes and the food was nice and hot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjtiA8K7Yn8zFI9EHGutnYCMGgNpr6bqWeSBP4&fid=0x0:0x2eeb89f07c710dc8"],"When":"2024-4-1"}]

I think if you're comparing to Alberta all McDonald's in BC working great - I'm still shocked.
If you'll find source of smell and reduce it, big improvement guaranteed. Good place for getting your fast food.

Save yourself the trouble and order elsewhere...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiitwF84cZcySDYGputupSdV8SI9vgvBwWRCsh&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"A super let down, I was stoked from the look of this vegan friendly falafel salad bowl. It's a shame as Donair Dude is expanding round Van and this is a sweet location. The server was also mostly on her cell. It was really tasty. The fries were super crispy, and they had a promotion on falafel wraps for Tuesday‚Äîonly $6.99 for a large size, which is fabulous. Thanks to all the staff for working hard!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDOYb8OukeXYE160cBEog_UU6SqKSMwcpT1pI&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Ginn J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFOOQZPhZylsgMOLmtSB5bJOkt-NwtAZ31Ulkb5_TUEpijBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been going here for years.  We like it enough to detour to pick up donars on our way to or from downtown.

They have some different options, we have only had the donars.  It's a large wrap with lots of toppings and the sauces and spreads you choose.

You can see the meat and veggies in the pictures.

I have a secret that make mine amazing!  I ask for them to add sauce between the veggies and meat instead of after.  Then I get extra tzatziki again after the meat.

I LOVE the sauce and find it makes the whole thing amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoVQivfJifYxMl9MHem5HxA8kW7tz_rDqJoIKv&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Uros Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqZKUGj61BfmTYu8vecdYC7cNoaJsQnfWJB3zipm50mUOPG3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my favourite place for picking up food. Everything is always fresh I even saw a couple of times when they are checking level of moisture for salad and temperature of meats.
My recommendation from menu would be Chicken and Lamb shawarma
I highly suggest you to try this restaurant üëåüèº","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMgKBWff15It3wNY0cES-7ZuHdvio_TIte1SeF&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Benson Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtBEfS9X_MJW7bxqD13ohJeGd5V9EZSiM8mSElst7WCoP6sbO4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The staff were friendly and the food tasted good but the portions were disappointing.  Usually when i get a donair it's stuffed full.  This was not.  They were skimpy on the meat esp for the beef one.  We paid $8 for a small poutine and it was very small.  It was like a small McDonald's fries portion.  We had a much better experience here before, big portions that time but this was definitely disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNL1Pol5OqL0kg685v8apFbV4szhkwrqPq4j__Z&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2024-1-15"},{"Name":"Sam Hemas (Sam)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjwSH6Yo6LPnaOOzgQirLYeyYJeI_qJ3i3ipqb8xIgC_pC3DNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lamest donair you‚Äôll ever have. Came home from a long day of work only to get a double-layered rap of pita bread that I could‚Äôve made at home too. Called the restaurant and they didn‚Äôt even offer any credit, only mentioning that upon my next purchase they‚Äôd give me extra chicken. No thanks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6YlLcQaZwJcHKNQ6UYkF3UYOH9AXAsHcgBA9_&fid=0x0:0xa90405ecf82ff9d8"],"When":"2024-7-4"}]

As far as I‚Äôm concerned, this Burger King location owes me a full refund for a burger that was INEDIBLE.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa3Yjgi-VMBQj6NPJtJnS33c2i-WukchIKRjPs&fid=0x0:0xff9d38d06a11f8ce"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Johnny boi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqRygOl0JhZvs2tqIvAsSOOYy4obRJEyJ4d49S7DVYx8PR9JQVAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"All right I know it's the fireworksAll right I know it's the fireworks but when I got inside no one was ordering food ...July 24th 2004 On this day at 9:00 p.m.There was no one in the lineup I saw the poster say Whopper WednesdayI asked her how much is a WhopperWhopper Wednesday she said it doesn't start till next weekWhy would they put up a poster for Whopper Wednesday if it didn't start yetSo I don't know why there would be a poster up anyways it was$8.86 for one WhopperWhen I refused and walked away she said how about a junior WhopperIt's $5 less...I don't know how this can be a franchise Burger King if they're not going to order honor the promotionsAnd the poster doesn't have any date so how do I know it starts next weekI'dI I thought I beat the line and I was like what's a chance of theirI thought I beat the line and I was like what's a chance of their knowI thought I beat the line","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNocfJVE1E9qCB50agRXKmAZEYecvjufrhlEKJA&fid=0x0:0xff9d38d06a11f8ce"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Darcey Middleton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-2CBq4NBSY7uSN2n3CsTuEbL2tPyNKqZr_wQHZdBYKXGsZdA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Honey average this is a good place to get a meal if you want to stop in and grab a seat. It also tends to be the cheaper places of all the places around to eat. For as far as a fast food restaurant it's a so-so this meaning that sometimes you can taste the oil because I don't think they recyclic enough. Also it seems that they neglect cleaning things a little bit more than some of the other restaurants. But generally if you're looking for a very quick bite to eat cuz you've got to get on and do things with your life that's okay it'll do in a pinch","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cody Gurash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhAjV9iLKzoJQKzWSEo8m7kVLvzFbWp_FPgFQ-hRIEGiN2qfI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I honestly don‚Äôt know why I keep coming back to this Burger King location. I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôve had a single positive experience here. Tonight was the final straw. The ‚ÄúOpen‚Äù sign was still on, the door was unlocked, so I walked in‚Äîonly to be shouted at by three employees telling me they were closed. The blaring neon sign outside clearly gave me the wrong impression.

I should‚Äôve stopped coming after a previous experience when a piece of the drink dispenser fell into my cup while I was pouring a drink. I notified an employee, and their ‚Äúsolution‚Äù was to fish the part out of my cup, screw it back in, and walk away without a word.

If you want to avoid long waits for food even when the place is empty, or rude and careless service, I‚Äôd recommend going elsewhere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tania Mardani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWggPCicA3a-P1_DPXV5NcQqXv6ocr6c9-SbjTTzkecRu3tHVu6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible experience such bad service i ordered a whopper meal and asked for half onion rings and half fries and barely got anything and when i asked to put more they said thats the size and started rolling their eyes. Literally got 9 fries and 3 onion rings and apparently thats the size? And my friend got 2x the fries and onion rings. My friend is indian and im white idk if it has to with race or something but dont come here at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTnsTtCrKY8qu_XmI-M4dVd394_mNnKpG9jVfP&fid=0x0:0xff9d38d06a11f8ce"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Abigail Stephanie Y√°nez Haro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSkEeebx6Pv2LMbK2HcwEgG80ouW5BDwu3nn-hxOPBqaY-rA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you go to buy something there, double check your food, as customer I trust in the quality of the food provided by this kind of restaurant, I never expect when I open my food for enjoy it find this surprise, actually this is pretty dangerous for me or anybody who eat this, I could be poisoned by this sandwich.

One recommendation also for people who is working there,care your customers and their health, I am really upset to find this, because is pretty obvious that the mold in the pan means that pan is old, how many items did you put in the food of your customers that already were bad and also, because when I went to buy there you weren‚Äôt busy so you must to check the quality of everything always, even if you are busyüò° you should be ashamed for give that food to your customers.

So disappointed and upset with you #BurguerKing team üò°.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON2oyo7jcVDDuyJrCALIFJLLxBwoUEvCdRYyzH&fid=0x0:0xff9d38d06a11f8ce"],"When":"2023-10-28"},{"Name":"Gooseberry Bilberry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMJD-L9WmQytMhbODZNa3Nz3Kk8Z3fxnupE5Xvb8JG11rhZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The chocolate milkshake was just melted vanilla ice-cream with warm chocolate syrup (it was watery). user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Taha Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvkg4h5sHYdPTTUvMGr5Ud3Br1PeSfw04_pdtFZLfwqdlzD0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal‚Äîthese words barely scratch the surface of our experience. We placed our order in the early hours, around 3 a.m., and were astounded by the freshness of the food. The chicken and Philly cheesesteaks were exceptional‚Äîpiping hot, deliciously flavorful, and mood-enhancing. The crispy chicken wrap was a revelation, tantalizingly mouthwatering. This gem of a shack is an essential visit for anyone in Vancouver. I'm eagerly looking forward to my next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOW0iwLaIia-5zZRXfLYedMlhnZL7ZczD5sgI_V&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Ahmad Awais","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKCENA3EQDxfNwGRkIzdwRQJIr8-nzzvbQk_P3TVWN1UAiJIKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At the heart of downtown Vancouver, Rao Burger Shack stands out as a must-visit spot for burger enthusiasts, especially those in search of an exceptional Philly Cheese Chicken Steak. My recent experience at this establishment was notably impressive, blending great taste with attentive service in a way that merits a detailed review.

Firstly, the food quality at Raoul Burger Shack is top-notch. The Philly Cheese Chicken Steak, in particular, deserves praise. It's a well-constructed dish featuring tender chicken, a spicy sauce that adds just the right kick without overpowering, and cheese that brings a creamy balance to the mix. All these elements are tucked into a bun that's soft yet resilient enough to hold everything together until the last bite. Additionally, their halal-friendly menu is a significant plus, catering to a broader audience and ensuring that more people can enjoy their offerings.

The service at Raoul Burger Shack adds to the overall positive experience. Suhail and Awais were the staff members who attended to me during my visit. Their approach to customer service was practical and focused on efficiency, ensuring that my meal was enjoyable without any unnecessary fuss. They were attentive and helpful, demonstrating a clear understanding of the menu and the ability to make recommendations tailored to customer preferences.

The ambiance of Raoul Burger Shack is another point worth noting. It's clean, with a straightforward layout that prioritizes comfort and convenience. Focus remains on the food and the service, aligning with what one would expect from a pragmatic and efficiently run shop.

In essence, Raoul Burger Shack delivers where it matters: high-quality, delicious food, efficient and friendly service, and a welcoming atmosphere for dining. Their Philly Cheese Chicken Steak is a standout option that I highly recommend to anyone visiting or living in Vancouver. It's a clear indication of the care and attention to detail that goes into their food preparation.

Rao Burger Shack is worth the visit for those looking for a reliable, halal-friendly burger spot in downtown Vancouver. Suhail and Awais's dedication to customer satisfaction further enhances the dining experience, making it evident that this establishment values quality and service equally. Whether you're a burger aficionado or just in the mood for a tasty, well-made meal, Raoul Burger Shack is a place you'll want to check out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqfL2uIFg1qHydoQn4SGab7c9yBAEHx8DU5NhT&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Matthew Kowalchuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq-O4ECqESFAypUX_-5AoNQcv0HSkITMZvRnyOLtcDoZ6m5Jk7xw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The butter chicken cheesesteak was amazing and it looked even better than their picture of it. Good service very friendly. I‚Äôd recommend these guys to anyone. Oh, and very budget friendly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbr2QUHWvcIhL62hW9VmUjmVAw-fdSryOlkYu1&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Jordan M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0jOCT7_UjE_pVpdkV_6218DCloXK20qrJ4le2tn5-BdBjP2o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Had the Philly Cheesesteak and it was very bland and most of it  fell out because the bun wasn't even connected.  Beef was tender issue bun was nice and toasted but yeah everything falling out as I picked it up ruined the entire sandwich.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwN-do8_XQpnqnYgadraXK6QpFlkfcJXDxBZI&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was walking around the area and took the opportunity to have dinner, I had never tried the food here and the truth is that the Philly cheesesteak is very tasty! Besides, it is huge! You can share, they prepare it quickly and the car where they prepare it looks clean, is in front of the subway station.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFsP830ob863zSn9QcYGVd62RKxX3Gcq1D5OtI&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2023-11-30"},{"Name":"Nikoo Niknam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX911CLq91Pl3Cmuy8c4MdZ2Pny-D6lu4R_Ig--XYPw0xsB6a3S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""Rao's Burger Shack is a must-try for chicken and meat burger fans around West Georgia Street. Go grab one, you won't regret it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtp2iJMfvFSgzcWOqaxX02lPW2qTMpiUENmaPe&fid=0x0:0x44ba53d4fbb4a162"],"When":"2023-12-17"},{"Name":"AR Ramsha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI95whI4JylGVrIdK2hrBj_G776M-lVNvpzDmKf5PtyJV1Ufg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had their burgers and we loved them..... Ur trip to Vancouver would be incomplete without their burgers. All halal!!!!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Faisal Maqbool","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt8qLUomDHoZxBuysxJPkKir42pK1SKINKdKlzikufhnuwPWHFRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best budget burger. I wish everyone was like that!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSOQ7SQYQJ5QyFEtQFgy8MOgB9XQ3IKLGNn5KN&fid=0x0:0x23d19bc99d3bf870"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Mojan Forouz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVuwLlICaS_B7C86HADYYOHkP4eC3LNpRkbZMgdYFQSiUfSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Wed oct 23rd 5.30 pm
I work near this subway and My friend asked me to order a Shawarma chicken wrap on my break for her break.
The guy who was making the sandwiches, told me he doesnt have it and asked if Teriyaki chicken is okay.
I came back to work to double check with my friend if she wants Teriyaki.
I went back to subway and told the guy that "yes. She is fine with Teriyaki"
In middle of making her sandwiche, he asked me what kinda cheese i want for my wrap.
i told him please use the same cheese as #25, which is the shawarma wrap.
And then he told me that he can make shawarma wrap if I want.
I again told him that "yes, that is what I wanted from the beginning. But you said you cant make it."
Anyway i got my wrap but not even an apology from the server.
The whole conversation took like 20 minutes which is the full amount of my break.
Maybe you should teach your servers the menu first.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"neha gulati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW6oasaP0eYRCfyQn9VgKc0YLYInVNG9l0bQ3Q1cS0OrPOopY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wnna take a moment to appreciate the girl today who made my sub. It was perfectly crisp to perfection, the coustmer service was amazing. She is precise and fast. Thank you Aayushi. Your efforts are appreciated ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AnooChi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX724gIupKTCShWzyZdsap_cJn15icjlO94DUGjIkT_Iy-gyYiV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Subway is my go-to fast food chain when I'm looking for a quick and healthy meal. I love being able to customize my sub with all my favorite toppings, and their fresh-baked bread always hits the spot. Plus, their commitment to using fresh ingredients and offering a wide variety of options makes it easy to find something for everyone, even those with dietary restrictions. All in all, I highly recommend Subway for anyone looking for a tasty and nutritious fast food option","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNpH7ga_V0NzmTS12ENv9UARG51dakggCTs9rt&fid=0x0:0x23d19bc99d3bf870"],"When":"2023-4-30"},{"Name":"Shaun Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwWHkPvMVWClSn9V0l68FcS9wWNbY5JKBLOpzqDC0aUWCwbOmE9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"When we went at 3 am, there were two customers in the store without masks on. The employee that was working did not ask them to put a mask on, and it took him over 15 minutes to make their order of two sandwiches, without so much as acknowledging our presence or even greeting us.

The chicken had a lot of water in it and looked very off-putting.

Their online order tablet was on the countertop. Anyone who's worked in a store with an online order tablet will know that they are rarely ever cleaned and should not be put on surfaces that share contact with food.

He used a knife to open some boxes and then used the same knife to cut our bread right after.

The whole time we were in the store, we did not see him wash any of his two knives even once despite having made over four orders, with one of the knives visibly dirty.

The employee also mixed up me and my friend's order and charged us incorrectly.

Overall I am very disappointed In the food and most importantly, the cleaning and safety standards at this location. I do not recommend coming here, especially at night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrMRymsOyXtKf2VDpwiYVIC1AyvaqSKBwoS7kO&fid=0x0:0x23d19bc99d3bf870"],"When":"2021-6-5"},{"Name":"Lovepreet Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUckaMLAe-vplVU9gfZG0ow8oc9z3BVGDqqdWkC0sWXde1v_ZZC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is really good and always clean. Also, one of their employees mehtab gives best customer service. Always Recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Red Redd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuW4frUJu_cv_DYJEwwpKzwj49L3WlhcWpv94rtKYLdajgtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Says 24hours open and they guy says they‚Äôre actually closed for cleaning 3am-5am.
