[{"Name":"Rushikesh Dabhekar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVk_kFmvOWmGs89eaWUtZUOZ7UgQj1RM5pn0Oz0Z4tnPyH-DaIYpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The Subway restaurant at Canada Place Cruise Terminal in Vancouver offers a convenient dining option for travelers and locals alike. Located at a bustling hub, it caters to a diverse crowd, from cruise passengers to business professionals and tourists exploring the city's waterfront.

One of the standout features of this Subway is its efficient service. Given its location, the staff is accustomed to handling a high volume of customers, and they do so with commendable speed and professionalism. Even during peak times, the line moves quickly, ensuring that customers can grab a meal without significant delays.

The quality of the food is consistent with what one expects from the Subway brand. The ingredients are fresh, with crisp vegetables and a variety of breads baked daily. The selection of meats, cheeses, and condiments provides ample customization options, allowing customers to tailor their sandwiches to their liking. The restaurant also offers a range of healthy choices, including salads and wraps, which is a plus for health-conscious diners.

The seating area, while limited, is clean and well-maintained. Given the high foot traffic, it can get crowded, but the turnover is generally quick. The staff keeps the dining area tidy, and tables are promptly cleared and wiped down.

The location within Canada Place is another highlight. Patrons can enjoy scenic views of the harbor and mountains while dining. The restaurant's proximity to various attractions, including the Vancouver Convention Centre and FlyOver Canada, makes it an ideal spot for a quick meal.

Overall, the Subway at Canada Place Cruise Terminal provides a reliable and convenient dining experience. Whether you're in a hurry to catch a cruise or simply exploring the area, this Subway offers a quick, tasty, and affordable meal option.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLqPJmcuBWwQ-nlYhnB6cdkUYbIWUiWlZVYObr&fid=0x0:0x3282ddd0f955049c"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Tarandeep Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIujb_mnLrjWv5i3zzdKr9tp_FAUtTeAEfQsiSldFcEOQqmAnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Stupid guy working there. We ordered online and he made a mess. When we asked him about the customised order we asked for online, he started opening it in front of us without wearing gloves. Wasn‚Äôt made according to the order. See the picture on how messy was it. Will he make one like this for himself.
Worst experience ever","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXTGk5ycOyl15f2MN_0D8i5adXSmn3wOB-H9dT&fid=0x0:0x3282ddd0f955049c"],"When":"2023-11-19"},{"Name":"Mercedes Heath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMAAwp0yypn_wykvDuULWX5j38PQFAFVTP2nvMdQb_QYbx2H4Z=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently had an absolutely infuriating experience at this Subway location that I feel compelled to share. After placing an order for two sandwiches, my card unexpectedly failed to work at the register. Despite my best efforts and numerous apologies, I could only purchase one sandwich instead of both.

To make matters worse, the man who appeared to be the owner or manager was beyond rude. Instead of understanding or even offering a shred of empathy, he berated me, calling me wasteful and making it clear that my card issue was none of his concern. Let me be clear: I never once suggested it was his problem, and I repeatedly apologized for the inconvenience.

This man‚Äôs lack of basic decency and customer service skills is astounding. I‚Äôve never felt so humiliated in my life. Avoid this Subway at all costs if you value respect and decent treatment as a customer. There are plenty of other places where your patronage will be appreciated, and you won‚Äôt be treated like a nuisance for an honest mistake.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manvirsingh Saran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcM0-biWjGttxe-VkifMzeH_tsC0W_OlwDwtMGNVq9mAEUDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Manpreet Kaur is an outstanding worker at Subway! She consistently delivers excellent service with a friendly attitude, creating delicious sandwiches with precision and care. Her efficiency, attention to detail, and dedication to customer satisfaction make every visit a great experience. Highly recommend her for top-notch service every time!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damini Thakur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgyaV_tgCegt0lvBCl4n7ZCzcdA8dhvwDvIdj9ICRlvidn5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The overall food was not so good but specifically an old indian guy was very rude. Servers were very friendly and efficient.
Place is very clean.Will be back. üòÄ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PJLife","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWExxPLfiKH1wH-7GDM8WPUua0npwK45Ph-MlKP_DnWih5mHjztcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is my first time here. This place is still fairly new.
Very clean inside.
Nice ambiente for a fast food place.
Friendly staff.
I ordered the chicken Donair plate.
I asked to have half chicken/half beef.

Good:
Chicken, beef, baked potatoes, Persian rice, salad.

Needs improvement:
- Besides the beef there was a heaped tablespoon of very fatty tissues :( , I haven't experienced that before at other Persian places.
- The bread was too dry.
- The hummus is lacking flavour.
- When I paid, the server revealed to me that there is a $3.-! surcharge to have the meat 50/50 :(

[{"Name":"JESSICA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB2i5CpRP7UX8-wv47l2MrFmMz2VuMLPi87EdWVFtliHFbqvwR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mostly a to-go kind of place (it‚Äôs very small, two counter seats and 4 bistro tables out front. Not air conditioned). May be a little pricey but the food is excellent. My sandwich was very tasty although they admitted they forgot about it so it came out extra toasty.

Paid street parking unless you park a little further down or into the residential area.

Their ‚Äúpop up‚Äù on commercial drive looks good - proper sit down restaurant and stellar menu offerings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo3V8NmFwSdtWthqVS-Xj-LMdqiszvyhPmPXKV&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Arunima Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqoZsqmmxBjiRNkcPGwdxtGxL-oPRtsSNO48vOTPeKiMgI0Akq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Guys. Do you know the feeling of being tired of trying disappointing pasta places in the city and just wanting a comforting, tasty, good quality, authentic and cozy spot instead? I‚Äôve been searching far and wide for a spot to fall in love with and this was just that.

Everyone who worked there was so wonderful, down to earth, genuine and inviting. It felt like we were in Italy - a spot where friends sat in cozy tight spaces to share some pasta and pizza dishes. As we were waiting for our food, we decided to dine in instead and I‚Äôm so glad that we did because eating pasta fresh is the absolute best. My boyfriend got the lasagna (10/10) and I got the papardelle (10/10). It just hit the spot, seriously. Food that made me smile.

We just felt so much joy eating that delicious food, surrounded by good people and a truly authentic experience. I can‚Äôt recommend it enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOglfepRYfERVeF7sz3X3O55m4_M4mnbnk5yof7&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Byron Tie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDmm9uxlv7ZX_46OxGNgHZQTbRy7QXdKtN1ufhyCa6-3bIa_4z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The shop is small but has dine in options. I'd say three two-seaters. The staff was helpful and would come around to get our opinion on the dishes.

As for the dishes, we had the gnocchi and rigatoni. I like the gnocchi dish. It's not the usual pesto-like salad variety but also has a tinge of acidity. Lemon, I assume. Also, be warned that the rigatoni is a bit spicy due to the Italian sausage. The house bread is the size of a panini with some herb filling too. The parmesan on top makes it a bit salty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwqTYZNBJ9lxhgnASs4bQqiUCi_0MnTBdURM9I&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Lina Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMOOJAQ_d5e3RYHFmeH4oG1oWsfGw_dOI-6CcE0u1o9YLLayI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When we first got here the worker was so friendly and helpful. He took the time to share recommendations and made sure to answer any of our questions. We got the calabrese pizza, chitarra with meatballs p/:5/ and the cannoli. They were all SO delicious. The pizza was crispy on the outside but somehow still airy and fluffy on the inside. The pasta was flavourful as well. The cannoli was the perfect sweet treat that‚Äôs not too sweet. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDhVk466jscbpcv59sCMoFYHlSCjmmhf7U0pjY&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Sierra Mennis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIx4XwcTzaLi2LpryhmTXAXYxnawQiM53m6E0faZ5zJSy1ctg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow. Nonna‚Äôs Cucina was the best dining experience. I‚Äôve never been to Italy but I think this is the closest thing you can get. Highly recommend and I will be back as often as I can.
I will be craving this meal everyday now. I would pick this restaurant over any fine dining Italian restaurant.

The sauce on both pastas was so flavourful we were scooping up every bite. It was ready so quick and all the staff were amazing and attentive. We also got a pizza to go and the dough was fluffy and light.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2cYZiPFS0aspJrDO4N4p9KQlbxyoSY_YgJIRa&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Caitlyn Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU23oPs6bp630i4HnRsvlmDM8OHCc6tCmjkktp0TTzRYVRaKdEDRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Decided to try this place after passing by a few times on Hastings St. it was a beautiful day so we sat in their outdoor seating area. We ordered the rigatoni pasta and the funghi pizza to share - both were so delicious!!! Rigatoni was so tasty and left us wanting more! We decided to order the full size of the pizza and figured we would take home leftovers. The dough was so light and fluffy and the topping amount to dough amount was perfect! Would definitely come here again to try their other dishes ‚ò∫Ô∏è","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvn1z2OJ9CDZtKlB0fOB_NCjMEdaMz_aeMpwCw&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Alan Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-QmMYfw75kgf5vonVt_7RAAdUJRl5hAF6Ijht6iC6ZE8aPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both the pasta and panini I got here tasted amazing. I love Italian food and this was my first time trying this place out.

I‚Äôve always driven by it but the street it‚Äôs on is a fairly busy street so it‚Äôs rare I have the chance to pull over and park.

If you are in the area, this place is worth the try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXRofTM1EqpN-HnqJeA__qKFw_F_wkfvhU2A3O&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Shelby Arcay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt_QKC9FK61HAUpgSazEjsikOeouxBKdgrqazYrsNSfBM-2t4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite Italian spot in Vancouver. Prices are good and the food is full of flavour. The staff always greet you with positivity and I always leave a happy customer. The fennel sausage ragu  is phenomenal; my second favourite is the homemade gnocchi. Looking forward to seeing the business grow in the future with more menu items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP06LeEm68qxRrkXeZaMiw8rq85RtnZBuLZdJ8&fid=0x0:0x7f543d68054da813"],"When":"2024-8-15"}]

I‚Äôve tried Korean fried chicken from several places. Pelicana, bbq chicken, prinkle chicken, chicko chicken, nene chicken, bokbok chicken‚Ä¶just to name a few. 350f Chicken takes #1 spot for me.

The seasoning, flavour, crispiness (batter), temperature, chicken were all on point! The service was friendly and welcoming. I had mild yeongnyeom, I can‚Äôt wait to come back for more. The coleslaw was delicious. The fries were crispy and the oil used was clean and not bitter (such an important aspect for deep fried food). I tried the garlic mayo too which was a nice touch.

All in all, a great restaurant serving Korean fried chicken. They have more items too like a chicken sandwich which I‚Äôll have to try sometime as well.

Great job!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8Jj1WrSp3lMrJ4ntLK0mKydOwiBw3abr3lbxw&fid=0x0:0xb939405c6a6a8ffa"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Í∞ïÎØº (GoMin)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLV0HAxW6yoyS2LWAyHfIbQd00eCE1-5lIR-L3BQWhtQpGjZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This chicken restaurant is really crispy outside and moist inside. It doesn't taste stimulating, it's a lot, and the fried food is very refreshing. I can be confident that it's the best chicken I've ever had. The staff are also bright and friendly. See you next week 350F chickenüòçüòç^^","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmxtud4Q7pB8PfYMP1xz-jt9HmBYLjACG9TnRD&fid=0x0:0xb939405c6a6a8ffa"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Koko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKIdo0slxr7J5iMREWHfz80O4lxVqOhwbO2ykGUitx0QXOqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We used to come here all the time due to huge portions. [{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Interesting hole in the wall type Chinese restaurant. The outside and interior reminds me of Hong Kong where all the menu items are plastered all over the wall. But what impressed me was the photos of celebrities and politicians that visited this place.

Food was outstanding and great value. We got the 2 course Peking duck and 3 dishes. The pea tips was still young and crunchy and the house pork chops was amazing. We added the truffle fried rice but you can only taste small hints of the truffles. Our meal came with a yam soup dessert. Also you get a free t shirt or hat if you spend over $120.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlmT-R0g0VHFBG81I2UcrJABq1nI94SZA5uJnW&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Casey Ye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEApUDalFbqPMkPa848Ez6bzcTZugbIf9CdQT67iXdNxdfBiDr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for a late dinner after hiking, it was still busy at 9pm on a Sunday. Seated quickly and admired the walls of menu items üòã It was late enough for the late night menu, which is a steal at $17.95 for the Stir fried rice noodles with beef, which comes with free plain congee. Also got the Sauteed Shrimp with Mayonnaise sauce and Beef and Eggplant in BBQ sauce. The portions for both the late night menu and dinner menu are quite large and we took home about half the food. We also got the daily soup which is good for eating deep fried/heaty foods. After the food, we got some fresh deep fried mantou with condensed milk for dessert üòã All the food came out quickly and we even met James the owner of the restaurant. Would come back again to try the seafood and other dishes for late night!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1dNLOyBRBG9NXTb5SFnZCxHPcrv9K2hcGzAKo&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"HX Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlYYhpD9JHfzL6pBbvHaEDo2KwU_rwj_gqucPvsBKa_qy6gJr5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Many choices of Cantonese-styled food with good prices.  No matter whether you are with family, or just a single person, you can find suitable food here.  Excellent services.  Food tasts good too.  They have special bonus for customers who are born in a Year of Dragon, if dine-in and the order is over $60.  Will come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMD8Uxg1Q1yldoUeg44Rf44yGLbf0q-7lj1GUrR&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Kaman Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTfY1lFx7N7LsexryuKa9Q76pyfiBSBOSe4KZKmNeoZtDKwC8s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Update on Sept 6, 2024 - the recent visit had pulled the trigger - enough is enough! We don‚Äôt want to go back again. There are many flies flying everywhere, the washrooms for both men and women are disgusting, and the dirty dishes just placed on the washroom hallway with lots of flies. We can no longer accept this level of hygiene. Not recommend.

Update on Sept 3, 2023 - it‚Äôs with huge disappointment to share that the quality of food is dramatically different from our last few experiences. We ordered the same lobster set and dishes and all of them were over cooked tonight. I‚Äôve heard from others saying their food quality has declined however I wanted to give them the benefit of the doubt and experienced myself. And the rumors are real. Despite their denial, I feel the dishes tonight were cooked by a new chef. Need to find another restaurant as likely not going visit again.

First few visits - The noodle stir fry is excellent - full of ‚Äúwok air‚Äù üòÖ. The crab prawn ball is crispy and tasty. There are so many items we want to try and plan to visit regularly.
4th visit - We went again and ordered the lobster with three other dishes - they all tasted excellent except they are very salty. I asked for low sodium at the time of order however they are saltier tonight than other visits.
5th visit in July 2023 - reminded the server for low sodium given our last experience. They made it right this time. Glad that they listened.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp4cuAxiZ34pNp_Q0MDfsac6gKNul33oY-tC3u&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2023-2-21"},{"Name":"Kalvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYzAZd-0_JeniSNljNxgImCwzlXWbe6PzaDeAXT6_nhg5vP5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing service, lots of variety of food to choose from and reasonable price. The food tasted delicious and if you spend over $120 you get a free t-shirt","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXWHogXiJSEJuBOrKrI4RHCwWayakBMbs3lHw-&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Brian Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUOfBDs595dJxJAq4k1IVA9RV2OpG0vGwzghD4H27vk-WWrnM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting Vancouver from NYC and we booked an Airbnb nearby and was on the hunt for some Chinese food open late.  We picked this place on a whim after looking around online and seeing what was close.  It's a small family style restaurant and pretty busy (being Saturday night) but we luckily got a table right away.  The food portions are rather generous and very tasty.  We had enough to take back as left overs.  The next night we went out to another Cantonese restaurant and was pretty disappointed in both the service and food quality.  So the following night we decided to come back to James place and it once again held up.  Dishes tasted better than the Cantonese food in NYC for sure.

We showed up pretty late so after the other tables left, we were the only ones left and James, the owner, was rather personable chatting with us and gave us complimentary milk tea after my Uncle had mentioned he had been really looking for some good Hong Kong styled milk tea.  He took the time to even sit in with us and take a picture, joking that he'd put our picture on the wall. (The walls are covered with the dishes you can order as well as celebrities that have dined in the establishment over the years).

Overall, it was a great restaurant that is really flexible with how you want your dishes prepared, like style, vegetables, type of noodle and mix and matching things not on the set menu for additional prices.  The lobster and crab over noodles was tasty, as well as their salt and pepper pork chops, Peking pork chop, and free range soy sauce chicken.

I definitely would definitely recommend this place for Cantonese food if you're nearby in the Vancouver area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSmOAcONhdOyYuPmmb0mDiLBCZmbJiRxMRM0in&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Ada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_tT85lO7aZKFfq17wWpo8ldgI_n0GJFJfBhG1nWiEa2zXCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Generous portions of food. James (the owner) also gave us two free dishes to celebrate a birthday. Parking lot is a bit small, but free street parking available. Great service. Food taste good overall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3xmXLgBbWTUrdG4khA6jt2w7YXHr8u4mWGCrP&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-2-7"},{"Name":"Natalie Hung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHr3HsTZAqLVgf9XzrEXrIt7hvJaMN7wt6f4rbE0kNaZlMHnHC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I left this place feeling confused. While I was offended by their service, their food was good enough that it almost compensated their horrible service. Almost. So it wasn't enough. Therefore I wouldn't recommend this place or be coming back.

We made reservations a week ago for 8 people at a specific time with specific dishes. Due to their popularity, we felt like reserving a king crab and a Peking duck is necessary. And a phone call was placed a day before to confirm all the details. However, when we arrived just 3 min before reservation time, they told us no table but almost almost. We understand that for busy Asian restaurants, sometimes it's hard to provide a table right on time. We told the waitress that we'll wait outside instead of having 8 people crowding their front door. She agreed and said almost almost, and I'll come get you.

60mintues later, we're still in the cold waiting outside. I'm unsure how and why this happened, with advanced noticed and confirmation. Either way, we were cold and hungry. During that last 30min of waiting, we repeatedly head inside at 10min interval to remind the waitress that were still waiting outside, in the cold.

Eventually we were seated in a very crowded space. That means whenever one of us needed to stand up, we would have to ask the table behind us to provide some space. If you have clusterphobia, avoid this place. The waitress informed us that because we were kept waiting outside, the drinks are on them today. How nice, but a drink doesn't justify an hour of wait with reservation. Still, I appreciate the mild gesture. Then the owner came to show us, a group of 8, the king crab he saved for us, oh let me correct that, the sad king crab that is left. It was small, missing a leg, and not looking very fresh. Usually restaurants like these will let you choose another crab if you don't like it. But the owner said this is the last one.

What happened to reserving a good king crab? With a week advanced notice....? Didn't we call twice to confirm?

I am fairly upset by this point. You can only be so careless, especially in the service industry. The one thing that brought this restaurant to a 2 star is their food. Their sauce is not overpowering yet flavourful. This compliments the main ingredients nicely, whether it was beef or shrimp. Peking Duck was a bit dry, lack flavor. King crab was steamed with light seasoning. While it was hilariously tiny, the taste was good.

Conclusion: I couldn't recommend this place for their lack of care and sincerity but if you don't mind waiting 1 hour or more to have good food in a very cramped space, this might be the place for you. Come here for regular dishes, not king crab. For a $100 meal/per person, I suppose I expected more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdudg7ZTDWtug2knb2wTOy1AtCcV9_YDErKtc&fid=0x0:0x65925ec6c07f412c"],"When":"2024-4-1"}]

Food was ready super fast and it tasted okay. The two soft drinks machines were spilling some strange drinks and the only acceptable flavour we had was the iced tea. Place was decently clean but we‚Äôd have a better experience if we ordered to take out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp34_r3Ge1APYZZcHqpx_aNab4Z3Nt4G4mcdZC&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Iman Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY_It5dFbhJ3ahD3y8wnnvsyYECBdVwU0ipYiueTLf-0IgvGbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I gave them a 4/5, but it probably should've been a 3. The food is fine, but nothing special, especially for lunch or dinner. The service isn‚Äôt great compared to other competitors. The atmosphere is the worst if you plan to dine in‚Äîit seems clean, but it doesn't feel that way. There are lots of sounds, like alarms coming from the kitchen. I don‚Äôt really want to comment on the kitchen‚Äôs cleanliness, but based on what I saw‚Äîparticularly how they deliver the food from the kitchen to the counter‚Äîit wasn‚Äôt that great.

The food itself is 4/5 for me, which is why I gave that rating. We ordered two burgers, which were tasty and delicious, though they could‚Äôve been more exciting. The portion size was enough for one person. I wouldn‚Äôt recommend the chili bowl‚Äîit was too watery for my taste. I prefer thicker bowls, though in terms of flavor, it was fine. It‚Äôs not spicy, though.

Overall, the environment could be improved with just a few simple changes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdakf8kXHa8IL0yeCLAx_yE319KWrJlcN_1Yts&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wow that ghost pepper ranch dip has a nice kick. Classic jbc is my old school fix. Wendy‚Äôs burgers definitely better than McDonald‚Äôs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlf2loHhTSUQ4a66_2VPoRdfVTBjpy-rkYk2VM&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"Teresa McDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJgK1lYbcY62oaa5HP9MrGkUTqm21H6gjNFZhAjqtbAjn7Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The drive thru window staff we nice and polite but our fries where horrible. Hard and dry.... no excuse at 1:30 in the afternoon. Throw them away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN788agFan6vZvUDc9JaPRXX_Iprv7T6rUyWkfb&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Marcio Branco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJpH4c1AStXGLzhU_K5D8rYICGT6O5rpfivfRSfHV3Y9IyIQpOAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service was fast but cordial and the food was ok but better than the MCDONALD'S, The atmosphere is to bright and nothing cozy what does not looks like an Invitation to enter / stay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKbVboaAE8YDzC2sqzH2PWkNqd7i6IBit0sdg5&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Moyez B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6Eamn5ca8yTbck8IWNLNrD9ZeZUGnCTcQ08dD3UxDg2X-UdoJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The cuisine is delightful; however, the establishment is grappling with a shortage of personnel. The employees appear overwhelmed by their tasks. The carbonated beverage dispensers show signs of neglect, with one machine out of order and the others unclean. There's a noticeable absence of ice, and requesting it from the staff garners exasperated reactions. The overall organization leaves much to be desired. I regret having to share this review, but it's crucial for them to improve their operations. Particularly during the bustling dinner hours, they should ensure a sufficient staff presence. Preparing for dinner service by restocking their machines is essential. Responding to customer inquiries with eye-rolling is highly discourteous. It's important to note that this issue lies not with the staff, but with the owners, who ought to invest in additional personnel. Cutting corners is not advisable. The dining area where patrons are seated is in an unsanitary state. Basic amenities like napkins and ketchup are absent. Wendy's, what is the reason behind this? A serious reassessment is in order. They should seriously contemplate making changes and hiring more staff to address these concerns.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0IrBqOezMBNdOXZq14YX18T_cjdISgLiSJ8Oz&fid=0x0:0xed78ef518e3a9411"],"When":"2023-5-5"},{"Name":"Galen Linnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNqh6OaD5JO605dhFZ_swUxiWJTWNOmPRydYKWwfPde2gyYndblQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Last cheap fast food chain out there.  Food is all great except the chicken tenders but their chicken nuggets a just as good as McDonald's. Truly fast truly cheap best selection in Canada.  I was shocked when I came back to Wendy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ANANTPREET KAUR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbICIId8YkIswWfHSLn3H8pWeMD4TtbtTeAaJl9KVaRrZMM_s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just ordered at this location‚Äôs drive thru cheese egger n ice coffee and the lady at drive thru was extremely rude and unprofessional. Didn‚Äôt see her nametag, but she was a half blonde kinda highlights with brown hair And she closed the window at our face. And this is such a nonsense gesture with poor customer service .

Should train employees at better customer service. And employees must know how to treat people with respect n obedience.

She told we have cars behind (it was 2-3 cars), i get it but you should know how to take orders not only quickly but clearly and especially with respect n politeness.

Extremely disappointed in the very morning by this lady.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Dayna Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdTXsRCng8gkDyx2catnV4K6fzDuqTRgvYofYTuKX7ZeCSb9QP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled upon this cute breakfast nook today and was pleasantly surprised.

I walked in and it smelled clean, the bathroom was also well taken care of and cleanly.

The menu has a ton of great options and decently priced, the food tasted wonderful.

We are from out of town, but would definitely come back if we were in the neighbourhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYuLuujylWp_zdiQjFM9NFhd0VbkjxVbiKhYI9&fid=0x0:0x53d888b350705520"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Nasrin Moradinik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3Kk8XG4lRXLDtLDJApv5hA6eMxp6DW5P1QuWyvqwc8cZF38O7Xw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Well, a local and friendly spot. Good for kids to enjoy their favorite waffles.  The lady at the counter (probably the owner) is very sociable and nice.
The service is quite good.
There were number of rules which were funny!
There was a map hanging on the wall showing each customer's nationality.
Overall, nice experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_4A1JvblaFIMqRGTrFg9quwJg6mSoW7Z9EQOL&fid=0x0:0x53d888b350705520"],"When":"2022-10-13"},{"Name":"ab mmm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHzw184Ql0kVbik_CHon4BqqpRO4zCONgSafgBk5QdOByjLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a cozy place with delicious food. Their waffles are so good! My personal favorites are as follows

Sweet waffles: Nutella Waffle(I know, so basic), it's so delicious!
Blueberry whip waffles! It's light and sweet.

Savory waffles: The tomato asparagus one! It's a beautiful blend of sweet and savory.

Pro tip: Get Hollandaise on the side too, you got a pretty sizeable amount to relish.

And you get to sit with Goldie, the stuffed bear!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiqWDGdN8zTOApXyt7R2FdGa3Hy-bfpLQ5lVK8&fid=0x0:0x53d888b350705520"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Marcus Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpW5Leh6_TllyZ2Ih33Q7ftm5wDxHHa4rTFHqr8FR8KCSYSyz9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don‚Äôt come. Soggy waffles. Way too sweet.

Some red flags: we don‚Äôt see waffle station in the kitchen making fresh waffles, constant microwave beep and door open/close, what we got does not look like the pictures hung on the wall

We ordered the BBQ pulled pork waffle and egg/ham waffle.

BBQ pulled pork - The bbq sauce was overly sweet and the waffle was soggy. I ate less than half and couldn‚Äôt finish it bc it was way too sweet. The oil and sauce just oozes out when you start to cut into it.

Egg/ham waffle - also very sweet bc they put syrup on the waffle under the ham.The egg looks and tastes like it was cooked via the microwave.

$20 per waffle, not worth it

They probably changed owners bc someone in our group came once before and said it used to be good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJ3OQ5WNu7EpiKX11t7zZw4oTBMRu1G1AWXFL0&fid=0x0:0x53d888b350705520"],"When":"2023-8-13"},{"Name":"Matt Erikson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMKn5KCXOg3X5LUx5FGZnbbAJU0DW2_9e7xGzYhjkbq7Y8CA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic spot, the waffles were the best I've ever had, and overall the food didn't miss. Wish they had a chicken option but still would give this place a try if you're more into savory stuff because the waffles are that good. My girlfriend loved her Reeses waffle as well, they had tons of great options to choose from. Thanks, we will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBWjpzWhM6Z_J6lfZzLHxHYx5jQJ9z_8UKuTvq&fid=0x0:0x53d888b350705520"],"When":"2024-3-7"},{"Name":"Jeffrey Thi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnSLNTuZqg5C19sBhKr3KiKOUrYvcysFQt67sFfcfA4TLq1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend and I enjoyed our food a lot! 5. Then she said she can‚Äôt do the refund due to a manager not being on site I had asked for her name and she said she didn‚Äôt feel like giving it to me then I said I want to talk to a manager and she said she was the manager after telling me there was no manager to help me then hung up the phone on me since she did that I went in person to get her name because she wouldn‚Äôt over the phone If CARMEL is the manager no wonder they have bad reviews I will be in contact with an actual manager because I want my refund and will never come back I have a video of her being rude as well if I could put it on here I would.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Salome Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_2K9wAlCYCB6lo06gWP1WGP_DEt_C1rY4Zl3dAQ7JYEIxzv9C=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just ordered a choco brownie blizzard tipped and the cashier said in the rudest voice, ‚Äúcan you just put it in my hand‚Äù was literally loonies but okay so I did and it‚Äôs vanilla ice cream you cannot taste the chocolate like usual, dawg what did I do to you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3DnGnetIwYk4GDO7dlCqWOTLu_42Cbio1Nrza&fid=0x0:0x446c3fad3558f60d"],"When":"2024-4-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jessica Roberts-Farina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4Tow237HlTZOzs4ESi4uFxKQ98updyjSQg39nzCBrgjuUTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The space was cold and smelled of diesel fumes from the street. The happy hour stadium nachos was served cold and got soggy quickly The ginger beer was not ginger beer -it was a mocktail with juices etc.

The cashier asked me how it was when I had finished leaving the half the nachos uneaten and when I told him the nachos were served cold, he responded rudely and said, well yes only the cheese is hot. I repeated, it was served cold, to which he said, well did you say something? I ended it with, you asked how it was so I'm telling you.

If you don't want an honest answer or ultimately not actually care about the quality of food, don't ask.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Afie Ebrahimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWy05KWDvac-gEpomT-JcJzcumTxfB81Vfa1KEyj27X9NnmEqAm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I‚Äôve been coming here for many years, but in the past year+ it‚Äôs become so inconsistent on top of price increases that I won‚Äôt be returning any more. Today, I had a Pacific Cod burrito which is supposed to include tempura battered cod. The batter tasted like corn meal and oil, and there was almost no fish in it. I am honestly confused about the person who made this and thought it was fine to send out. The two stars are because the service is fine and the store itself is very nice. Also the loaded tots are (usually) great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKp7pRKsdfHdLRR27wA4-P7ydXm7uypUaXJsXP&fid=0x0:0x47364e478232a053"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Robert Monroe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg9DGuuqs1J12VHJ2upNOFXp1UusbARxPCrTtQ7yFMcG1BAls=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Highly overpriced and they do not offer table service. All orders and payment made at the front cashier. $8 is the cheapest for 1 taco. Highway robbery.

One taco and a shared appetizer was $21 + tip. No drinks. No wonder the flagship Gastown location closed. They just aren't getting the message that they need to change their business model.

WHY are Vancouver people tolerating this?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"andrew Brothers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIJvRoNgyzTz3tv9kERyvdo0xQ3YCe3g-C5fpd7o0Wgv07EQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ate here twice during our 5 day stay in Vancouver so that should tell you akk you need to know! I had the feta nachos each time and my wife the tacos. Luv it! You've gotta stop by üòâüëç","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCx5LOBI8fv2xYa_O3X-JnUXwoW_AfhRSq0ze6&fid=0x0:0x47364e478232a053"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Mackenzie Tierney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWs6SfOnp2Xlzd5aiLeHdsQBmNeiJuBnuYBIiI7dlF5vsinf-LK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôve been wanting to try this place for a long time, and it was well worth the wait! The tacos are huge, and delicious! The wings are also amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0QsCX-k5W_lX2JdpPNaUZeFI8S7ickSZmOY9S&fid=0x0:0x47364e478232a053"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"behnoosh khoramrooz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4lW_vvhzQ6YOn6Wkf7m0i33va21OdVis0bl63xsIyxnbd9V-8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice place, good vibe, but the taco for me was sort of oily and I felt not really ok having it. But the reason I am adding a comment is to warn you about the dessert! If you do not like egg taste and smell, the lime curd vase is not for you! I wish I knew it before trying that, had a terrible taste for all night after having just one spoon of it :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kurt Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAybV3FwvXjuD8K4iYY6qxPMBoj7ChB0b4G5SiOgOs4urNb2Fb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service! Fun friendly atmosphere. As an electrician I absolutely loved the crazy light fixtures in here. Had the pork al pastor burrito bowl and the vegan cauliflower burrito bowl. Hearty satisfying meals with a large portion size. The classic lime margaritas were also fantastic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrZio-IHNDbeDAHOFphhABlVU-USHZ4XsC9xXq&fid=0x0:0x47364e478232a053"],"When":"2024-2-21"},{"Name":"Jason Brien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5Jp4_OPogVs6Q1FKC8Rd-K2O3hvCZrEVAxaFmVEm338CDugXC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got glutened at this place, and it wasn't the first time. I'm aware that the menu does not have explicitly stated GF items, but tacos are naturally GF because of the corn tortillas. I've eaten them lots in Central American countries and the US. The server at TF told me which ones would be safe and which ones wouldn't be (due to deep fried items in them), but they were wrong. The Gastown location also did this to me, when they were still open.

The prices are also ridiculous now. The cheapest taco is $8. If you visit Bellingham, just across the border, you can get $1.50 tacos at a food truck that are delicious. I don't know what it is about Vancouver but they just can't do tacos here properly.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Tara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvz-VTcwi5AwXbPx-NXjcs5r94hlSJW_GQ6DyJLRaBZRXGVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite place to eat donair! Since the new management, the food is so so much better! I come here regularly for dinner and I am always so happy with the food I get. The fries are super crispy and very tasty. The vegetables in the donair are fresh and crunchy. Soo delicious! The people are very friendly and courteous. I just feel really comfortable here. You can get so many different dishes from starters and snacks to main courses and desserts. I've tried so much and have never been disappointed! The prices are also super good and fair. I can recommend everyone to come here. You will definitely find something!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODJ5y_ekZN1kcwdbk6RlGnM2pGm9z_YL1prEdo&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Karan Sidhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDLbEvFaVIfvno8VwDvLjsv_dZM22uiABVZtGFVq2OJOuZQJqr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The savory aroma of seasoned meat fills the air.  A warm, soft flatbread cradles the flavorful filling.  Fresh toppings add a delightful crunch and zest. Each bite is a burst of textures and tastes. This truly sounds like a satisfying and delicious meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHW7wWGTWtVeARCwj1h3NrpN0gpY942m7peSto&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Shiva Radmanesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX50D30SjZBR4QvfRxKL45XQxTtaGKOp6R4BwFd5j_tfXu-Hq4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff were so friendly and kind! The food was very good‚Äîone of the best donair wraps I've ever had. They toast the pita at the end, which makes it extra delicious. Plus, the portions were generous for the price!

I definitely recommend this placeüòã","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1WZhg03XeA3DAJt3bcpCPcSGEjq72-Nu-4iqr&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Mitika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ13d-XaIY3wPr6LwYhQewsHMI0ZDjxHH6I50QVcfofaooY-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the chicken donair wrap, and it was delicious! The delicious, well-seasoned chicken was paired with fresh veggies.The soft wrap kept everything together wonderfully, and the creamy donair, hot sauce and sweet sauce added a nice spice. Every bite was a wonderful combination of flavours and textures. Overall, a must-try for anyone looking for a wonderful meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFAdKIvxkWzJITspFO3AzKD5F-_SsSsDEybEX2&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Rikki M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUvyslYCN7agK8c8p3HKMWjdAOjCN-XcutzDs7D-YUa-_vaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the meat and fries. I found that there was plenty of fries but not enough chicken.  The fries were delicious and cooked to perfection. The server also added some sauces which elevated the flavours.

Service was friendly and quick for the most part. Took some time with frying the fries but it made the dish worth it.

Atmosphere is not the best due to the location of the restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjOdGz_0Cx-PeZV_SR4dpjYzdzhnS4vWgTvAde&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Jer Neale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbCaum_MysohqXLPLzgQkFSXvuj_F54m3xnt4xa593Ukc7pfc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place is an absolute disgrace, and I genuinely hope they go bankrupt and shut down immediately. For $15, I was expecting a decent donair, but what I got was a pathetic excuse for a meal‚Äîa donair the size of a pizza pocket. I was stunned. It was laughably small, insulting even. And then came the real kicker: the toppings bar.

Everything looked like it had been sitting out for days, maybe weeks. The tomatoes were pale, mushy, and downright depressing. The canned olives were rubbery and tasted like they came straight out of the bargain bin. Every other topping screamed ‚Äúexpired,‚Äù like they gave up on quality entirely. The only thing that looked remotely edible was the cabbage‚Äîcabbage! That says it all, doesn‚Äôt it?

And the drinks? Five dollars for a can of pop. FIVE. What kind of shameless price gouging is that? Between the microscopic portion, the inedible toppings, and the rip-off drink prices, this place should be ashamed to call itself a business.

I couldn‚Äôt even eat what I was served‚ÄîI had to ask for my money back. Donair Dude is a scam, charging premium prices for trash-tier food. If this is their idea of quality, they deserve to close down immediately. Do yourself a favor: avoid this place like the plague.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPetRTY-BdOWdZxr98oBm6NF_lto4Dduqsh4R6H&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Grace Ling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUakUlWflndNvgw-Yl0g2ZK4LQnjLXdKErmm9hCWSPtuym81G7s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An awesome casual Mediterranean food chain in Vancouver!! Got a chicken plate and loved the dolma. They also open late and have friendly staff!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPv0W5IlMCk_joC84hOoLYlmv43xy80cKif_vfX&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Tiffany L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUp9tcU0VfIrVwMMWedmQgxxjhefNC-iN5gUOl5miUKsKVCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"There was barely any meat in the $16 donair, only a few shreds of chicken. Not sure why the other reviews are so high when there are also consistent complaints about the portion sizes of protein.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3I_1-FD78aaxcF4nYb4yrs2l8Paixo4JiqK3L&fid=0x0:0xaa1819e6f4327d7e"],"When":"2024-9-9"}]

[{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A reliable and cozy place for standard North American Vietnamese favourites like deep fried chicken wings, deep fried spring rolls, house special beef pho and even crab pho. Everything tasted very good and as expected. The ingredients all tasted fresh and the broths were flavourful but not too salty. A nice dinner. The sauces they give are a great addition to the chicken wings and spring rolls. Sadly they don‚Äôt have fresh squeezed orange juice or classic bean desserts but what they do have is very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXBXayIPTAs929rnjs5cjg-02zUcPqnUJrfDXT&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"J Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLoo9VmGrNdWf2ch9xBiUKHfC3K_3offFhwdmM7ItsULyE253o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The restaurant is quite spacious, it would be easy to get a table without lining up.
I ordered 1 house special pho#17 and 1 hot and sour pho. The soup of house special is kind of blank but the hot and sour pho is much better and flavorful. The quantity of the meat in both bowls are kind of too little.  I could get much better portion from other Vietnamese restaurants.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLPD8Ng4y1WfVgZWcPzYw_uKoUS-OD_PNnJa2Z&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Cathy Bautista","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDCqyWoUP-a1GwTqsebZnDLFXiJkqOWRFyNCUGvbvvdMFJc1rM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down, the best Pho Spot in all of Vancouver. You have not truly experienced Pho until you‚Äôve stopped here. Order the hot & sour and you will not be disappointed! Not only is their Pho incredible, their service is too. The atmosphere is extremely welcoming and the staff are incredibly kind! I come here with my girlfriend often and it‚Äôs always a great time. I would rate this place 100/10!!!üíïüíïüíï","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOrOBbk5Ivs7hgty_StmgGnkItamTX2j25mXiW&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Kingsley Okorji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdbNMOtU9Xb3dEBkxcsYW5uuMGsbXul0_k5jvFJ1x0kpksbHn2Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is like a second home to me, the staff are impeccable. The service was great and they were so attentive.
The food arrived quickly and was fresh and flavourful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO24DnAaV_l6NfF2XeVO0Dx-C5Cj2JHbdr6_qSN&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"D D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVn-HmKGkiEXpPYEJdaFnX-Wk9npBuMky8Sv8ZSJcapzQOOPiN3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Weekdays visit at lunch is a good time to dine at Le Pho ... quite a bit of seating and always fast and friendly service.  The young ladies are quick, knowledgeable and pleasant.  Prices are very reasonable.  Pho broth is not overly salty, noodles never overcooked, banh mi always tasty and generous fillings.  Our go to pho since Bao Chau closed down up the street.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPFQHAo3qSV6nfR6ItoyTZqh2i8zqA8ICevWNa&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Tom C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdiYc5x_E-Q2lE0z_5xM3LFSGfnEnGmUa_btawv_geQdXHww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"On this visit-

Pros:
Inexpensive
Free parking on Hastings
Friendly staff
Pho flavor wasn‚Äôt bad

Cons:
Grilled chicken tasted microwaved and very little lemongrass flavor
Spring roll wasn‚Äôt crispy enough, needs to be refried perhaps?
Fish sauce seems more sweet than salty-more fish sauce needed?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbiRnvk4TSrIZlnBk0ZHkNJGGjhvRrJTOrSSZV&fid=0x0:0x61f42e4fca14bf6b"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"Katey Asaph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn7c7lLZIRt7OmkHc04gN80jznMggDi46jobRynscixvgYZDxk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Favourite pho spot in the city by far. Was hoping for a Torta Ahogada but thats only on the lunch menu. Instead I settled with the Cochinita Benedict which was delicious. Not as good as my wife‚Äôs chilaquiles though!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJsz3RIWOpCOJ5UOtaLp5TuGvYQH3x7t0plKHE&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Jesse Jardine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCzDR0nQseDX-YvbnsmT8LhszGtAEvY7TAlWdNB93j2elpLTP1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best brunch place. Bennies are 10/10 best in the city. I've been everywhere around the drive trying every Benny and nothing touches this. Salmon Benny is amazing. Go here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp_A3TczPJpITrhJJq1BM3rTe_JhUMm5HN9BR5&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Lee Van","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkdc0b5WROtpnJCruJpetIegq6Snt_2bGm0A5pSa9cqY1SCXL5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My friend and I headed here for brunch Sunday morning. We agreed to sit at the bar given there were no other tables available and we didn't really want to wait. The atmosphere is lovely, a little cramped perhaps and a little loud at times. That said, the food was good. My friend and I both got the eggs benedict and avocado which was yummy. I would come here again. We both managed to find parking on Hastings Street, no problem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO97qYwp0UeKlKXXuIF-0HOPOEYh_pgkzeqptHR&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"i trasgu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj3xDN63RHMh2Uktz1CJgwXYEeitjUUjFguEsiThcfmzVO2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could give Caf√© El Roundel more than five stars I would!

This is one of those restaurants where you wished you had a bigger stomach so you could eat more! The food is amazing, authentic, and delicious; prepared in an immaculate kitchen with traditional ingredients but with the modern ingenuity that you can only find in Mexico City or Guadalajara. Simply the best Mexican food in the lower mainland.

The atmosphere is modern but welcoming and comfortable; our server Eileen made us feel at home and made great recommendations for our first time. We're planning to become regulars because this is one of those places that you can eat exceedingly well without ever feeling uncomfortable; ingredients are fresh, top-quality, and dishes are healthy but oh so satisfying.

For instance, nowhere in BC will you ever find chayote (pear squash) salad, aguachile (like a ceviche), or tortas ahogadas (typical subs from Guadalajara with Livia bread) because this kitchen is miles ahead of the cookie-cutter Mexican food that we're used to here, offering us vegetarians and meat eaters sophistication and deliciousness at great prices.

The drinks are another refreshing (lit) feature: cocktails prepared with care in vintage glasses or wonderful brews, and a fun zero-proof selection like Jamaica (sorel).

As if that wasn't enough, they have a great playlist that had us grooving and vibing for the whole time! I can't wait to try the whole menu because every dish and drink our party order was scrumptious, satisfying, and prepared with care. We were so happy here!

We have officially tried all items in the menu including breakfast/brunch! YUM!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlf8cTc-b0nF-yNIKysBj3RSL8Lki_AxFoF6P0&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2023-11-22"},{"Name":"Fatemeh Sayadi (Tisha)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT0iXGjcmugjaf-sxnw_j5g7IpzISbK9kqKoWSQpUn_JCfvpEr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely recommended. We had cappuccino and mocha I loved it. For meals we ordered basic breakfast, quinoa bowl, and black bean Benedict. The eggs were poached really well, the cubed potatoes were seasoned perfectly. The staff were nice and friendly, the waiting time was only 5 minutes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7zD5RWhxljCel363sxw4ntCIUXRzMqD-i1aHm&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2022-4-9"},{"Name":"Chucho Godinez (GasparIlom)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcjzn0qHBMp7jO9n6NwwgcfJ8Iqqx_He8Ip146cN1pYA36rR9T4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The good: The food is amazing, I had the huevos ba√±ados and my wife had the chilaquiles, both with nice presentation, full of flavour. My wife is kind of a Coffee snob, very picky but she insisted I mentioned in my review that the coffee was very good, smooth and bold. We were meeting old tenants of ours we keep in touch with and we had a long chat, we were never disturbed or rushed to vacate the table. I like the inside even though is a small place.
The not so good: Don't come here very hungry because the servings are on the small side, however I see that everywhere we go this days, Restaurant owners reducing the size of servings to compensate the high cost of ingredients, labour, rent, etc. So I get that part and I don't fault or give a bad review because of that. At the time to pay the bill, the machine handed to you comes with the tip screen and the lowest is 18%, I mean you can customize it, but I think everyone is doing that. The service was worth of a tip and it was earned.
So: Overall a great experience, will definately go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONlOFXshLPhGGdiAyqKUS9VRrZ_Zy3LKuBbjaS&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Matt Moya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6Dd2-qLoxdQ0V-pcqlJ4XGtTWjvUlfICq4eppY1oKocACDwTq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A breakfast joint down the street was full, so we came here. This place is our new go to! Absolutely awesome brunch/breakfast in a charming little diner setting. The staff was exceptional, and very attentive. Their standards for cleanliness was top notch. A safe and clean environment with exquisite food. If you find yourself in the area, this place is an absolute must visit. Can‚Äôt wait until my next visit here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMflkVGevJANORmyempc9_765vamYssnh3P1tQg&fid=0x0:0x105adea0b6311592"],"When":"2021-1-30"},{"Name":"adam Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtRBMp_7sreO5jr6GK1rc0vTPe6S_2b-2RKMSbLp6gu5A7HI6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I‚Äôve been here a handful of times and it‚Äôs just a very inconsistent place.
Came here yesterday on the weekend and it was busy. Not a great welcome just told to put a name on this list but there was no pen and he left before I could say anything. I ended up putting together a couple seats at the bar. All good, they‚Äôre busy.
It‚Äôs one of those places that are so small that if you pick up bad energy from staff, it kinda sets the room you know? The servers both just seemed like they didn‚Äôt want to be there and ours was nice and everything but she seemed sad, maybe cause her coworker looked kinda cold and miserable .. I don‚Äôt know I can imagine if you‚Äôre working with people that aren‚Äôt in any way fun it would be kinda sad.
I ordered the black bean Benny and my egg was overcooked and my husband got French toast and it was burnt on one side. The place was busy and I didn‚Äôt want to tell the waitress cause i knew if they remade it, it would take another 30 minutes and I was hungry. üòû

I feel like if they had better music that was a tad louder.. maybe some sort of beat.. funk.. or something? Something to pick up the vibe in there a little cause it currently has mopy vibes,  happier friendly service would make a huge difference

I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôm going to be back after yesterday though, it was just off in there and not worth the money","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This location has been here a long time. It‚Äôs a the gateway to everywhere. Recently just tried out their 2 for $4. Pretty reasonable breakfast. It‚Äôs also summer time and $1 frosties are back.

Plenty of parking and  drive thru till 4am.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6AO5wQaRLY5zzqEq4BuayuD7zxO3OG-SIFpS6&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Ana Revel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGS4JJvdl4RjmcavxVgwZC7FBR-0w3eGVN7g3lUR86gRQQf_M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This Wendy‚Äôs has gone downhill , the customer service is awful, the food is gross and they just rush you out. Half the time they aren‚Äôt even speaking English to you. Very frustrating when trying to order your food and they can‚Äôt repeat what you ordered. Will never go here again, been coming to this Wendy‚Äôs for over 20 years, won‚Äôt waste my money anymore. Just example of what the nachos looked like‚Ä¶.. gross I threw them away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsOpAKSKXgrlxIIqsa-6VVrK1fuu8u5j8SeqQh&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Stan ‚ÄúThe Anti-Slip Guy‚Äù Schaefer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzqltE5LGtJImuoUpVJ_NYvhJbn49XC-SYegXTLH-CfeoTWoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"So, the purpose of this review is more to inform people about how Wendy's is going downhill in its quality. I have a couple of photos attached. These photos are showing expectation and reality. See if you can spot the difference. I purchased two Baconator Burger meals that came with fries and drinks. Unfortunately, we looked at the pictures that were displayed, and we both wanted baconators, and when we got them, we said that they can't be the same thing. You be the judge.
After mentioning it to a basic manager, I asked her to bring me the store manager and she said she would and she never did. Upon leaving the store I managed to speak with the store manager or so she said add her comment was these are the old pictures. I said well this is what we saw and what we were expecting and certainly not what we got. For this kind of money I would have rather gone to A&W and or Burger King and for a few dollars more I could go to White Spot and get a much better product with the ambiance. Be sure to respond to this and talk about it, Wendy's is not the only one but there's certainly one of the worst.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5a08HG0vi97U2uGXdpHAlSiaR9M1ndZA9cwjf&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The new French onion triple cheeseburger is delicious. It‚Äôs a super juicy, meaty, beefy burger. The junior cheeseburger deluxe is also very tasty and fresh. Wendy‚Äôs beef patties taste so much higher quality than most fast food burger joints and the flavour is simple and cohesive. A bonus is you can add extra lettuce and onion to many burgers for free. The food tastes like it‚Äôs made from real ingredients and less processed than other major fast food chains.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBfJGP8lrrdVHwn4_V9_xhs23ZQkc6pkGfeuF1&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"chriskennedy100 Kennedy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5PqIPqW9Ue04hGs3Rsu-Ek2fKjfwcNvzHH9NT32jYU8JyNvBS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Service was fast and friendly. Food was very average. Poutine was terrible. Positives: ketchup, hot sauce and Mr Pibb refills were accessible from the dining room without having to ask for extra.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAvWGrHVIvaB29_Is0vaWekZUd9sAm5kAgkisJ&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Sammy Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBJMF7OKrde3n-1RDPQZZJjqfy5A3iAdhYJ8WjDWi_FmppCvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"App doesn't accept your money, deals don't load, baconator has almost no bacon and was soggy. This is not a one-off experience.

Update: I got very sick after eating here, not a pleasant experience. Avoid this Wendy's if you can","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPT3t7_LbTExh8YS6mpQ_wzevlhDebtBkGA5RjK&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Gurjeet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC0R3TCdF8VTtMgu6gvYzUwaVbtbm02rf9YcNk8eZ2ERHN-Qkl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"cleaniness is zero. I saw staff standing idle in the window but there was garbage full inside the restro. The sitting was really bad. Tables were not clean, there were flies in the store. Unhygenic","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvwgFFxkOM1mJGYH-vNyAcBUV3UQzXQmoNd4tp&fid=0x0:0xf4ceb47c30b2e520"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Bryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRidrZ1cEyLmbrN8TmygXBul8WYjPnNLvi6euVJbKaYHzdO-QaUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wendy's consistently delivers great fast food with a variety of options to suit any craving. The fresh, never frozen beef burgers are always juicy, and their crispy fries are a perfect side. The Spicy Chicken Nuggets are a must-try for anyone who loves a bit of heat. I also appreciate their wide range of salads and healthier alternatives for when I want something lighter. Friendly service, fast drive-thru, and reliable quality make Wendy's a solid choice every time.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Everything made in house. House smoked and cured meats + salmon.

Free range eggs 100
Blueberry Pancakes 100
Pork Belly 100
Pulled Pork 100

Blows away all of the fancy brunch spots in Van, it‚Äôs not even close.

Recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGrzH0QxhEA1nLX35uZjQwJZPLnidgtKTXIqXH&fid=0x0:0x6075da54d0f16636"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Miss Mayhem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGowE1po-uzevgz4y-llWcltZGBd0Jj1Qx_2rqJzm0bNHjXwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The breakfast was so tasty! I didn‚Äôt want it to end. Highly recommend this place. If it‚Äôs busy you‚Äôll have to wait outside so make sure you choose a nice day! Nice atmosphere and friendly staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZt6LQ6w6dhTo2dMiuEs9yvCHHE3qNKiWrmiDR&fid=0x0:0x6075da54d0f16636"],"When":"2024-4-9"},{"Name":"Rob A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5iHCDcXnWRHfHj4-jkqdudvb5w0x1zWoPJtLQCzFoKOU9xt4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don‚Äôt sleep on the awesome dinner menu at RED WAGON‚Äî but be warned, side effects may include post-meal dreamlike states of fluffy mashed potato and gravy delight.

We all know red wagon for breakfast, but if you haven‚Äôt gone for the dinner menu you are seriously missing out! Brad and team are serving up an amazing rotation of seasonal comfort food that will knock your socks off ‚Äî skip the brunch lineup and walk right into this spot for dinner most nights of the week!

Last night we had an **amazing** in house made French-style pate/terrine, following by a Caesar salad (complete with house smoked lardon), then we shared the steak frites with brined peppercorn + the pork cheek bourguignon ‚Äî the pork cheek, just added to the menu, quickly became the STAR dish to fight over when sharing.

Prior to this visit I had the smash burger and the bistro (wet) burger and both were fantastic. I will put red wagon‚Äôs burgers up against any Vancouver burger establishment (I‚Äôve tried them all) for the WIN. My take is that they aren‚Äôt trying to copy other‚Äôs burgers styles and are just having fun bring you what they like so you can join them in burgerville.

Also a wicked cocktail and beer selection, and I haven‚Äôt even mentioned the dessert. Butterscotch custard is one of my favs but the creative assortment of milkshakes will always set you straight too.

So‚Ä¶ go support a real local business, put your money in a real neighborhood and real local team, and be happy eating awesome food made from scratch that leaves you feeling fully satisfied and is still worth the $$ value!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM60BgUDdb6bpFd-96TeEqtBrbunM0r5CVEihsH&fid=0x0:0x6075da54d0f16636"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Alex Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKw6vbDp2wwnwGTgY3u4AHRVGKyyIunXuhDwQ_GXEbd3GqTyiat=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I finally got the chance to have breakfast here and it did not disappoint. I ordered the Super Trucker - the pork belly was succulent and went very well with the eggs and potatoes. I'll try the pulled pork next time which will be a nice excuse to come back! The pancakes were also delicious - thick and fluffy while having subtle crispy exterior.

Service was attentive as my coffee was constantly topped up. The diner's open and rustic atmosphere has a relaxing setting, especially for a wet, wintry day in the city. I look forward to my next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzn9WuurS3hu4KULmkFwOhXqwlHWy64Cy-SZVc&fid=0x0:0x6075da54d0f16636"],"When":"2023-12-1"},{"Name":"Denny Hui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuGFgsc9U61TCKDV21ZHXILH-aGrlI-hjZswBeAYg3LhKf97Y3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried a new place for brunch. Red Wagon Cafe staff we very friendly and welcoming. Atmosphere/decor was bright, lively and very comfortable.

We ordered Eggs Bennie, the Super Trucker and Wagon Burger.  Pull pork that came with Eggs Bennie was dry but overall, it was OK.

The Super Trucker, subbed pull pork for bacon. The bacon was delicious, pancakes light and pork belly had a nice crisp to it. Overall, satisfying and filling dish. Maybe a bit too big a dish, they do have just Trucker selection, less meats.

The burger was also delicious. My son loved it!

Overall, great place to have brunch. We'll definitely be back to try out some other items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCRN6PjV4MklaoiTMuIkcR343hBWL2wNcGM_X7&fid=0x0:0x6075da54d0f16636"],"When":"2023-6-25"}]

Macdonalds makes us pay extra for bags, so just do better with your service at least!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachana Gurung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLXzRzO8XH_Ab4lCSTdihtxpb_krNRbvghrkGgxrYRveAIaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The employees were not even wear Fish net. They were so unhygienic and the place was very dirty. The security guard just stood there doing nothing. This place either needs to shut down or work on being better. Really concerned for health and wellbeing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBmqIRI5XvyTw1cIC9nxjg1FyB62kgEpDV9JzggKt76VhbVNE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I love affogato! I ordered a delicious cone of ice cream and a single shot of espresso in a big cup. Now I had everything I needed to make an amazing affogato. Just put the ice cream into the cup using the wooden spoon you can get from McDonald's, and you‚Äôre all set for a chill time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sky Rosling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWl8l_ZHjHeTFxAdYV9u12SGLIIgbhCL_ijAteXF1s0_mJLr_ky=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"McDonald's isn't what it used to be. You might as well go to a decent restaurant, for the same prices that they're charging now. Every location I go to is full of garbage, sticky floors, and just obvious lack of concern for cleanliness. If this is how the lobbies are, imagine how disgusting where you food is being cooked is.

I'm done.","Images":null,"When":""}]
