user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Megh Raz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ4q-z4LFs37HL-LH9u0JenlekZ4kvp37NW_mrc_ElfMJTIDnP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love the chicken at Jollibee! Their spicy chicken is perfectly crispy and flavorful. They served my favorite drink, pineapple juice, which complemented the meal perfectly. The sauce they provide is awesome and adds an extra kick to the already delicious chicken. The view is also fantastic you can see Mount Pleasant and downtown from the restaurant. The service was fast and friendly, making the overall experience delightful. I highly recommend Jollibee to anyone craving tasty, well cooked chicken and refreshing drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0Bm6dPsRhLGc7diP3oHrHMOodQN-0_orYaj2M&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Just Me Traveling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX18amg9WNM9rF8Fs9axj8FE9tNtrVpXPgaMIl0yMbfuZ56ahzt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried Jolibee in Vancouver for the first time. The Broadway branch have a lot of seating area inside and few outside.
The staff were nice and the service was quick.
I ordered the 2 pcs chicken with mashed potato side. I had one regular and one spicy.
The first thing I noticed, the chicken pieces was quite small.
The chicken was crunchy as expected for a deep fried chicken. It was also moist, but I find it lacking in flavor. The regular one is a bit bland, the spicy one is better. I can taste some heat but also lacking in flavor.
I did not like the mashed potato, jt was smooth n it same problem as the chicken, it was bland.
The gravy taste good :)
Overall, it was ok but I prefer Popeyes chicken. It was good to try though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_t9-z1Zwn7OkabffD9kHuTLn-fTv9Ve2R3px0&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"toffy concepcion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYhf6f6Tr-b7ekbkXxFz9ueDreb1BCkopv3RQXbcpm54DeMfYl5g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I normally don't give bad reviews, but there were several shortcomings. I ordered a 2 burger combo with a Jolli spaghetti upgrade. The burger steak was cold at about 24C which surprised me because burgers are terrible with cold fat. It was promptly replaced but I discovered the problem, the gravy was cold and it was cooling the burgers. Luckily the replacement burger steaks were hot enough to warm the gravy. Considering the premium  prices for the quantity served, I expected better. The Pancit palabok skimped on the toppings and egg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRZfOn5uT508N7RS0chrT11kRGkJPaheQDM6Kq&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Autumn_Kiko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1zcZdU411-b8f5Fcx7HImynMifJ7qg-_yzjSJzTLgmhJaggW_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"For a fried chicken plac√© it‚Äôs ok.  The best item for me was obviously the chicken.  I did like the flavour profile.  The other dishes not so much.  However all my Filipino friends love the other dishes.   It reminds them of home.  For me it‚Äôs just the chicken.  But I do recommend them for that.  It‚Äôs just that there are so many fried chicken options in this city.  I know I know. I‚Äôll get roasted for not giving Jollibee higher praise.  Sorry chaps","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1OybNa9qb7AoP4dCdNDO06TMZ3-H7RlXHfBU4&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Jyn San Miguel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUOliweXs_wImUTvRSH64GMR_26U6jitTvJkokXQXsS9NcE1JA-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience at Jollibee, thanks to Lance! He was incredibly friendly and efficient, making sure my order was accurate and served promptly. His cheerful attitude added a personal touch to the fast-food experience. Keep up the great work, Lance!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFwkTVuFjy5cO8LldhqnHkApFNAfXiMGgsH4a_&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Ronald Gonzales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu_qMBYRQzMxPvC1VqPxURH-6i0LZqoUY9DdNjVP7URT75_JU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My go to place when I‚Äôm craving for that juicy-licious and crispy-licious Jollibee Chicken joy. The staff are warm and friendly, the food that I ordered is warm, fresh and delicious. We ordered the Spicy Chicken sandwich with fries and pineapple juice and a Ube Dessert Pie. As well as my nostalgic childhood favorite Jolly Spaghetti with it‚Äôs sweet savoury flavour and the irrestible Spicy Chicken sandwich which has the perfect blend of flavour and kick enhanced by the soft fluffy bun, the crisp tender chicken breast and the jalopeno peppers surrounded by the signature spicy mayo. It‚Äôs like heaven in your taste buds. The Ube Pie much like its O.G. sibling Peach Mango Pie lives up to the hype with its crunchy flaky outside crust and soft warm and taro like sweetness in the middle. What can I say about the pineapple juice, it‚Äôs like summer in a cup. Cool & refreshing. I‚Äôve gone here on my lunch break with family, friends & co-workers. Being centrally located between Cambie & Broadway. Close to Sky Train, City Hall & VGH. Jollibee truly feels like home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPSG9StuC0X4F3qUvJgEuMqBtNu798HGgd1KwN&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Asimov C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlK1Ddp9SlXQAmYnBYRUpOnRwspEIip3hgYKsyK1tYRO5fPmaC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"First time trying it and it was disappointing. I ordered through DoorDash. It felt overhyped, like Popeyes. While the skin was crisp, it seemed like the oil was old‚Äîfresh oil usually results in a lighter color. The herb taste of the skin wasn‚Äôt to my liking, though others might enjoy it. The mashed potatoes tasted like powdered ones, the gravy was nothing special, and the fries were super greasy and soft (probably due to delivery). I‚Äôm glad I satisfied my curiosity, but I won‚Äôt be ordering again. I prefer Church‚Äôs (when they used fresh oil) and Shawn‚Äôs Chicken in Richmond (which uses fresh, not frozen, chicken). Overall, $50 of disappointment.

I gave 5 stars for service and atmosphere because I used delivery but the food itself only 2 stars. I did felt like puking after having the mash potatoes and discarded all the left over. It was disgusting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsmphE6RBxFo6u6MQHsA-6X2sqq7zSn86cfZo5&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Emily Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEvwebxzOOvHfn2UnHwr4i_lsQ_4WBBcdmwEUmGOtZoyfwO9Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Since they‚Äôre known for their fried chicken, I thought their chicken sandwich would be nice too. Boy, was I disappointed. It was dry and lacked any sauce/veggies in between the buns. It was literally just a piece of fried chicken and a small dollop of mayonnaise sandwiched between some bread.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTd72_kwJr5t4wVNSAoMXATqlHGsEbxiQjHI1r&fid=0x0:0x1b70cbce4dc1e91d"],"When":"2024-3-8"}]

Additionally, the food always arrives with nothing on the side, and they don‚Äôt provide any ketchup or mayo unless you specifically ask for it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sebastian Starr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhSvOC5wDB6QLhdw6nycrdlj9Z6HiFg5pyiZeM7AxqVD1GaQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not too busy certain times of day, as was in and out today with a simple order. Lucky I gave this location 3 stars being very generous on that.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"iliya rad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILAb1ihu-HIrNGVx93vqZzOtGaxBlaJ3r6hTPlFPEd1u7V-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"30 min wait with 4 staff in the back, maybe 4 customers in the place.\nAnd I get a burger that's not even put together correctly ... literally not stacked correctly ... since when meat is on top of the burger bun.\nNeeds new management asap !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDxmAsvGCFPEcbFWTIoQ4aHzSONuVOdXKlmRv9\u0026fid=0x0:0x2bc399686dbec794"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Lee Peter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7UVItcL2yy7qutxCcuFw6eG1GmLYCqqXjDF5Geiod69gJmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In a nutshell, the restaurant was really nice. The worker treated me in a kind way and gave me the bag. It was my first time of visiting Mcdonald's in Vancouver so I was surprised by its service. [{"Name":"Tom McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0J48kC1hZM1V1aRsvHOZVDophlDmEISwqhKMFe94oVeHk06c2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Downlow Chicken Shack - Commercial Street

‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è

My son and I visited Downlow Chicken on Commercial Street, and it was an experience worth every bite. The atmosphere is casual and laid-back, perfect for a relaxed meal. We were greeted warmly by the staff, who were helpful in explaining the menu and helping us choose the best options for our preferences.

We both went for their signature fried chicken sandwiches, and they did not disappoint. The chicken was incredibly crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside, with just the right amount of spice. The flavor packed a punch but wasn‚Äôt overwhelming, making it one of the best fried chicken experiences we‚Äôve had. The house-made sauces added a nice kick to the sandwiches, complementing the bold flavors of the chicken.

We also tried a side of the fries, which were seasoned perfectly and served piping hot. The portions were generous, so we definitely left feeling satisfied. The vibe in the restaurant was energetic and fun, with a steady stream of people coming in for their fried chicken fix.

Downlow Chicken really lives up to the hype, and we will definitely be back for more. Whether you‚Äôre in the mood for a quick bite or a sit-down meal, it‚Äôs a must-try for any fried chicken lover. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM68B8XUqu13hFJ89993grC0BIeeLUyQmUefa-q&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"michellebrown4","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkEMyAsWWgzknYkLqMFS1yqiBkRorrtVjHSB73_uCTAPIwl3Rx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always fantastic chicken. The sides are very good too. I always get a sandwich and im happy when i get thigh meat. Not many spots to sit if you wanna eat there but its surrounded by nice parks so not too bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-bBYlNp33fBvD90DmU5VViY_5iWWYOcA8xJu_&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Maria Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvbESQ5VVhECE3DxzTqt9zJd2QEo0t29jmUjjJM-9Ox5shxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best fried chicken we‚Äôve ever had ( and we lived in TEXAS for 2 years)

The thigh was our fav but all was great & juicy!
Will def be back to try the jerk chicken burger.
Staff was so friendly and helpful too, great experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0LwjVIFpWF11EOMZEvu8KabBYQMM4-64KUDss&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"katelynn c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoqcwb_gcSeJsQp6Fk0xxFfLaz6Ca58KOlakGeP011yHdUWdF9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"the staff was really friendly and the food was AMAZING. both the normal fries and truffle fries were insane, especially with the DL sauce and truffle mayo sauce !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvc0iuYPqZaYAqNv-PKfpyi0Nnk1vlZJZRa9p3&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Mar M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPsU37lph3WCoUer9hGpW5esNjqO5X44hXw-f04YFWktsI5g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Best chicken sandwich in Vancouver by far! The fries are also great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNog2jHl3Qcrk7czCxGYQNe8UZU1sBhk2p-1SE1&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Keith Eastcott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk5BCUEJh42hOpsF-_OoCCbmyygcrHIJcijMiuq6slKML49qmN0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely the best most delicious chicken I've had. I honestly can't properly describe just how good the chicken is here. Spicy options available and they do spicy right. The restaurant is clean and the staff are always very friendly and welcoming. They do offer limited inside seating and also have a seating area outside as well. It's always pretty busy so I'm not the only one who loves it. You can order ahead or just order in-store.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_gH1W2K4ckqEXjVCqHeyEmufvs5lmgB2PKwpr&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"maggie o","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9A5PydPe7Tcx0vvDAgMCxpdBCWS4_34QTKzuvzWDEq4oQ02l7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my new standard for fried chicken. The team is loud and excited. They excel at communicating and it shows in the quality of their product.

Their house sauce is a MUST GET!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUQea1ec48Wks4-WJ-lnQBDqt3_Dal9ZQXpVNH&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Thomas Wilczynski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJD24Or0RUBGSuMLrdcePCdBXv8sl7ZLUknVBIS-JYZ_nACiVt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This eatery is out of this world! The chicken is addictive and the staff is lively. Many spice levels to choose from. I went here for a late lunch, but I heard that this place can get absolutely packed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY-BJ_yhsBR6LPs4ZZKKgdbGf6on6WHi2tikwi&fid=0x0:0x75969767dbca6887"],"When":"2024-11-11"}]

[{"Name":"Fiona Calwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGwYqtBbhui5t7-Q1b_CIuKjMulrwHAFM53dyE-aoHnRDzJNgXlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome little chicken place! We got there before the rush, we got to sit at one of the 2 tables and it was very cute. Iced sweet tea and all the chicken was pretty yummy! It was a little less salted then I would prefer but that's totally my own preference. Chicken legs were better than the burger IMO. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGOT_Ezu7vX1lPh-LbsXQ4vlYjxYN2wpyLqbE4&fid=0x0:0x3acaa5552ce0fe50"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Donald Overlander","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHkhUvtU4pxJdumyiSAcxjbcdGAGaHweKKGqPTFB4fZ5GX2Cx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Basically EVERYTHING is gluten free?!? Yes please. This place was on our 'must try' list almost a year ago when we planned things out... WORTH the wait ;) (and there wasn't much of a wait once we got there and ordered!)

Gluten Free FRIED chicken was delicious, fries (no cross contamination!?!) were perfectly crispy, and... The crispy chicken skins -for real- as good as anything we had in Kentucky/Tennessee BBQs stateside.

Would definitely recommend to anyone, but exceptional for any one with Gluten sensitivities.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM350d0oxNR4n2FsbeCjpJRcU7GSRAsiYOQi7bq&fid=0x0:0x3acaa5552ce0fe50"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Jacob Eggleton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKglmLD5rXwOjc8AHPEPB6gAEwPhBhb__7HRJ9SZ8w4UTzGyNa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had this for take out on the way home from work. I didn‚Äôt realize it was gluten free and really enjoyed the sandwich. The fries were perfect and I got a side of gravy which actually had a lot of flavour to it. The bigger part of the restaurant opens up at 4 if you plan on dining in. Also after reading some reviews I would recommend not ordering through Uber eats and just picking it up yourself if you can. Overall quick and delicious food. Price was alright","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1sahlb1j5FQ5bzKueDMqEpB0zj6VE30gmOMIP&fid=0x0:0x3acaa5552ce0fe50"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Rhiannon Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqf4gANIqc3hKm76zSE0AgzBsIJ5dO8Y2KAQIqO7tqkF-Ogn4Z7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went in to celebrate a birthday and have a gluten free meal! The food was exceptional! Everything we ordered was a flavourful and delicious. 4 of us at the table and we ordered - 3 chicken sandwiches,  2 loaded fries, chicken and waffles,  mac and cheese and 10 piece spicy nuggets.   Definitely our new favorite family restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMspRLGJKUiqmwqVMrnw7aJ3mdkYeQB532OczdV&fid=0x0:0x3acaa5552ce0fe50"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Amrita Nayak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgJ3b8LMBlPc7G1Rv8sy6cyH33IeJwYGYkw6c-i8ocBKF5odAKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you‚Äôre a fan of chicken and waffles, this spot is worth a visit, though it has its highs and lows. Here‚Äôs the breakdown:

**The Good:**
The waffles were a standout for me! They had jalape√±os baked into the batter, which added a unique kick to the flavor. It was such a creative twist that really elevated the dish. They also served the waffles with a seasoned butter that I absolutely loved‚Äîit had a savory, almost herby taste that complemented the spicy jalape√±o waffles perfectly.

**The Not-So-Good:**
I ordered the fried chicken with the chili flavor for an additional charge, but unfortunately, it didn‚Äôt meet my expectations. I was hoping for a hot, spicy variant of fried chicken with a crispy exterior, but what I got was chicken coated in a thick tangy chili sauce. It made the crispy outer layer of the chicken soggy, which took away from the classic fried chicken experience. This might just be a personal preference, but it wasn‚Äôt what I was expecting.

**The Atmosphere:**
The place is very small, with only two tables inside and a couple of metal benches outside. It‚Äôs more of a grab-and-go kind of spot than a sit-down restaurant. That said, the service was friendly and welcoming, which added to the overall experience.

Overall, the waffles and butter alone are worth trying, especially for those who enjoy bold flavors. As for the chicken, I‚Äôd recommend sticking to the classic version if you‚Äôre a fan of crispy fried chicken. Despite some misses, the friendly service and creative touches make this a spot to consider, especially if you‚Äôre in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNe5ZY4hwmQf_oikD85rPTql8i5glYE_syJS5yx&fid=0x0:0x3acaa5552ce0fe50"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Michelle McLatchy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFj-ARxSUyfWePV4Nuk15cm4O_3Q8U-RBQPIoKZE3tQUxFmzygKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's not cheap but very good. Every once in awhile I feel like fried chicken and as someone who can't have gluten this place is amazing. The chicken is great, the ribs are great, the hush puppies are a favourite. Thank you to whoever manages this place because I'm never ordering from here again üòÜ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_3dka4xgU0nuqOD0JHVxemWgvW8Dalqp1faOB&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Sub like Scottie! For face value, you can't really go wrong with a veggie patty sub on promo with Subway rewards scheme is pretty solid.
Yum grub, fresh bread and a good amount of healthy veggies and salad is dope.
Server was also super friendly at this chain, very approachable and patient, nice dude.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSVFvWgMoEBpAX5GyTPCndcOfJYn9DDLJN9ET9&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2024-1-26"},{"Name":"toffy concepcion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYhf6f6Tr-b7ekbkXxFz9ueDreb1BCkopv3RQXbcpm54DeMfYl5g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This subway has the best service in Downtown Vancouver.  It used to be a nicer area but this subway is still a well lighted spot to eat a good cheap sandwich.  They're the only Subway that doesn't rush you through selecting the condiments on your sandwich or trying to skimp on everything.  They will even toast your sandwich before putting the condiments.  Really nice touch.  Friendly crew also.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiHSiN6HM3EDkQvUvx7DLk3zM-Dq9cryHnnYVb&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"Subhash Masson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2WvCOvAcdMo4C18y-KP7_EQGwCPtrmO5uMOn8KgXOF2Tjorst=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely pathetic subway experience i ever had. Please avoid this store
I ordered 2 foot longs 1 veggie patty and the other one chicken teriyaki.
The staff is so rude didn't even know how to deal with customer's and even the owner was rude didn't know how to interact with customers.
The staff didn't wore gloves while preparing the sandwich when asked she said i didn't touch you sandwich.
Even the washroom wasn't working.
Literally worst subway experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxDYHyt36eePwntyJ3g5D8RkuyubObsQm7WBKc&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2022-8-2"},{"Name":"MORI N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmh-25mC5oA1PFMMA_52ysg1xmB302WDBqAM9LeMqrXCsb_9pPTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have you ever been at a Subway, watched them make your sandwich and wanted to just climb over the counter and do it yourself....cuz they were making a mess of it?

That's pretty much me at every other Subway when I do go, but not this time.

I walked in...store was immaculately clean, the service professional, friendly and fast. My footlong was Super fresh...the bread and all the ingredients. The girl that made my sandwich made it like she was making it for herself. Time, attention and care.

You know what this resulted in?
A Sub that I had for dinner that makes me want to go back to that Subway...and I will.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzAeoosn2f1tttjbGWbGWkuRgKsS6mYF6H8ZZA&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2023-6-13"},{"Name":"Manni Toor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmE1OlzRDPNAGK9ArIBTmEaqwr9ZldAVNA6SeX5ounTd5B2A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Visited this place few times on Tuesday evening. A young lady, Neha with tons of attitude took my order. Upon requesting to use a clean knife and refrain from contaminating my veggie sandwich with any sort of meats. She said ‚Äúyou are not allergic, and if you are you shouldn‚Äôt be eating subway‚Äù. This isn‚Äôt the way to treat a customer. She particularly have a worst sandwich build, worst customer service and no ethical sense at all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kameron Thanas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPcE30200yuEen3lacsZO9WItzbb-XR8wP018JWs9FX3iXrk4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I‚Äôm so sorry, but nothing was actually toasted, my sandwich is wet? The kind lady creating my sandwich just had no clue, and her trainer just left her to guess what was going on. I got over charged 3$ but didn‚Äôt want to cause a scene so I left it but getting home to a wet mess I couldn‚Äôt eat was incredibly disappointing. Contact me for any more info!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Venecia Regalado Bail√≥n","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKDaLY6vXyEh9NqBKVrogrBL7WMj7hBoa87zswnZRDY6tD6mk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently renovated, the cleanest subway in downtown I‚Äôve been to, plus the guy was very friendlyü•∞","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQxs2rh268S6siZK7B7GMhUjDSqvV2EgvCMhqB&fid=0x0:0xaf0f44acd8388e9e"],"When":"2024-6-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jessie M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfV8fdnzXGmeOfbTj7nd3OtqK8e2FDgmxbhWehw2T-4g3QINC5yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Normally I don‚Äôt think a chain like A&W deserves my time reviewing but this location‚Äôs chicken wraps are the freshest I‚Äôve had. Melt in your mouth good. And the guy who served me today (around 4pm?) was really nice, courteous and seemed to value me as a customer (not on autopilot like most fast food chain staff I‚Äôd encounter on a normal basis). Definitely gonna go out of my way to come to this location again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXo5sPZ67s_mnhJwZ79b2vBa8twlqYbk9eZujv14dBdLN9-xEyftw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not a lot of light coming into the eating space so it‚Äôs a little dark. The area is a little sketchy so it doesn‚Äôt always feel safe here either. Other than that, the food is what you would expect from the franchise.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7ukcFstNni-xvl71bE_YfLOFPGZtMWdVIhFNg&fid=0x0:0xf727c0cc9b817deb"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Akshesh Doshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBVJ8F96SVQclD72pqTOfMoK8nBhWAwxE5Shu_8ugYVlBFqtfARQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice burgers with a couple of vegetarian options available. The beyond meat burger is their classic and I was told that peri peri burger is also vegetarian. Currently, they're also having a limited edition masala veggie burger.
Cooking time seems a little slower, compared to other burger joints.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdmViQQqZJ5D7rlfVytoSMfLd_O_IpMKSKYrus&fid=0x0:0xf727c0cc9b817deb"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Atticus Courtoreille","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDPVSDzysaFcZ6EOv7aEnxQUc78pf_GxGqTDf7LiYG03TyOTVwSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Workers are not accodmating for people who have suffered a stroke or or some sort of TBI such as myself who can't read, write or explain things easily without some sort of assistance. Usually when I order from places most people understand English well enough to take my order without confusing me.

I walked in with my child and ordered a kids buddy burger with cheese meal, I asked for chocolate milk at the drink. When the order came I was given just a normal adult buddy burger with cheese, no fries and the chocolate milk on the side. I can't read the orders on the screen without assistance. My kid can't read yet. So I was charged for the chocolate milk and buddy burger only. So I asked for a refund on those items and just be charged for the kids meal as a whole as I didn't need another drink. Just a KIDS BUDDY BURGER AND SMALL FRIES. The worker could not understand what I was saying, no matter how many times I tried to explain. She kept on asking me totally different things. I explained it 5 times and the worker still couldn't understand what I was asking........................... whoever was working cashier tonight can't even understand oder directions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Candice Raines","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzjnJ5U_F0-oAUJqtZ4oFpCWRZewadHmFd1BiXv5fltA6STC4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could give the service less stars I would. Stopped here on our way back to the ferry. We were hassled by a homeless lady outside .. twice. Not the worst part though. We could see the staff from the road laying on the counters talking. We decide to go in and the garbage was overflowing, the tables were dirty and the staff just stared at us instead of saying anything.  We approached the counter to order, still no hello. Ordered our food and they seemed annoyed we wanted to stay in to eat. My husband tried to use the washroom but it ‚Äúdidn‚Äôt work‚Äù after she tried the lock a few times. We receive our food and the fries were clearly old. Stale and hard. Hardly warm. I ordered a bacon and egged and there was less than 1 peice of bacon on it and then I bit into something super hard I thought I broke my tooth üò¨ super disappointed in this location. There was no one else on the restaurant. Spend that time at minimum emptying the garbage.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TMAC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnLj6mKuLqNX_50_MUunJXGn9t13mqGeB7RHgWTUaq6hBFwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am disappointed in this A&W. I love A&W, but this location is horrible. The harsh browns were greasy and tasted like months' old oil, so disgusting. And the sandwich was slapped together which completely came apart in the bag, not to mention the horrible taste. Had I known, I would have never set foot in this location. It has almost ruined A&W for me. The place also smelled really dirty as soon as I walked through the doors. This location needs to either clean up their act of shut down.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samarth Bajaj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2AIpSfd2EWbC6taXlwpqy3fQyilqDImGYi2FrcLw9PVcPzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"the staff here is very rude, especially the guys named Hussain. They guy didn‚Äôt
let me use the washroom even after showing him the proof that I had a medical condition and cannot control my bladder. I even bought food just so that I can use the washroom. The guys here were super rude and didn‚Äôt care about my condition at all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNMLiwAnKS16_eARJ-JLGwfWL9L3WaXSWXYeTexdrqIDBLLFEl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Hashbrowns are great from any A&W. I love buddy burgers from every A&W except this location. Multiple times I have been given burgers where the patties are not cooks properly. The patties should not be red in the middle. This typically happens if I get a burger in the morning. Lunch time the staff tends to cook them properly. 2) I ordered the seafood sub. Misleading photo led me to think I was in for a hearty meal. Wrong again. There was hardly any meat at all. And no I am not kidding. A small can of store bought flavored tuna would be significantly more in comparison ! Double ugh !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMP6YYhjD0n8I4eHOlDu9CJmz8yQNrBm6jkc1AhYiQcdtoaFjP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered a Steak and Cheese sub via Uber Eats and the bread was terrible... a huge piece of bread that was too big for the amount of fillings and  flaking apart like it wasn't fresh. Subway  and Quizno's are far superior in every way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gil Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdHf-bMjyJVRJpxr0SqP9cx9EFIg38mPoS2j56YvJ7U0Rkiw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Usually I like the food here, but my last experience soured that greatly. [{"Name":"Melanie E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR0bJcxqNkJt-i1wxCH3EaQXevncA86panZszfT__NAs_0KWRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I hadn‚Äôt been here in years and it still has good value food that‚Äôs delicious! We came here at round 7 pm on a week day and there was a lineup. It was worth the wait.

Food: 4/5 - we all ordered different vermicelli dishes. The spring rolls are  a must order. They give you good portions of food. There are both vegetarian and non vegetarian options.

Service: 3/5 - they were too busy to be attentive

Ambiance- 4/5 - nice decor. A great place to dine near the PNE or if you‚Äôre in the neighborhood.

Parking - free street parking after 6 pm","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWkKkdPl2cCFSEfikaWjYZ7GkUU_adw1v0i6xK&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Lily Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj-rxgq_V1Q4saFv72RQW5O--t_V1VvUJqtWUExhkFTfKEPMJh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good broken rice and BBH. As a local Vietnamese born and raised, I approved these 2 dishes. No wonder why they are fully packed at dinner time","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM66hhPmRCzs4oa__CbySNckGyA3ieZCnZ_ypWz&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Jacquelyn Richards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVONU_YBYFNIeoLEzA8ujcDmbFhTZmt2O3a7IpPqrF91KJfdd-f=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give Le Petit Saigon 10 stars if I could. This is the best Vietnamese restaurant and the best pho broth in Vancouver I‚Äôve had.

I would come almost every weekend with my dad and usually order the same thing and the servers knew exactly what we wanted to order and all of our little accommodations/requests without having to ask, they‚Äôre super friendly and attentive, so the service is really great here.

The pho broth is deep, rich, and flavourful. The noodles are always cooked perfectly, the spring rolls are amazing, all of the vermicelli dishes we‚Äôve tried have been great, the seafood soup is incredible, and the bun bo hue is also the best I‚Äôve had in Vancouver.

I‚Äôve been coming here for the past 12 years and have never had a bad experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxMGQN_utqewaQIK1p4_RWlLvv7QQMhGnAx9x2&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Amy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjXHHF3vPFKXXTvrLI9L9GLLX-x9A-g0rYHpm8C9R04tRthXY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went to Le Petit Saigon on Hastings after a hiking day. It was a bit hot as it‚Äôs facing South. A large fan was turned on facing the inside of main dining area.  TV had a soccer game on. Took 1 star off Atmosphere due to the strong smell (of beef soup base ?) that day in the dining area.

I ordered rare beef, brisket, and tendon pho noodles. Condiments included diced green onion and cilantro, bean sprouts, basal and 2 wedges of lime. I seldom see green onion on the condiment plate now and I really like the additional green onion in my pho. If you need Vietnamese fish sauce, you have to ask the server for it.

The pho bowl was refreshing and of good portion. Yummy and tender beef. The veggies weee fresh and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbhVR0i1MdQOMxLvhh7uOe3Y9lEZ9Vq97-z2FS&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Nicolas Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxCKAreGx67VSJZEieVsVD3BEZWX5PIEfeqAwrDtBfWBdP92qotg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chicken noodle soup and spring rolls were simply delicious, full of flavour. They chargrilled the chicken!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtE9qsFNyNAH61HJP-pVZqi51JwuMHWaxafGf5&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Andy Chiang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6Ytd6jvLjiUIKjc2DLdidLuwgHbgPUD4GPhFuPOLEoqlZ2vbh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Solid pho option in Vancouver. I order here frequently on Uber Eats and finally had a chance to visit in person.

The portions of the bun are solid, and they do not skimp out on the meats either. The pho is packed with greens as well, can‚Äôt go wrong with plenty of cilantro.

Definitely worth a visit if you‚Äôre in the mood for pho and in the area. It‚Äôs very clean and modernized.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNie7BU_m0qYW-vLRRBZMeR91h8X7JBe_AdLEi9&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Rachel Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqzyahGpYVl9TNKM5uQDsIQgYnpD5kXfG_HAM4KRUfbZoVE2I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you for the great service and food I had at this restaurant. The waiter was very friendly and accommodating with our drinks. And the atmosphere of the restaurant was very nice and clean! What great restaurant to visit before my Niki concert today! So convenient that restaurant was within walking distance to PNE, and was able to stumble across it on our way there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0lCh5x_AXdKcdxXLmTYEI4nr1CSCyFULeDY1b&fid=0x0:0xf5946034f432d38d"],"When":"2023-8-11"},{"Name":"Maddex Auchter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFbdc_Jpu9lgyVAtc9ZyFFDgYAW-nKM0j28CpXDABNK7dJ1A0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, absolutely incredible, everyone was very friendly, food was out in good time, and everything is a fair price. I ordered the Whole Mozzarella and it was sooooo good! Super crunchy and the inside was stuffed generous with mozzarella that literally melts and pulls when I bit on it. I had the cheddar corndog, but I think the regular beef corndog might have been a better choice, as the cheddar hotdog was quite rich. The exterior/dough was wonderfully crunchy and savory. Plus, the option to customize the sauce adds an interesting touch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrWF4AeZB6TzsuInah6QyepLx2qTy2YG9tM-w9&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Bernie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPXTBFQGy4UZogf6r0hGxUGZ8fvtwePPN5iicbAtQksaWtpwOP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Chung Chun has been a family favourite for years. They have kept a very good standard of food quality ‚Äòtil now. We got a box to fill up our cravings.  It's a variety of original Changchun (beef), Gamsung potato (beef&chicken sausage), ramen chip (beef), double cheese(beef&chicken), and whole mozzarella. All are delicious and satisfying.They also have drinks but the  downside  is there‚Äôs no place to eat. It‚Äôs a challenge to enjoy the food while hot unless you are parked nearby.  Customer service is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3OGP393MeiOWpGyq5Pk5v8Z_WXeNiRgayYKov&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Stuart Zatorski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSDRYqSOt57Z5cwdG02l7ycmr0cXhkj4Am4zko8chGPj1z4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Servers were exceptionally nice, corn dogs were exactly what you expected and wanted, waffle fries were a bit small but still done perfectly. Did the volcano corn dog, great flavour, crispy outside, tons of condiments, I‚Äôll be back!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqmRG8sahyTmRiuXyNgBHFc1lb6Vlv4Ct28AlP&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Eva Zia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJp1CScTOq-jdIBVBA-K4f_r74TZU-kRd9MclConVIiSCPfy3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the hot dogs here; they're crunchy and delicious with lots of toppings and various sauces. If you love corn dogs, definitely give them a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpWAIoW27rm31VuLKHugnCgiFtARTihO2Sj_L8&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Shayan Emami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMRtVjgeF0Xa8B9cN17jFb1xX_jsiTrD6AvufKoea_Jc3WiF0j=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried this wired hotdog place for the first time. I ordered half mozzarella half beef and it waffle fries. Half mozzarella one was interesting and delicious before I get to the meat part. Fries was nice too. Customer service was respectful as well. The down side is there us no place in and out of the restaurant to eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnZSUv2jg2kQx_GhJJ9EyaOswt0kpeXDkWJrOu&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZkgGiC5-j-O-VzVgprqqwroxXjpq6xanKiXxkhY0oFzPVaY4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This tiny corner serves up tasty rice hotdogs, where one is big enough to be a light meal for a small person.   This is takeaway-only as there's no place to sit, and there's a table for standers but the place is really too small to support anyone eating in.

Because the hotdog is covered with rice mochi, it doesn't feel very heavy or oily, even when deep-fried.

I tried the half sausage, half cheese dog.

I liked the mozzarella in it: The mozzarella comes out soft, stringy and melted, which goes well with the crunchy shell.  It's very comforting/feel-good to eat.

The beef hotdog inside isnt anything special, it doesnt taste like 100% meat, it's just kind of soft processed meat... But the outside of the dog makes up for it. So the meat is definitely not costco hotdog level, it is almost like luncheon meat texture, so that could bother some people. It wasn't meaty enough for me. (Probably a typical "American sausage" texture in other korean/asian food places too when they incorporate foreign ingredients, like into hotplates and hotpots etc. Its supposed to be a bit light i guess?)

Next time ill prob try something with the chicken in it to see what it tastes like too.

Extra toppings come at a price, I think $1-2 extra.  But
there are many sauces and cheese/butter powders for free you can choose that they put on for you. I think i took some chipotle mayo and bbq and some of the powders.

Popular place for young people as it's also hard to find any takeout food under $10 that actually tastes good. If you are very hungry, you might need two dogs that would make it about $15 pre-tax.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqu3F3gthiT_HezhQmGV4arsYPLukOq1ldEbSe&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Phoebe Yoon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBobFZYdkUy0kQUzZxOyqZ7NGAyh6Lk-gQMCkP71H6TcT_C47A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is delicious and definitely an affordable snack or meal. They start around $6 and you can add however many sauces and powders on top. The staff working were all so sweet and welcoming. Just be aware there‚Äôs no seating inside so it‚Äôs take out only~","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwKxU-HxFnswkibCGPSctyKMBeu4vcg8bo2C-h&fid=0x0:0x718bbd575e412752"],"When":"2024-7-7"}]

I ordered beyond burger and it was terrible!
The staff are nice but the food is not good at all!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvxt45tzQ2VLTCc-eaasin_6ycSNFGCLZQSh6q&fid=0x0:0xf83e51d6d5d63268"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"James C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVybEIM-9WvzTrgb4D7iW0FR0lZmn3QLOqzC7hXg-uLtO4DOmcv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I like to try new foods and normally enjoy being adventurous. Sometimes, however, an experiment does not work out. This happened to me when visiting a Fatburger in a food court near Vancouver's waterfront.

I ordered a California Veggie with fried egg and several other toppings, and after taking a few bites I did not feel well. I ended up throwing my meal in the garbage, which is something I almost never do.

While I give Fatburger an A+ for creativity, the taste did not appeal to me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMHVPMy0JZaEftZWA9nuc9fUO_uCU3z2ZI7YGO&fid=0x0:0xf83e51d6d5d63268"],"When":"2023-5-31"},{"Name":"Chris F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5iETqIQBeQI1auEFM0Tc1cLHlBlPg-u_xQZRZgDTvUjh6noO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Love love love.  Fresh produce and a juicy juicy patty every time. That flavour!! I love the California burger with cheese and bacon and avocado and a fried egg.

They do breakfast too.

A little pricey but with that flavour and the freshness I think you get what you pay for.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg4ax3D9B_ZQOfe-Om7b-ljBdhUpraf8WYAx8F&fid=0x0:0xf83e51d6d5d63268"],"When":"2020-1-31"},{"Name":"Andy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwnYBUxFWoUS3xdDztCFskNaxF_aO6KHKt-MnZL_Co0Byk_UXp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I've been wanting to try Fatburger for a long time and so we decided to check this place out while we were at waterfront. I gotta say the chicken crisper burger was pretty average and small and the fries were nothing special. The strawberry milkshake was good but the donuts were terrible. They were overly fried and very hard and just soaked everything in oil. The first batch we had was very hard and stale (?) and were not fluffy inside. The worker remade these for us and they looked slightly better but were still very tough and oily. I should've stuck to McDonalds across from them. Oh well, lesson learned. Fatburger is not good bang for your buck but I'd come back for their milkshake only. Pictures are attached. The donuts are the 2nd batch so they look better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIAjwS9hwOOcfirrZzU7aUjEUyeORYJ-cUb9Es&fid=0x0:0xf83e51d6d5d63268"],"When":"2022-9-5"},{"Name":"Philipp F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9nqyB9QhIvgWZCTwO_crnQSVBV2CgRq8LaNqyZKCm8eZE1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Burger is ok but cannot recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHyxLLzj4C0wVpjRKdox5t_Vj4czmLOtd_LVY4&fid=0x0:0xf83e51d6d5d63268"],"When":"2024-12-13"}]

But in this particular Subway, an employee named Harman told me that I have to pay extra, even though I didn't choose any additional veggies. Even she was very rude","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Disha Shah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcaKuudjp36zO9_RKlZYQrsDC7bLWjjp2RGsByYcaKc-gI4Y3drA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The server was a girl was very rude. When I told her to spilt my bill into 2 she very rudely replied that is not an option. When I further requested her to be aware of these things she replied that I should go to the place where they do spilt the bills and told me to get out of the store. She also did not give me the receipt, I had to request her for the receipt. I had an awful experience with the store and the lady server w as not even ready to give her name.","Images":null,"When":""}]

The food was simply outstanding: fresh, juicy, and incredibly delicious. The kebab melted in my mouth, and the uniquely flavored poutine left me amazed.

I also want to highlight the service: the staff was incredibly polite, friendly, and attentive to every detail. The atmosphere is cozy, and you can feel that every guest is valued here.

I definitely recommend this place to anyone who wants to enjoy high-quality food and excellent service. I can‚Äôt wait to visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXbdIoWS2pOUs3c4yZwpq7K17mwr9OXM8KFpBz&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"RhE ‚ÄúR‚Äù","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhxn3fL4a0hIxT8HJcx09RB-3VeIdPygNVtHUnZO0hk197vWIP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to try some local specialty food, something that defines the flavor of Vancouver. Granville Kebab & Poutine seemed to be a well-liked, popular choice. Now I know why!!
The food was worth the trip to downtown Vancouver.
I was greeted warmly as I entered the door.  The gentleman behind d the counter was quick to take my order and offer suggestions. Superb service!!
The beef poutine was Excellent!!  The  meat was tender and very flavorful. The cheese curds melted through and mixed with the brown gravy, coating the fries, creating a delightful mix of flavors!!
The mixed kebab plate had a generous serving of beef and chicken on a fresh pita.  Both meats were tender, juicy, and seasoned wonderfully. The mixed salad was crispy and served with a very tasty dressing.
If you are in the Vancouver area and need some delicious food, this is a perfect choice!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhfTLRZ6uxtsHlYOKT9BknqPbvXG_k3nMxQI1q&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Emily Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzcgEV5nus0hzaBx5tUMeLvYjjt5vu9E_0khJ0y_etciWRdCjW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The guys who work here are super nice, decently sized clean seating area compared to other kebab options, and the food was AWESOME - we got beef poutine and beef wrap. The staff were super friendly too. 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjSZx1AHIZteSX53e2zsQN7BiUC6CE-uuF9ZSG&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Chris Hausermann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqFO4oG4XJj3OkmTyO7b_8SA19JmEqyu7mH7khiyZ7BYY9P4o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The flavors and the freshness of the food are just top notch. Staff are as friendly as can be. üòÄ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGHWRdOy0Q2JHiFj9wzmlWJ3ALnB2aG-G6KtHC&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Robin Vaughn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaz7fOGXT-P4C1FOMBJT2aooeML-6wU3TdX55kGuSIbBN67Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôm in town for Taylor Swift and ended up on this side of town late night at around 2am . The food here is absolutely outstanding! Honestly, the service was as well! I went to move some crumbs from my table and was instantly humbled by the staff already right behind me! The place had an amazing smell and they cooked everything to order.

My biggest complaint is that now I‚Äôm going to be in Dallas Texas dreaming about this place for the rest of my days üò≠ the tzatziki recipe must‚Äôve came straight from heaven.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSj8Hb-R4p6k3JeBXOt31j0zDdv9pgciZajXY6&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Iman Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY_It5dFbhJ3ahD3y8wnnvsyYECBdVwU0ipYiueTLf-0IgvGbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the large beef wrap. However, the wrap itself could be more generous. It's a skinny beef wrap, different from what I expected. I'd even say it's a normal portion, so if you're really hungry, it's probably better to go with the rice.

I looked at other reviews, and based on the photos, it seems they offer some nice dishes. So this time, instead of ordering delivery, I‚Äôll go there in person and try one of the rice dishes.

For now, the whole experience was a 4/5. üåØ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOswkNpSqig83LGtaD1ZslZRIElC-pRzSfwzQQ-&fid=0x0:0xad6f0e5370c08217"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Diwansh garg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBDLNd-YelP7jXuy3L91yVcGY5cXrJfY3yeneZ92CgyTIr94Ja=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was THE BEST poutine i have had EVER.

[{"Name":"cbw009","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcg6Qz_zo_Vvr7xtd6rezE3UVg5iHtNFJI7muaibGl99bUOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A welcome comfort food on a cold Vancouver evening.  We were visiting on a rain sodden winter and came across this delicious and healthy food bar. The spicy tomato soup was instantly a comfort food.  Also had Moroccan stew with brown rice and kale. Partner had meatball sandwich , which were fresh and tasty. A clean friendly place to eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_MPXuCHOMoVmJD3Sdk0okEGMdc1HroU0rvHwD&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Mafer Anticona","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfenwk-HhjETIAhpi6LAyTFGl__2S3lQytD96mm4p0PIBLsYWk0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I visited this place for the first time and ordered the soup and half-sandwich combo. The red chili soup was delicious, comforting, and felt homemade. However, the sandwich was disappointing. I got the chicken and avocado option, but it was basic: just a few pieces of chicken, some lettuce, and avocado that looked a bit brown. The bread was soft, but the sandwich lacked flavor, and the sauce was barely noticeable.

The service wasn‚Äôt great either‚Äîthe staff didn‚Äôt explain how the process worked, just handed me a number. While the soup was fantastic, the sandwich was underwhelming, and the overall experience didn‚Äôt impress me. It was convenient for a quick meal, but I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôll return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNd7NiWBcFbQcOC-zr9AUmudliVAjczr-c_P6Rm&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Dana Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQIw-0oOUNgoyniYugTscGkgpKJS8tpx4V0tAajn3ZGkNIfqEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place for refreshingly healthy eats downtown. I mostly do the build-your-own salad bowls, where you can combine a variety of interesting "salads" with a base and optional protein of your choosing. The chili-lime tofu, my go-to, is grilled fresh and juicy with a tangy marinade. I find these bowls very filling, but the price adds up quickly as you add more salad scoops, so I find it best to be conservative with my estimate of how much I think I need to eat.
Besides the salad bowls, they have some hot entrees. I tried the Moroccan chickpea hot bowl and the tomato soup and both were a little bland, which was especially disappointing for something labelled "Moroccan". I would go back and try some different entrees to see if anything else is better, but I would say the salads are likely the best choice here.
They have a very limited selection of "healthy" baked goods too. I really liked the chocolate pistachio cookie. As you would expect, it's significantly less sweet and has a slightly drier texture than a regular cookie, but if you like that kind of "better for you" treat, it's good. Very cocoa-forward.
I've had good experiences with the service. The staff is friendly enough and usually pretty fast. It's counter service, but they'll usually bring your food to you at your table.
There's a good amount of seating inside and a few tables outside when the weather allows. It's minimalist but clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmNl4VDvSict3IisR6QJ0lm8r-nBFxzJkKglmB&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Harrison Peers, Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLj2rlpKO7KJT6UpX1QjjJ2eHUX0QnhMR1u4oJxXhKAEkrBbvS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot BELIEVE how good this food was. The mushroom cold pasta is ‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è - SO good - The staff recommended it and it is WELL recommended. I also got the chicken pesto sandwhich - which is also delicious - but this cold mushroom pasta is incredible. This will definitely be added to my mental list of fast healthy foods downtown. Also well priced - under $20 incl. tax.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiIltj8MAqpHLfDyiGcFXr7D_eg-nnGPf5S8AZ&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Nate B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiJ-fIEoLKJGuGLppNQIFzU9-c6XEPxopAbjbPaYyM77tKgYI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here and I had a hard time choosing what I wanted to eat with all the great options. I went with the chicken avocado half sandwich and soup (ginger chili tomato). Both were absolutely fantastic!! Great place for fresh healthy options in the downtown area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQXx_GJw_3gIl0rbHUCtCL49aNNwR_Ni7uGBGR&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Iman Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY_It5dFbhJ3ahD3y8wnnvsyYECBdVwU0ipYiueTLf-0IgvGbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the tofu quinoa wrap. It was fresh, healthy, and tasted as expected‚Äînothing extraordinary, but enjoyable. The portion size could be bigger, especially considering the price compared to wraps from other places.

Next time, I‚Äôll try one of their bowls and hope to find something more unique. Overall, it's still a 5 out of 5 restaurant.

[Update October 2024]
I ordered the Everyday Bowl with half power greens and half brown rice. The greens were basically a spring mix, and I think the portion could have been larger, especially considering the price. It feels like the fresher the ingredients, the more you have to pay. I enjoyed the beets and pear pieces; they were nice, juicy, and, of course, fresh. The breadcrumbs and feta cheese added a salty touch, which helped enhance the overall flavor. While I liked the presentation, I enjoyed the wraps I had last time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUnL0Z1h_kb2WBhsmOM73NK1dce42M6BP6-m8a&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Wheels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsz1Rg53Q2-m5JHAwzfaowNSrC2JEVYhO1hHp4iyxB4sDy77VI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We usually get  delivery, so we don't know how the service is, but we absolutely love the food from here. We usually order chicken bowl with BBQ avocado. For healthier food I highly recommend eating here! The flavor is on point. We will be back and absolutely love the food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf7nCXde35pCMXnSh-V_V2Ga-NTiUCUvp6u8he&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Michelle W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6tNY8LO-QtQJ_R3rutBRZjHuvLbh5erCPRhIIR0T3kxt4zQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I typically don't expect much service from fast casual restaurants; however, Edward went above and beyond to make our experience exceptional. He not only accommodated our requests (rice to greens ratio, cooked protein) and delivered our food to our table, but he also surprised my mom with a cookie after overhearing that it was her birthday.

Food-wise, my mom and I each ordered a Nourish Bowl ($13.50), with hers being Beet + Pear, Southwest Quinoa, and Seared BC Albacore Tuna (+$7), and mine being Curried Cauliflower and Wild Mushroom Ditalini. Both bowls were refreshing and satisfying, with our favourite market side being the cauliflower. All of the market sides look to be vegetarian, with gluten free and vegan options available. I don‚Äôt think the additional protein is really necessary or of value compared to the market sides.

Ambience-wise, this location was great with its high ceilings, natural light, and clean aesthetic. It's also conveniently located on Robson Street, so it's perfect for a quick lunch or break while shopping.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnDe1O-1FXkr0bjLP6n34stwE8K6yU_X6mn68&fid=0x0:0x395f657cd29c4ed2"],"When":"2024-6-14"}]

[{"Name":"Rita S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz4B_m-DEY6gB1M4srcx7Pqc9qpVfzxMltQJQofY2yJbolWeK8BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Last time I came here it was great but this time they had run out of toppings for the vegan dog so I just got it plain and I was going to add some condiments. The hot dog I got was nearly inedible and not because it was vegan but totally overcooked and dry with an also hard/dry bun. I went to pickup my other food order elsewhere and asked my husband to get this one but I definitely wouldn‚Äôt have accepted it had I picked up. The chicken karaage was also a mess fried in dirty oil flecked with black. Absolutely awful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSxuTgYWsxigHU41_yOQRZuTpQc9e8yJ5K54hO&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Alexandra Gaevsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnjItyjfR1qVEZnY6caUOLCi6uNaCD4VjAop9J7DwgHSC2Qmwo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The hot dogs were decent, but nothing extraordinary. One of them lacked flavor, which might have been due to the bread not being as fluffy or bouncy as expected. The service was okay, though the food took a bit longer to come out than I would have liked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBj1b89Ej4tYv213b66A0m3Vz2yo4MeVEy3WTL&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Rob Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY5NTqMTgx_lD2eaipV6ZhBPVVFvaOf4WFNgkQid9KGHJe0clt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got to try 2 different types of Japadog during my vacation in Vancouver, They were both quite good. My only regret is that I couldn't try more varieties. Okonomi was my favourite and they had a Vegan option as well which was nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO41vOG-ZH-zO-nQoLHXcpGE3amDRgnbeY7grmB&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Alan Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMJD-0CMNr79zyDjaY-DyvlmCayfvuEGwkzuGa7BLyrbYyMDqo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A friend told me he drove 3 hours from Seattle to get this. After eating one I finally get why. The mayo is paired with a lean sausage causing it to actually be fairly balanced in terms of fat vs lean content. It's a well constructed hot dog.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOorMBjuXCYlF53Trn1vZcZ52o8LYt_pXbV_Y4X&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"sayo. ca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_x_czI-SgX-My0FUcudbm6l-nVMJffVnfmTctcdj39xcVOZoSgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I liked their foods when I tried them in Toronto. I was glad to come to the flagship store in this time. We had Wagyu Menchikatsu, Avocado, black sesame shake, lemonade and matcha parfait. I really liked ‚ÄúAvocado‚Äù, which has house made sausage, cream cheese and Mayo. I heard it‚Äôs quite popular for locals. Menchikatsu is much bigger than we expected! It was juicy and satisfying. Staff were very friendly even if they were busy. If you are in Vancouver, please give it a try these Japanese styled hotdogs at this store.

Wagyu Menchikatsu $14.98 Avocado $9.89, black sesame shake, lemonade and matcha parfait","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCBytVPOT13oD27KzLUjJnuNjy4NNhTM37DznC&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Jordan Gamache","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZmSaYmwhADhRlODHchAsnihXVMUVO1oBBO_boK7KmqaC9cZy35w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"JAPADOG serves the most interesting and delicious hot dogs with fun, Japanese toppings! The curry poutine fries were absolutely wonderful and the katsu and yakisoba hotdogs were spectacular. We were genuinely surprised with how well the flavors worked together, and the food came out really quickly. The JAPADOG tea/lemonade drinks were also perfect for a hot summer day, and we look forward to coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcDNjVxOcqerS8uls69IJV0GlwH09uZV-0-2_E&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Pushpa Perera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC_LqZDm87q7hBfncOFtdGHnXZ2H3BJ66AOmocM5ZUJc_QFwM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried these:Japadogs
1. Hot Spicy - All beef, lettuce, special spicy sauce
2. Cilantro - All beef, marinated cilantro, sesame special meet sauce and chilly umami
3. Teriyaki Tartar- all beef, teriyaki sauce , Japanese tartar sauce & green onions
Hot spicy Japadog was a little bit spicy taking over the beef taste.
Also tried Karaage and Love Meat (pork)
My goto drink Japanade with the hotdog!
Over two lunches in VC while traveling.
Also Jap curry poutine nice
Delicious Japadogs!
Sadly, didn't have a chance to  try other hotdogs.
Recommend if you are visiting Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdVPd1_JTnDUl9g6EyckSVu6R8xTfr667EinRD&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Chanil Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUQGp1nrL9JxzAwqk4JQgTjHyMBxLETKa4reQFPABq175G_ZSPDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Japadog is a must-visit when in Vancouver! This spot puts a unique and delicious twist on the classic hot dog, with Japanese-inspired flavors that are out of this world. I tried the Terimayo, and it was packed with flavor‚Äîperfectly grilled with savory toppings that made every bite amazing. The portions are generous, and the service is quick and friendly. Whether you‚Äôre grabbing a quick bite or exploring the city, Japadog is an iconic stop that you won‚Äôt want to miss!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0TEhFJscEAT1wRLwawGxjy1bG6oFG3yPBz7Xn&fid=0x0:0xd7477f4236c75e05"],"When":"2024-9-22"}]

[{"Name":"MORI N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmh-25mC5oA1PFMMA_52ysg1xmB302WDBqAM9LeMqrXCsb_9pPTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don't.
Why? I'll tell you why.....

The BBQ Burger
The Bacon Cheeseburger
....this review applies to both.

The buns were both disintegrating they were so soggy. They were soggy from the massive amounts of sauce they put on, and what happens when you put too much bbq sauce on? It becomes too sweet. Too much mayonnaise on the Bacon Cheeseburger was an insult to the burger, and the taste matched the look and the makeup of the burgers....miserable (see pic.)

The fries were unseasoned and just squished into their ...fries cup?
It was actually quite terrible, and I was craving Fat Burger.

It's interesting, it almost felt like a drunk person made our order.
Kinda like...."ahhh screw it...let's just toss everything on, wrap it up, toss it in the bag...and send 'em on their way...."
That's what it tasted like.

I don't know what to tell you. If you're craving Fat Burger maybe try a different branch?

I wouldn't go here...if I were you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-cw6xaJpQx2NCyYbJZqySxzoJfywt4g7qISMZ&fid=0x0:0xe8b7743d0fd7fcf"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"bondgirl42","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUE1gO1zmqZ8CoQWAw7bV2vdDtzMde9euGHhT2IFtfAuvnyNYaE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great burgers and the poutine was delicious. We got our order to go and service was very fast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKzaETKTtlTJMtzBVCm3oMfVgLhnDFqTFI8pxy&fid=0x0:0xe8b7743d0fd7fcf"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Sally K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS0FtpQtx3YuqrRFA5HEswfCULjQCZ3bwXSyydNupxhx29S0cd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The atmosphere is indeed good; it‚Äôs a comfortable and inviting spot to hang out. The staff were friendly and attentive, which is always a plus.

However, when it comes to the main attraction ‚Äì the burger ‚Äì it fell way below my expectations. The bun tasted like a generic market bun, lacking the freshness and flavor I was hoping for. To make matters worse, the maple bacon wasn‚Äôt cooked properly, which was a letdown.

While the overall experience was pleasant thanks to the atmosphere and service, the burger itself was a disappointment. I hope they can improve the quality of their burgers to match the rest of the dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEDW3b0Q0f5jk0G5AyUEWpiKpl-jEpiDamzCHb&fid=0x0:0xe8b7743d0fd7fcf"],"When":"2023-9-10"},{"Name":"Marie Aguilar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJIHIvI1GcTvwnEbjOZgsk97BeKLiW1sB1pG5n_afHXMHnPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location around the corner from St Paul's Hospital.  Sister was having surgery so the three of us went out looking for food.  Burgers are big, loaded with toppings of your choice -  or get them all!!  Yummy, flavorsome.  Perfect bun/hamburger ratio and the fries are crispy.  All in all, a good meal and the service was fantastic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"karanveer singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5YxLCUu91Sfygt1yr7M9Z08axzn3DExI-nSoKNmwU0gCwD_U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Fatburger on davie street. The burgers were juicy, fresh, and cooked to perfection ‚Äì you can really taste the quality. I went for the classic Fatburger with cheese, and it did not disappoint. The toppings were fresh, the bun was perfectly toasted, and the portion size was just right.

The staff was super friendly and attentive, making sure everything was just how I wanted it. The atmosphere was clean and comfortable, perfect for enjoying a great meal.
Overall, it‚Äôs a fantastic spot for a satisfying burger fix. I‚Äôll definitely be coming back for more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aom Hildebrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqzk0-t2eCJ3dWbzxrmO1EFkEGk94crNKQpEhBC-DrbexpqzAYfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We dropped by late on a busy night but the staffs were smile and good service even they were really busy. We got foods fast. Do not talk about cleanliness because what a busy night but after most customers left. She came out to tidy so clean and organized. The washroom was clean, happy. She even had a treasure box for my girls to choose what they liked to take home, very kind of her. So everyone were so happy and had a good time there","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgbI7dITOtIPFKpnyeH-bAhfOBw1WWe7PXc2BD&fid=0x0:0xe8b7743d0fd7fcf"],"When":"2022-9-20"},{"Name":"Dylan Emery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVWEybiLf37yEEuTzfa6hpxTG-XqhKlmcvi5fNfIMCBsCw2lI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always have a pleasant interaction with the front of house staff. Food is prepared promptly and served with integrity. Very tasty menu options. Reasonable prices for lunch or dinner. The deep fried pickles are so flavourful and served hot. Well done! üòÉ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcel ≈†mejkal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKg1z6u7TpA39bcjk1stYz2u8mFpZ0_fCvgKsGvl0hjUBKRIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Burgers are decently good and we like to order them. However, today we wanted to try mini donuts as a dessert and that just ruined the whole experience. Every bite was like drinking oil, donuts were soaked in it. Very disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQU1p3H4DT8scglMjpI1fRAri8KbbIaDmIcrmk&fid=0x0:0xe8b7743d0fd7fcf"],"When":"2023-7-7"}]

The staff is very friendly and the prices are very reasonable for downtown Vancouver. 2 slices and a pop for $10.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gwen Flores","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGwkMxksK5JlQb9Xg3xvLMsNVCiY4wyGrvApcpemZLNfJkvuTy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pizza. I am a pizza addict and this pizza was one of the best I've had in a long time. We came for a visit from California and were blown away by the pizza and wonderful staff. I highly recommend the margarita pizza. Oh and the white dipping sauce is amazing üòã","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOk325mc7CiVyZad_4rwLnNjxRZl9Bp9srbxFo&fid=0x0:0x3e723f7a95c6c03b"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Maria Kuchapska","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUifA0DEEGB_JLhFNyQyJxsse6YnNAXEOGlGS0er3OmjnEbkPk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Accidentally stumbled across this place after a show. I rarely eat pizza in Canada, but this was really pleasantly surprising! Although the flavor I wanted (gorgonzola potato) was sold out, the artichoke and truffle mushroom were both really good. Thin crust, wood fire, not oily. The staff were friendly, and the prices are very reasonable for downtown Vancouver - two slices and a pop for $10.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MORI N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmh-25mC5oA1PFMMA_52ysg1xmB302WDBqAM9LeMqrXCsb_9pPTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This pizza was actually quite terrible.

We usually order from our favourite pizza place but they were closed Christmas day, so we thought we'd try this place.

To start, there was hair on the pizza....not a topping I ordered. (see pic)
Another thing I noticed was that their dough was most likely not fresh and frozen. How could I tell? Well....the dough was incredibly soft. When frozen dough is thawed...the locked moisture from the freezing is released within the dough during cooking and therefore renders it soggy. So....there's that.

Also, another decorative piece on the pizza was the leftover charcoal soot from whatever source it fell from onto the pizza (see pic).....not good.
Mostly, I think with this place and our experience were issues of hygiene, which it seemed were completely disregarded and ignored.

Yeah, I don't think I would eat their pizza even for free just because I'm not sure about their hygiene and health measures practiced.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOxVvfLzcbkYkqSrLUnDp2psknYBWxgE15P7MU&fid=0x0:0x3e723f7a95c6c03b"],"When":"2022-12-27"},{"Name":"Tizil Raj Choudhary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdSCVfvkCJJzlolK4_12AaPorDuyB0sSqWarGkFMdmTJd6aqTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice service. I live in alberta. Visited this place on so many recommendations. I was looking for a pesto chicken slice but there were none. But this Indian server helped me out. She gave me pesto drizzle to top on the regular slice. Genuinely nice service.üòÅ will visit again.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Second, the Hummus, honestly idk what was that served with the food, It was alright but it wasn‚Äôt a hummus (see the orange solid thing in my pictures), I guess I‚Äôm a bit harsh because I was expecting an authentic experience.
I would recommend other places if you‚Äôre looking for a freshly cut, authentic middle eastern food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKCm6TgrOju8wpR78fl18yglVlk72X6TtSY2da&fid=0x0:0xd47f23ff5989cc7e"],"When":"2021-2-26"},{"Name":"Richard Hu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCB56XCzqLXPTj0T4EOd8tvwIFn4GWTIrLiWLv_XQ1gQilVZqz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had to try this place just to compare all the other donair shops I‚Äôve had around downtown.
