This location has gone downhill for me. The last few visits have been disappointing. The staff have been unfriendly and the quality has gone down. They‚Äôre either being cheaper with the toppings or the workers are not following the order instructions properly. For instance on my last visit I asked for extra pickles and onions, but could barely tell. There were only 2 slices of tomato on my entire foot long sub and barely any meat. The subs were poorly wrapped and the takeout bag had mayo smeared on the front. It makes me apprehensive to come back to this location. I hope this isn‚Äôt due to the new management.

I had a fantastic experience at this Subway. The service was friendly and quick. Ordering online was very easy and to top it off, they surprised me with a free cookie for doing so. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JJ MT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT4HbZwldoVKa9hEN3lpKmHzCRnnGUnFKXUgOk-UqAH4jZA5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This subway was doing better after the new mgmt, but it seems to have gone down in quality again.
Disclaimer: i worked at a corporate subway chain for 5 years

Staff:
friendly but absentminded, causing cross contamination risk
They dont change their gloves enough, and will touch things in between actions that then contaminates their gloves. Ie. Touching a door handle between meats and veggie sections, and not changing their gloves. If a customer has to ask you to change your gloves,  you are not paying enough attention.
Theres also items getting mixed in the cambros, ie. Onions in the lettuce. Im allergic to onions, so this is a cross contamination risk. The staff need to be mindful of this and carefully pick ingredients out so the arent dropping all over the place. I noticed this issue in multiple cambros of ingredients

Food:
I dont know if its a lack of training, but theres a few issues ive noticed from my visits
- Not assembling the sandwich correctly in terms of how they place meats, cheeses, and veggies. This causes the sub to be messy and difficult to eat.
- Pressing the items down, if a sub is assembled correctly there should be no need to press down on the ingredients in order to close it.
- bread not proofed long enough causing at least a 2inch different in size of the sandwich. This not only makes it smaller than what im paying for, but makes it difficult to put the ingredients on and messy to eat because the bread cant fit the whole order.
- putting weird amounts of vegetables??? Idk if the process has changed since i worked there, but there used to be a minimum amount and specific way to assemble all the ingredients, both for the look and for the ease of eating it. Ofc you can always ask for extra, but there was a specific number to put on to begin with... but this location just kind of throws stuff on. You'll ask for pickles and get 3 on a footlong? The minimum was 8 when i worked there.

The food tastes the same, its subway. But theres issues with procedure, bread size,  and correct portions, and i think they need to be retrained. Ill avoid this location in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0ob3XBhRattxBuT3-aPMP5wYfYxbrODK6YqsieDCFq1t4teI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"order online and easy to pickupÔºåsteak and cheese taste good deal is goodÔºÅwill come back next timeÔºÅ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuC2mQsYJLdTfjSsUjwBoGzyWg0fXpJrjahWU1&fid=0x0:0x6b345aa4c06c80b9"],"When":"2024-2-20"}]

[{"Name":"Marius Techere","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfcNi21vzYEJSjaSQT8sjQyA2kwQcvSTyDINPLTLRrbxNVwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The fries and the chicken were tasteless, even though is a Korean restaurant all I got with my order was some unwanted ketchup. I guess for the additional taste you must pay over 15$ plus tip. It about 15 min to make that menu. Nope I will not go back there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXFHizfCezaaZqwj-BmfZZUmo46BXJzK5xWwmY&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"Phil aw Sufer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHJXoxHG2i_BGcNQ_zKE8qlTT-eiWamqzQCfMoK1cFG0l1h3EF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an urge for Korean fried chicken and came across Chicko Chicken on Dunbar. I believe they are a franchise with many locations in the lower mainland. I ordered the half portion of their Yangyeom chicken. It's their sweet and spicy sauce tossed with their fresh fried portions of boneless chicken.  The flavor was awesome, and the chicken was so crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside. Next time, I have to order the other flavors.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrGdkHeGXyD4wiOAYuLB_UniO4P2WxX4djE1B5&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2023-3-15"},{"Name":"Brock Aura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnr_sEMDNfoDwSGZD53SzjLC3ZDNthshJ3gL532nCm4kTy9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The first impressions of this place were not good. First of all, their digital menu clearly stated that customers get free pickles and drinks with a full order, but they said that was no longer the case because many customers didn‚Äôt want pickles or drinks, so it was an additional cost.

Then, after ordering my son asked to use a washroom (and they allow up to 10 patrons to sit in and dine, which we did) but they claimed to have no washroom and directed us to the Tim Hortons a few minutes up the street. I‚Äôm no lawyer, but I feel like this goes against provincial laws / Vancouver bylaws for dining establishments.

Onto the food. We got a full order ($25) of half soy garlic and half cheese powder chicken to go along with shake-shake fries ($3.50). The food is nowhere near healthy, but it is delicious. The chicken is juicy and the fries are crispy and flavourful.

I‚Äôm curious how much chicken you get in the combo meal as it is listed as a full order, but it‚Äôs only $12.

Overall, the food is good, but the customer service isn‚Äôt great and they should provide the extra pickles and drinks if it is stated on the menu (would have been no problem for a restaurant with good service and customer appreciation‚Ä¶plus, a couple of tablespoons of daikon won‚Äôt break the bank).

I‚Äôd go back to Chicko Chicken, just not to this location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTUBvjl44yMnI7tNtMNS4MKjreUIxKh7un_YEI&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2022-3-24"},{"Name":"Carolin Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6UTw8MiPD4lMns2KEwQKDCBNWoS11pESIXB034eh8riDIAVWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're a fan of delicious fried chicken, then you absolutely must check out this restaurant. I recently tried their boneless fried chicken, and it was incredibly delicious. The original flavor was crispy on the outside, yet tender and juicy on the inside - it's one of the best fried chicken dishes I've ever had. I highly recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIRT5LqOBt_7D3QFT7f-fpSvSdyu6hYQNv960W&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Jaehee Cha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAY1P22Gway0-AJutFXC3fV0uADB66AHSd3sby-SHYZc31y_0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The chicken here is absolutely amazing. The flavors are perfectly seasoned and crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside. Friendly staff and quick service make it even better!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Da‚Äôrealest Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUVgBeXcqR1bO-4oZd573-tL4gAQyeQLwC8L-MBtAGjediWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came in late night for some amazingly delicious chicken (I will give yall props for the good food) but I was turned down as the staff had decided to start their close early rather than wait until the 10 pm close time. I work in a restaurant and understand it suck closing but change the close time to adjust to the earlier close.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pranipa Ernest","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaq4DxYwn6r5cjtOzmSTjpWCfWRbwXJhzhSunjC54QZCRn_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered a half order of the soy garlic chicken and really enjoyed it. I ended up walking home for about 20 mins in the rain/cold and the chicken was still crispy and warm by the end! Takes about 20 minutes to make so make sure to order ahead.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqeW9_rsaMsgKKgSaHE-kvJOW3mcXWNTlc3Cei&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2022-2-20"},{"Name":"Djihane Damoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6Bw39FbPE2iSCOOlu8H9a_mX9tmRiWxstSp4aYfPtZPYrPw1Rvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing fried chicken. Highly recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoHDlWE8wvaN1w_7TEC7jloyPNtXhbWf50YbXn&fid=0x0:0xcda159c61221d78c"],"When":"2021-10-7"}]

They always serve with smiling face and all. They are very nice. They always greet their customers nicely. And about last incident about the washroom I was there. They were 6 people and they order one water bottle and they all want to use the washroom. That‚Äôs not right. People need to think straight and smartly. Manager said them nicely and they were so misbehaving with the manager . It‚Äôs not good at all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrGTxlku5kvFv5W_FIgEmEYMaI5rjeEJ24c_v6EjYbpaZPvnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have to say I was very pleasantly surprised by how hot, fresh and tasty my burger was. Plus, they have a $5.69 combo that includes a small bacon cheeseburger, fries and a drink. The burger was the best fast-food burger I've had in a long time. I do love an A&W teen burger but they are NEVER hot! In fact, they are always lukewarm. I have even asked them for a hot, fresh burger but I never get it. I see the burgers come out and they sit there while the staff members faff about doing other things. For some reason they let them sit and sit and sit before delivering them. Well, I'm sick of cold burgers! So I was very pleasantly surprised by this hot fresh burger on a warm fresh bun delivered the way I ordered it (no mustard or ketchup). Too bad the fries were lukewarm because they seemed like good fries. Also better than Mickey D or A&W. So that was lunch for $6. Milk tea was average.  Got the beef mapo rice bowl, flavour was good,  1/3 of my beef was fat, half my rice was hard.  Got takeout and the lady said the computer system was not working,  agreed for her to use a calculator.  I asked why it was $2 more.  She said for single use cups and tips. She forced tip me when the food was takeout and not even cooked to order.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfUD0MplobZDhYGcx_Un3A8jreujh0ii7YaSxwq2KY3T6FNZ8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excited for a chatty meal?Cheaty Food Bar serves the perfect mixture of Food and sweet desserts! I tried their famous Bubboden and I was not disappointed. They offer the most creative tea in probably all Vancouver!

The Cheaty Drink i had was the Lychee rose oolong - cold brewed award-winning organic tea and tea jelly - they were so kind and made it without sugar so you could really taste the ingredients. It comes in a cool cup which is reusable!

They also have juicy sandwiches known as Banh Me, but I had the Mapo Tofu Bowl as a savory dish. The nice soft tofu pares well to the delicious rice it is topped on.

Let me tell you about the Cheaty Bubboden I ordered:

The Cheaty Bubboden comes with Black beans and is topped with Purple Yam and Almond Milk making it the perfect mixture. (and vegan)

They can replace everything with lactose free or almond milk! Also they put amazing Mango Jelly in it and served it with the dried ice wow! The Skewers are fresh, handmade and the selection varies daily

Located at Dunbar Community & another good thing: they are open every day!

Also a big shootout to the staff: amazing customer experience! They are extremely polite and friendly - Thanks

This place is breathtaking","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Cristal Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKVgmGNO0nM5QsKQAT5sqSSfDi4-SXeOmE9QKCS4Yn3xevSRo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dec 4, 2024 (~4-6pm)

I was here at this location and the staff were so nice!! There was a long line up and I could tell the staff were working hard to fulfill orders. Even with the rush the staff were so friendly and handled the line well. There were some uncleaned tables but the staff cleaned it up when it was less busy.

Seems to be a new manager? He didn‚Äôt exactly know the system but got the other staff to help him with the register. He was wearing a blue shirt at the time which is a bit different from the other workers. Anyways, he has the best customer service!!! Thank you sir :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yaad Sandher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4VqzhtFXsN8-SkjJ6pLiBJb4rzwiahoG1EOJ8s3p2WewIRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I want to commend the staff for their outstanding service. From the moment I walked in, I was greeted with warm smiles and a welcoming atmosphere. The team was not only efficient but also genuinely kind and attentive, ensuring every customer felt valued.

The service was prompt, even during a busy time, and the staff handled the rush with professionalism and ease.

What stood out most was Navdeep‚Äôs friendly demeanor. He went beyond just serving orders, engaging with customers and creating a sense of community. It‚Äôs rare to find such a combination of speed, accuracy, and kindness in customer service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Foolery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2CL3907bWdn6DUj-R1WcSsdkc0ujUkJ9uj_u3cK3X0Z6Ozg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I just tried to call to leave a complaint but I got an answering machine so I‚Äôll do it here. This location of Tim‚Äôs has the best staff by far out of all other Tim‚Äôs I frequent. However we must address the corporate level issues on the food. I just ordered 2 hash browns and they were not palatable. They tasted freezer-burned and were barely warm. Even if they were warm enough that frozen freezer burn taste would still be there. They are clearly the same hash browns we can all buy in the frozen food isle and they have that same frozen taste when we make them at home- so we know. You think this is acceptable to charge people for? Why do McDonald‚Äôs hash browns taste so amazing? And made in a way we cannot replicate at home. I ate one of my hash browns today and it was so gross, I took one bite out of the second and could not believe I was charged $2 each for this frozen tasting not edible food. I went to the counter to complain and explain but instead of hearing what I was saying they just offered me 2 more hash browns- that made me angry enough to complain in this way. Your food is unacceptable now and barely edible and when people are honest and complain about it they should get a refund- not more inedible freezer burn-tasting replacements. Customer service needs to be back to Canadian standards. You complain and they truly are too deft to understand what you are saying in order to rectify it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTx21jQ3ixOeedWHFc3zDSy4yNyoRockoqEhp4ukWBqSAO1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"UPDATE *Scroll down for original review*

They are now being extremely pushy upon taking your order that you go to google reviews at that moment and leave a five star review. They even have a sign right at the till begging customers to do so. The woman behind the till looked visibly upset when instead of pulling out my phone to do so immediately, I just looked back at her and waited for my order. For the management of this particular franchise: good reviews are supposed to come organically and a reward for proper service and good food. This is not how you pump up your google review score. Do better.

Original review:

Usually this place is decent to grab a quick bite, but when I came in today at noon on the 10th of October, I could not believe how unfriendly everyone behind the counter was. It was so bad that I nearly felt the need to apologize for merely having my presence in the store at all.

On top of that, the gentleman who was in line before me had to go at extreme lengths to convince the people behind the counter to remake his order when they made it wrong, despite very clear and easy to understand instructions. It was a little hard to watch.

Not to mention that they don't give receipts when taking orders, so when they start calling out order numbers, no one knows which one is theirs.

Ultimately, customers shouldn't feel the need to apologize when making a purchase in store as it should at least be a marginally welcoming place to be.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"priya aryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhujY_qvoDTSZ3DP97_yKAaQm8JxpQCMGH0Nq4gNguul5LMBRz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My second time Review.

Store Manager  is great ladyüíú
I recieved  great service  from Hui, prince and other girls.
My favorite TIMMY  store,my neighborhood
Very lovely Team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Jafton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXFQ-6itxsd8z47x7lufVpEcdEYrXgfRlYBbJ56y6QBxE1Kw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this Tim Horton everyday for the past 2 years. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Wayne Parsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbKTlWkKr_9FrpGqHdG_gLVwj8ek5tp4JkYHZ7netDqWjWmvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"If someone was to make a AI version of an Irish pub, this would be the result. Meaning, it‚Äôs totally not real. The food was terrible. Overpriced and small. An Irish Pub should have good food and lots of it. My wife‚Äôs stew resembled army rations and was served at room temperature. Our friend‚Äôs roast beef sandwich looked like cafeteria food from the local high school. The salad was wilted too! And all served on a damn baking tray. Come on guys, put in an effort. We won‚Äôt be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2KCQuYhEAsiVGca5kaEKcVzPcDG_eAP0FMaB4&fid=0x0:0xa1ded410844b68ea"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Francis Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQYb0f3bY9eLZforDKXF2na-BCy9gLQ5VfdJ7bBPMLWI02Rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Over the years we've seen our local drinking hole change hands from the much beloved Dunbar, to the mediocre Bells and Whistles to now the Shamrock Storehouse. A fabulous location with a great enclosed covered patio, the newly renovated space has a much better layout and does exude the cozy charm of an Irish Pub. The drinks are great and the servers personable. I just wish the food lived up to the experience.

When I think of pub food, I think of hearty warm generous proportions. Sadly this is not the case. My $23 Roast Beef sandwich was meager with the thinnest proportions of roast beef. My friend's Beef Pot Pie seemed an appetizer size. My other friend's Beef Stew was in the shallowest bowl and hardly a stew, more like a gravy soup with some beef and potatoes. And cold at that. And everything is served on the most generic cold tin cafeteria style trays with the saddest soggiest potato wedges.

It really does take a lot for me to write a negative review about food, so I hope this establishment works out the menu and considers the level of quality of food they are serving because the price doesn't match what you get at all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Will Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5Hm6AjeO740qFyk5mKC2aWhtCN4pycpwipcFsZ-XhQKSlGf26PQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great new Irish Pub open in Dunbar where the old Bells and Whistles used to be. Great menu, great staff and a great selection of beers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrMwpdHgqtHxYLKqpCLzPRg1byc13SRfknCkjP&fid=0x0:0xa1ded410844b68ea"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Matthew Kindrachuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7IFlY4yDsSinymj9SX_qMJD5UdTHvZ4R80ygYjm9ZDr10XAbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was very good and my Guinness was perfectly poured with a smooth, creamy head. The customer service was decent but the atmosphere is probably the most redeeming factor. The live music and Irish decor of the pub, along with the late hours, make it perfect for Dunbar. The menu is also varied but not overwhelming at reasonable prices throughout.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"james joyce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSNU3IV7c5bc4y_E5DtWL0IkZIylxV8uOsght-XbzhurD0yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I wish them the best. Dunbar needs a good restaurant. It's nog happening here. I had the BLT. I don't drink so I had a Diet Coke. My friend had lunch also. Served on a baking tray  I had soup also. I think. I wasn't a fan of the restaurant before. Wasn't good and there's not much on this menu. And it's not good. To drop in and have a beer I guess it's okay. Not going back. Not a lot of seats.  No tables inside. I wish them luck. They need it","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse McKenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUO5fhmeB-ow2Rzs2WeDWCbDfsso9CCyYxBmw1B3X0paMAUSms=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great beer, amazing atmosphere! They had live music that was the best I‚Äôve ever heard at a pub; very lively, I‚Äôll be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhJHRx5lKZwLrAnwBcjMIOoBd8bdHfq4TZaWLs&fid=0x0:0xa1ded410844b68ea"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Clay Hamill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzV-QJ1zlhgWec1NtPfMTxGzP9lSYahOiyIkKNZKHXZLaHbww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great lively addition to the Dunbar neighbourhood. Food, service & happy hour is on point. Bar seating is an ideal place to watch any game & booths for a nice dinner out.

Will be visiting often!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Hynes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAcIwj2U-dthl_2N-I8m7pagy8ccXrJWhou7j53WoPgAZ_-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped into here and tried the potato soup with ham & cheese toastie. Absolutely delicious it was. Pub and decor looks great and has a lovely cosy pub vibe. Great asset to the neighborhood - I wish you all the of luck with everything!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Have the inspectors come here yet?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIfG5_v77e0rjxdOpUshc9rFYL_Cy3oLVNjOIy&fid=0x0:0x40efe50e19bcdef5"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Fala Ala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkiZZNXOSJcJKNOdJg0Pkoy1tLfFoG_lIl8csCpHww8XvOGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a large hot chocolate and a small fries last night.  7 mins after getting the fires, I asked for hot chocolate and waited a while to got one.

The hot chocolate tasted like sugar milk. Since I didn't want to go into the rain again to go back to the McDonald's, I drank some thought as long as it can hydrate me, it would be okay.

I went back to McDonald's, because I really not like it. It was 70% full.

The employee first filled it with chocolate syrup to 70%. It tasted worse.  Then she refilled it.  Still not right.  She only refilled to 70% too.

What kind of quality control or service?

I am glad that the fries quality control was good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ98NzX2Kz8KQkxg0LbIZeAi14VEO8BxokY9MloKqaqhBW7lA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have tried this location 3 times now, and every time they disappoint. When I asked if they could grab decaf from drive thru, was told that was the only pot in the entire store.  Wow.  After 10 minutes, finally got my second coffee, meanwhile my fries and first coffee were now cold and had to ask for fresh ones.  Store was disgusting from a cleanliness perspective, and not very nice people working there.  3 strikes and you‚Äôre out.  I‚Äôll never be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RandomAlpaca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc8u0_GgO8i6h2t6topz8d0q7v21fNNwo_yKKNeSkQzcr9qkb8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Sad. Then they take an excessive amount of time to give you a sad burger and some of the saddest fries known to man. This place used to be good, but now it‚Äôs truly awful.

Street parking available along the street, 1-2 hours free parking","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYTezoKLalZcQBP2PvntK9kFplb4zrfAhjlObN&fid=0x0:0xcb49aad57fbcc7ad"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Maryam Akbari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-eAd5hrPOKxHdjYcVS_udIPXyL_R_-31zZsqGfsMDwMJeHAE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cozy Thai restaurant in my neighborhood is a hidden gem, perfect for rainy day studying. Definitely worth checking out for a delightful dining experience with exceptional service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1K0ovpS3IZqhS3akfdPyytLwccrdj7gzBI0nKxpPJs3cRNw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I eat Thai all the time back in Toronto and this place is not 4+ stars. They have very decently priced coffees, and currently they have a promo ‚Äî 50% off all coffees for students until the end of October.

i got this large iced latte with caramel syrup for $3.7 and the owner gave me 1.5 pumps of caramel syrup to make it more flavorful :) i don‚Äôt know where else in vancouver you‚Äôd find a large ice latte for $3.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPU_VrhNpBM_dstxD9mRW8UJHFG0lOVMwH6En93&fid=0x0:0xea6c012d591acdde"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Ella Gladders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUN--GPQ4rHO9A_htxdSJD2kajMZXeWYnGkgvWASwFN0fIL5guv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I first went to Bynns, I thought I‚Äôd be disappointed considering it replaced the Starbucks, but I was more than pleasantly surprised. I‚Äôve tried many of the refreshers on the menu, and not only are they affordable, but they are so good and made with great ingredients. I appreciate that they actually serve you a nice and full drink rather than filling the entire cup with ice. I wouldn‚Äôt ask for anything else to replace the Starbucks. I also received a complementary refresher while I was doing shopping in the stores around Bynns which made my day. It‚Äôs nice to know that there‚Äôs still these kinds of stores that make Dunbar a warm and friendly neighborhood. The owners and staff are very nice and personable people. I‚Äôm very happy with the new implementation of Bynns and am super excited to see what they come out with next!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"June Ang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJP5yl8i7K22hs1ifUDS_dkFzkW6Tzf01nDChdS5OW-D97HA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped by a couple of times for breakfast, coffee and sandwich. Coffee was okay.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Halliday","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWQWDrPh_csHvdV5_dEwnBSFqvsryByMjJ5Uqpk65EzCcZ4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst sub I've had anywhere, even mr.sub better. [{"Name":"SUNGSHIN LEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTHEUJEH0mZSgA5db_QMPnswjUhhpjoXIbFsCVYlhI913rxbiN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is the delivery anchovy we got.

Seriously? Half opened up can in plastic wrap? I hope you guys know that this is hazardous to health and safety.

Also banana pepper root/stem not picked out feels like chewing wood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGwvkRDQDNVtC6CaiBii8c4YaQEdzTYxKe1Wo-&fid=0x0:0xaedfa8a633eedb25"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKf1RSg3_-AU0iu6cewVgjwGYoJmZNxdRNJCv62pXrCH7QK-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"So I just tried the new Shaq Pizza; and I've been to every other location for Papa John's. But I saw the sign at this location as I walked by, figured I'd give one last try cuz I've tried every other location and they're all horrendous.

But unfortunately there was no different about this location, the pizza was absolutely disgusting. The crust was gummy, it was chewy, there was a lack of flavor to all of it. Now I know why they give you that spicy pepper, because they want you to eat that so you burn your mouth so you can't taste that there is no flavor from the pizza! It's a good thing it was only $20 and a part of it went to donation for children, otherwise I'd be asking for my money back. The only flavor I could taste what's the Tomato sauce, which was sweet! It's like someone poured a bunch of sugar packets on it.

Don't waste your money, if you want real Pizza just go to a proper Italian restaurant, just avoid this entire franchise completely cuz no matter where you go it's not worth the money even when it's on the cheap deals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jogn wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHeyzidMpgdTdyID-q90KGoADC5i2X4TU7x2hviP2zgOVW3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôve been coming to this location for over a year. I always receive exceptional customer service for the staff. An employee named Sahil stands out as one of the most cordial staff members I have ever met. I will keep coming back indefinitely","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harmanjot Singh Tahim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIPozfOBKJE00VbEW0sh_Q0ZIW5jnO9JkFYcjaXthRGunUENA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visit this pizza shop weekly and am consistently impressed by the excellent and efficient customer service. The staff is always friendly and attentive, making each visit enjoyable. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terry Zudnick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbuKwn9CLFcVOjM6WUGKXcmax6e_3R1gP2wYwtTV-eOX-_qg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"GREAT PIZZA !  Ordered a Large Pepperoni, Extra Sauce and Baked Well Done - Special Promo Price $12.99.
My Wife ordered a Large Black Olives, Extra Cheese and Fresh Roma Tomatoes ( Yes Fresh Tomatoes ) also Baked Well Done.
Great Tasting Pizza.
Thanks,
TZ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"tia hoppington-scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIovhVvWwNjjpMvUNEHgNHY0MZ8FVeQXA03vBsqN6icPChYjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza with quick service. I ordered on uber eats and it was the fastest delivery I've ever had. The pizza was hot and just like I ordered. The dip and the pepper were free. It was nice to see since most places charge extra for everything these days.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUDZmrxEY5DTZcM7X8sjrsXBcSAYcx67y8dfBF&fid=0x0:0xaedfa8a633eedb25"],"When":"2023-10-11"},{"Name":"J P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPNOwczxQeYq8Qup51h2PTCgzkWZZqiOeXeOFsoHWK1IWAROM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a mushroom olive pizza but there was almost no mushrooms on it. The service was very friendly but the pizza could have been a lot better.

Already a bummer that papa John‚Äôs doesn‚Äôt have plant based protein options like Pizza Hut or Pizza Pizza, but they should at least load up the vegetable toppings.

Edit: I'm aware of the quality guarantee, but I did a carry-out order and your policy requires me to bring the 2 pizzas back to the same store. I took the bus and it was New Years eve, wasn't going to bother going from Oakridge back to Dunbar, back to Oakridge. However, the point of the review is to give feedback to the store management and an accurate representation to prospective customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt7jHECC8UBOIKsTTBfws5GNgM0vCQbDlz0t5h&fid=0x0:0xaedfa8a633eedb25"],"When":"2024-1-4"},{"Name":"Peter Kang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSbtpk6mh_0J3sf_Y9A7fc3wtih7ARkn-i0R0NjMntR0woTMmepw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my new go-to place. Always fresh, delicious pizza with variety of options at great price. The staff are friendly with excellent customer service. Special shoutout to Sahil for always taking care of me. Free parking out front for easy pickup. Recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Parker Pratt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJU0WC7BNhoquaNZ7TyZKhVt3dPGzFKMGuxVDDqWMVqqdm8QUp9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service is great and the atmosphere is VERY cozy. Front area is well kept and clean, but the back could use some work(not entirely their fault, the building is clearly old). The food was good but not great. We got a couple of different crepes, some hot cocoa and a slice of lemon cake. I'm personally not a huge fan of buckwheat so if it's possible to get white flour for the savory options I recommend that.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWLxyITN1V472cwwASIQVMH7ZsGX-A5KqPJw04&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Greg Mattson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFrbttlbDAMTrqcEYaEoNGgTXaMwtarCi6C54s9mUz7zEh6gC-iw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The best thing going for this place is the location, close to 41st ave & Dunbar - pretty much the only cafe in the area, unless you go much further east into Kerrisdale itself. My cappuccino was delivered to my table (!) quickly, so that was impressive. The coffee itself was OK. Besides that, there‚Äôs some concerns here: 1)display cases which at 2:00 in the afternoon were almost bare, 2)dirty dish return area that is definitely  not as clean as it should be, 3)the entire cafe needs some ventilation/fresh air, and 4)seating is comfortable but chair/table combinations are much more suitable for conversation than using a laptop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRarfiYmgJ-q1gvXlXqH8bHs1VvzgFWTifpJnF&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Earth Explorer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXx9WbpYHoWti2M8dulDcVEiSwzq2Is9YdecFV0_EjsI1gR2sUT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a quiet and comfortable place for breakfast or lunch and to do some work. The crepes with eggs were delicious and they have a very nice selection of tea. They offered some gluten-free pastries. The Wi-Fi was 5/1.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipND3MZzy6BrRmvXm3B8cUX11GPtpL_t6D7hNVb7&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Quinn Middleton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY2QdQYVqfpGNwtjggHktblvZSmbHIJsZC9kLsVLJDUcmOUHKb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"From the outside, you would think it's just a generic cafe that serves 'meh' food, but Crepe Cafe surprised me...

It's a family run cafe and the staff are very friendly and welcoming. I have only tried their sandwiches, but they are made fresh to order rather than being taken out of their display like other places. The espresso drinks are about average, but not horrible.

If you're in Dunbar, give this place a tryüëå","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHomGOF9USnTuxcIaFF03EZPIORc2-l_r7qor2&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"Katie Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIjMysay4-FQVEPUnU2iivCs6D7x1kzSWlLVk1hwpWr3ttr5es=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Cozy neighborhood cafe. Service was great. Ordered a mocha latte but it tasted like hot chocolate-- I frankly didn't even taste the coffee üòÖ Stuff are really sweet here-- I'm not a fan of sweet things but I was in a good mood and didn't really mind too much.

Crepe was good but wish they sold them plain with jam/Nutella on the side or something. The sweet options are too sweet. Maybe it was possible but I didn't ask.

Overall, a decent cafe stop if you're in the neighborhood but not a place I'd make a trip for.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1QYsaox0VwlHZND1laNGmTM-yhEhAArzbY4VV&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2023-8-30"},{"Name":"A singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhcpKZ1cLXYaxugzfB2P8fOQWU_fMxCyyERFq-nMAdFuUTUwXJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very ry well managed cafe. The staff is very welcoming and polite. The owner is an amazing personality.
A must visit cafe and I would truly recommend the place.
You must visit it to actually feel the warmth and aura of the cafe.
The food is amazing. The place actually deserves more than a 5 star rating üëè","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmQdctlbM12t5Occdf84xI_X4OatAdUnoO7Mf5nuujaBWYasmgPA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Not the same cafe. I visited many years ago.  The chicken crepe used butter chicken pieces rather than plain chicken and the daily special is butter chicken with naan bread.

The girl behind the counter was not the French ethnicity that I've seen here before but rather of that ethnicity.

The egg and spinach crepe she made was decent and fresh.  Nothing special to say as it was typical egg and spinach crepe that was decently seasoned.

The chicken crepe had butter chicken pieces, red onion and tomatoes. Temperature of filling very cool so I originally thought this was made first and the other made after but the crepe was a little drying and seemed pulling apart around the filling area so it might have been premade and reheated. Taste was ok, but would have rather had freshly made one from scratch, even if with plain chicken.

Was there early so room was empty.  Plenty of residential street parking if need to park more than the 1hr that the 41st Ave. street offers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTZVrgWlV-reEfTRBxo8KkMO8Pq-Lsk3Xe_r_Q&fid=0x0:0xace99864f8090dad"],"When":"2019-8-24"},{"Name":"Marc Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0-_fHdw6dI5UTCDSShdCSvLGyTKZoaiMYMpD52alAaa7n_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cr√™pe & Caf√© has a great Parisian style artistic atmosphere for the best coffee break, away from the distractions of the city, is close to the unique area of Kerrisdale, Vancouver, and the food and desserts are delicious!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"El Styles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrrii3J8F9-5asxwPQAFrEFqNgl8kKXITZ3zJga8KlqLQjMRtjbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is tough because I have always loved Pink Elephant  through the years at all the different locations I have been to that are no longer open. This seems to be the last remaining one. The food is so good (esp pad kee mao, red curry and spring rolls) although they have made some changes over the years I don't like as much. I always find the service to be good, especially at lunch - they can get you fed and out of there on time! It just reeeeaaaaally bugs me when a restaurant's online menu is out of date and prices are higher when you get there. Fix that and I will give 5‚≠ê","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTQ5-9Y5nbRxm8k5VaU9EGNMDHCdn7ZqX33r71&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Herman Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNkiZiWTHH4AMcQS5P0e7HeuuBX0dNeXwCFqQ9w2c9ob5i37E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for dinner after golfing and enjoyed some very good dishes.  Pork Jowl Salad, Chili Basil Wings, Oxtail Curry, and Black Cod.  The dishes were very flavorful and authentic.  This location has a cafe side and a restaurant side.  Food and Service was excellent, will return to try more dishes that they offer.  Plenty of street parking available as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwmMwLPKhUFJmHuelAesUg6Rl-SYZwIIR7L46X&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"Patrick Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfqQ576ERK8XNZqdO6FJ9KfO2oF9cxNCzwYsLRqB9EpPQi40PiZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is no ordinary ice coffee‚Ä¶ ask for Donut and she‚Äôll make you Thai ice coffee that will remind you of Asia!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_zorBClxoQqwF0zVqRBIK1btFaGvE3UfNbABr&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Meghna Lohia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDKr_p1LlgcuGuLVIbh3NBjokSxaSc0Kjo7j56Mx18FfR4wRsK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love coming here! They have affordable and good drinks, specials throughout the week, good thai food for dinner. It‚Äôs a vibe! I would say maybe they could improve upon their food options at the coffee counter, because they clearly can make some good stuff, so show it off in the baking too! Otherwise, it‚Äôs a great local place and I‚Äôm glad it‚Äôs here, cuz I need coffee.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catherine Byrdy (Byrd)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8uqMGqbkqGknJWQpYOqYnRycihvurvs3aDaz_7RfiDzMksAc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is adorable!!! We were hungry, had 25minutes to spare; I saw a cafe and demanded, ‚Äústop here‚Äù. I love pink and elephants, but I had no idea. You can tell the owners really care about their business, as every detail has intention. And the the best part, the food was amazing and they had wine, even one of my favourites. Absolutely divine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7tqtRolI1L_dEwKAVks10zF30i325sQD4NNA&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2021-9-29"},{"Name":"Allan Jarczak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5lii5x3jzHsbgojd__n6bk0jrQByqDlslPIHHRDBGzpD6SQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really nice, family run vibe.
The coffee is remarkably good at a fair price.
Hidden gem in the neighborhood.
Strongly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkNUhTMtqSiLd95lbrM29L1ejA76QLgpiRpQaZl_2nkhTdsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious, and awesome coffee. I‚Äôm so thrilled that they opened a cafe version of Pink Elephant in this neighborhood.

Also helps that you can do takeout in a jiffy as they have a cold section and a hot foods/dine in option!

Update: I changed my review due to the measly portions for takeaway containers. No way they should be 17.99. Other places down in Kerrisdale is 11.99 for a full sized meal.

Edit: Improved to 4 stars. They now have a lunch menu starting at 13.50 per. MUCH more reasonable. If they can enhance their soup noodles and offerings, they are a 5 star","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4-sU9ZopsXOEtMpZQt24YT0EO-g2T0tEB9Uxi&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2021-8-6"},{"Name":"chenying wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVohyi9laAnJ1eV4iDaY0BV1V6uumpi-oh9eNd3Ad2B5FmchvmW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"very nice and warm place to hang out. It's beyond what I expected (especially after reading the negative comments). Thai chicken wrap is fairly good and their chai tea latte is really great. don't know why but their 16oz drink is a bit larger than any 16oz drink I have ever seen in the U.S.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMI55-nSYW8-zuCG2YEF1bmSH8mPO_-fdIIHld&fid=0x0:0xd602003b05d77f34"],"When":"2018-9-1"}]

???????????? When I mentioned, she said oh that girl is new so she doesn‚Äôt know.

I‚Äôm here for fast food not a die out.

Most disgusting thing is what I saw two girls in the kitchen didn‚Äôt have gloves on to fried the  chickens. The manager is a liar and rude. Thats how they keep the food inside the package. I dont know who is the owner of this branch! Its defaming KFC","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQ5E6ijXvMjg__sJR0F2Ta1WrBcbwB-Q3aWDCJ&fid=0x0:0xea570e8490b3ec11"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Avis White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLezXDAGeWo5JKKgTo94vWK-7SiBygWvU5u9ajB_RtKP-9NSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I complained to the manager and she was very nice. She politely listened and answered to my questions and told me I can exchange the chickens if next time I get poorly cooked ones. However, the taste is very poor compared to Chinese KFC, and quite mediocre among western fast food here, and she said I am the only real person complaining, ‚Äúall the other one star come from the same IP address‚Äùand stuff‚Ä¶ So, if you are a fan of Chinese KFC, be prepared for a big downgrade. The coat is too salty and the meat is too plain because the CA store use different spicing methods and probably don‚Äôt pre-season the meat itself.

Also, the chicken drumstick was overcooked, too salty and texture is dry and rubbery. The other one was okay, it is somehow juicy, but still‚Ä¶ The other western fast food shop heard about my story and gave me a free chicken strip, and that one was much more tender, juicy and taste much better‚Ä¶ and chicken wasn‚Äôt their specialty. I‚Äôd say this KFC still has some space for improvement.

Also I asked if the coleslaw salad can have salad dressing aside and they said yes but it was mixed in. The person who gave me chicken was nice and friendly through. You need to ask for Napkins at the front. I don‚Äôt understand that they don‚Äôt provide napkins as a fried chicken shop cause ‚Äúit gets messy‚Äù. If kids want to get messy they can use your drink fountain, toilet tissues or even utensils‚Ä¶  I failed to see a point of making people to ask for napkins without knowing there was an option.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtCDGABQzGsZcStci9KkMlC_D6FzfpmQ11cdmi&fid=0x0:0xea570e8490b3ec11"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Byron Sheardown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNqxb0c_42J36yKVRNJaOWQgsDJlMUDs94sxLG_b3F9RGXTQ_D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Friendly staff. Dec. 2nd update

As for the chicken, besides the fact the pieces are too small, but the chicken actually smells bad as if it has gone bad.

I mean already the prices here are much more expensive than KFC Dubai, so please at least offer the same service if not better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ramesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF0eh0lxDnJlUw8AegdF8o-aLxaC1-KS09MVVBxFiHbIwoWBOw-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Disgusting employees...
No courtesy to the customers.
I will not recommended this KFC.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ0D8w6UrfYdjlfw2L04tsKhmY3wx71q-dDTyH&fid=0x0:0x23880dd16ae167c7"],"When":"2019-5-27"},{"Name":"Adithya Gopinath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNRH_f-B_VYNWiNozcNEgYY5mZvjRIt89GFolK4t69VWXn-jnr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm totally disappointed at this particular outlet and the main reason is the staffs inefficiency and inability to solve problems. People are lining up at the restaurant and the staffs are not efficient enough on expediting orders. On top of that they ignore customers and throw an attitude as if we are doing them a favor coming to their restaurant. Rest assured I'm happy with the kfc food but I'll never return to this outlet anymore. Kfc please teach your staff to be more flexible and train them to handle a busy situation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darryn Kar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdGNilEUkcW7nP2qRJRgYVXsTqIq7xXPT3AZrLOJ53NlbgoSDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nothing worse than heater lamp food. My kids especially loves coming to visit and it‚Äôs a very friendly environment. I got a special treatment today and it‚Äôs the most beautiful sushi rose I‚Äôve ever had. Also very delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8O6zLh1POGjCvZNOv6Tz5BHnE-w7ZERI4ABN4&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Maryam Rasouli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItu-r2M5cRssc3H-BTIyUIVfVg4I84H7Cx_24NB9LjMA-r49Sc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious food, warm and kind staff ü•∞
Try their rose roll and Sapporo beer üç∫ üòÄ üòâ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWtOShpV5SSG3JT80OBJprdN02QppqIpl8hs8S&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Grace Cooper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXwOlo6qF0CLFam1zD22TIhA6kh_YcUpn-7jXwu-hBtoxh0qKm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best sushi place I have been to, my friends and I always go there at least twice a week when I am home. The food and service is great and the food is always fresh and delicious. I love you red tuna!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcus Xiong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNKHkNu0r9L6u_s13vBOcHGIOl_tisn1xjH9tQbojiCd_NkDw-YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A nice little place in Dunbar to have a Japanese meal. The sashimi here is okay, but I have had better. The sushi rolls are delicious, but this place leans more towards a Korean style sushi place because the rolls are huge just like kimbap. The absolute best part of my visit was the spicy Salmon don, which is better than any other I've had before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiNCTCtM3jw9_htWX-QSGISUGFxK3-7xI6cFYx&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2023-8-31"},{"Name":"Greg Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaHoeF-L9BhMd7XvI_GxQRpRTwkeFABaWJFc7MMAFpUBndhYSOpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am local to the Dunbar area and visit Red Tuna at least 3 times a month. Their dine in experience is nice and homey and the staff are very kind. Take out is also a great option, and food is not soggy when you take out. I recommend the Nabe Udon and the Sashimi Salad as well as the Spicy Maki Combo and the Spicy Salmon Don. Portions are generous and price is fair if you compare it to other sushi restaurants in Vancouver.

Red Tuna has been my favourite local restaurant for many years now. Will continue recommending this restaurant to friends and family!

Edit: Don't count out the rose roll! Although expensive, it's a roll full of sashimi kept together with a thin slice of radish. It's my favourite roll!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7ieSHYr8fqzIcme-YFthLPXSXDexJ0TeTECNc&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"Keiliah Tesia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj7ZHPGOEpxFogmHZnD9unwPV05wRwHuqI4fjXoB-E3cWiIwHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the assorted tempura was good n good portion. Tea was perfect!!! Tried 2 specialty rolls 1 was the Rose Roll Salmon was delightful! 2nd was the a Mango Prawn one it was perfect as is didn‚Äôt need to add anything to either of the rolls","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbgTp8j85IULk5grzEuwAmwRygqPHOnyoSOjtq&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2023-12-21"},{"Name":"Laura Shi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxXpqCtIyt4WRYFqln4gPhOX2zyTgqBvqAuX1JH3tD-5I6bw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Be careful of black avocado in sushi rolls (it has been an ongoing issue for the past year).
Since last year, we have ordered takeout from this place a few times. Among those times, there has been incidences that the avocado was blackened in some of the sushi rolls. We mentioned it to the waitress one time and she said it wasn't rotten. We decided to give them another chance so later times when we order, we would specify that the avocado should be fresh. They did okay afterwards, but today I ordered again. When I went to pick it up, I saw a blackened avocado in one of the pieces. I nicely mentioned it to the waitress, and she said that they were too busy to care about it even though they knew that it was there. Then the boss came over and simply stated that, "If you are not happy, then you can order from other places".
The purpose of writing this review is to emphasize the importance of food safety. I'm disappointed at the way they treat their customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuDDsonLpaRHmMyr3F3hY9ycywU83BjRB1CkKY&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2022-7-29"},{"Name":"Florence Dais","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVckerGVDfARFg2H-kJQSQoEh4AvUtetEOGjAMCIHehOZTSvZo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pretty good sashimi at a reasonable price! Friendly staff and pretty quick service. Restaurant has a pleasant atmosphere although limited seating at the moment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHs78yneFh750NmqghAWPMGmkLtjUsJ1GRQckw&fid=0x0:0x9cd8223257679c34"],"When":"2022-7-27"}]

[{"Name":"Dana B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhkjBP3668gs610m4wl-_6XQOlQGLFtfdENITXTcV2cy0nemA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"All the good reviews here must be fake. It's easily the worst subway in vancouver I've eaten at. It's not very clean to start with, you get ignored for when trying to order and you're the only customer there.

I watched the girl picking up the meat that fell out of the sandwich whilst cutting, and she picked it up off the counter and pushed it back in the bun.
For some reason shen took off her gloves halfway when wrapping.

The owner of this place seems to hires indian students at wages probably half paid by trudeau, and is not even getting a fraction of the service that the customers expect when eating at that location.

The head office of subway that deals with franchises should be concerned what this location is doing to their brand.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"indramani rai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW53QJMyPYJ_nHtPLCQd8jxf3eS4e257poeG1BpjRDaxZXTA_aA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Purchased 2 footlongs. Komal made it and they very extremely delicious. I loved it. But it was taking long as there were 7 to 8 people waiting behind me. As she was the only one working at that time. Many people were waiting but the store should hire some more people. Should not exploit one person with this much of work. But anyways she was very patient and did her job very well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7BtoeW7UPf8QfvazKh0NNnvq7kcMRmqGCfB8_9wJeQ2ntCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in there with my grade 7 basketball team Nov21/22 . The employees were friendly with fast service. Not much sitting area for the 12 though.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mohammad Sedaghat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAX_Bha1X5q55jIoWh4ixbK1YzkOq3FUkGoKPjzp5klVAeh28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The guy gave half portion meat and veggies ( go to subway all the time ) it was just personal. I still paid full amount for so I think I should get a full portion. üëé","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heather Miedema","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVks27OmcA7bgu9efX1mSA7Swsl632OQI5O0645J_hM1pqyu36L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As a basic courtesy, even if you‚Äôre busy preparing an order (or your own lunch) you can greet people and let them know you‚Äôll be with them in a minute. I stood there ALONE for five minutes without being acknowledged. Someone came in after me and wasn‚Äôt acknowledged until she walked out. It‚Äôs so easy to do, and feels very awkward to be ignored.

Also, if someone says thank you say you‚Äôre welcome? You don‚Äôt need to be trained for this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nexionate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXA5cNDNfQ0pG_qVF1VyNVbL_LyzYbm7v1bIaZeoGl3cPiebEEZZg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered Footlong churros and was extremely disappointed. They completely forgot to coat it with sugar and cinnamon, it tasted completely stale. The aftertaste was terrible","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYVJcpwpqiV7uEg529mcPdNOIM4e4P4geIh-h6gGrcf8Y-uw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This Subway is quite fast, but they are usually "out" of whatever you are looking for. Even if they aren't. For example, today they didn't have the bread I wanted and told me they were out of green pepper. Attached is a picture of the green peppers they were out of.

The saving Grace for this place is that you can be in and out in a few minutes. Not the greatest care or love goes into your sandwich, but it is a Subway after all. Usually you have 3-4 staff working the lunch rush and the backwards line moved rather quickly. I wouldn't go back to this location if I could avoid it. Hygiene probably isn't the highest during peak times as they don't change gloves between handling money and your food. I didn't die so no sweat there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU7UmCFNYQpvOILkkoNHuyLpPbKgp2Vy176FL4&fid=0x0:0x58acac9515458ca3"],"When":"2018-12-19"},{"Name":"Blaine Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaxCNNIhq-K5TcDIWchkmQzn2ZnVkd4Swfmj3oSlTAwviu9O63=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Good service. But holy cow Subway!?
No roasted chicken‚Ä¶ gone‚Ä¶ after what 25 years? Menu is confusing, you go to fast food to get simple things. Even subway is also way too expensive‚Ä¶","Images":null,"When":""}]

We had a party of four and our server was spot on with her timing. The only thing that was unappealing was the shape of the carpet. But that's not enough to keep us from dining there again. Thank you Keg staff for a very pleasant evening!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"fathima afra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLrTpfTRWE1fMB7I-NL_XnYkW_8oXr3Dh4vNZGHmkDuhB66w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited the A&W restaurant and had a fantastic experience! The food was delicious, especially the classic A&W burgers and the crispy fries. The root beer was as refreshing as ever. The staff were friendly and efficient, ensuring my order was accurate and served promptly. The restaurant was clean and had a welcoming atmosphere. I appreciate the quality of both the food and service. I'll definitely be coming back for more! Highly recommend this location to anyone looking for a great meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C Shaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3koXweYeqDae9yphBnHcxOiSJktiKHx5YNVXw5slbrnKj0HMf4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I will always love their rootbeer as it evokes nostalgia. It is served without ice because they say the temperature is ice cold and the melting ice would impact the taste. I usually order the Mama burger because it is cheap or the Beyond Meat burger when I feel like saving a cow‚Äôs life. The sides are all pretty great here: the fries, sweet potato fries and onion rings are all good.

The only thing I don‚Äôt recommend is using the app. Your order is chewed up by the app and spit out differently from what you ordered. It is bizarre. I paid and was charged $51.10 in the app but the order I received was missing one of the sides, and the emailed receipt also was different from my actual order, and totalled $45.65. I had to order and pay for my missing side at the restaurant.

Later the charge to my credit card mirrored the charge on my emailed bill. The manager made it right later. A&W, please fix your app so the manager can get on with managing the restaurant and not mistakes with your app.

The food was tasty and hot. Order at the counter and check your order when it arrives.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zoltan Gyulasi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk0OXWAJ8BBGYlp_ZpOiFj3hYbCObf5vnsDCyhvE8LTMiohDA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Breakfasts are awesome. And it way busier now that everyone hates McDonald's. Also there's no crackheads ü§†","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM95hqvo9jC1PBQOWBe1Z_trA1QVBS1T8Zuq1ZZ&fid=0x0:0xb82b28e8519a62b8"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Trevor Mc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEo35TnbmyEECAgjsNtIaydhICHD804noT8dvtVQtHh7Mo1aM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has burgers. Good burgers. Better burgers than other burger places. Where‚Äôs the beef??? It‚Äôs here‚Ä¶ at A&W. Two all beef patties?? Nope. It‚Äôs one and it‚Äôs real beef. And don‚Äôt get me started on the icy cold root beer!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ben Klein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9R820F28I0t3X369CmfDuA-HVVZc86vM9sktLJOY_Gt7-9IRU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A decent a&w with the usual burgers. Subway serves an array of topping choices, allowing the customer to choose which toppings are included in their sandwich. The longtime Subway slogan, "Eat Fresh", is intended to indicate the fresh ingredients that are used in their sandwiches.

Subway is the second-biggest¬†fast food advertiser¬†in the United States, behind only McDonald's.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHxgu0H1oKTSDYBzw4NngDVB-0Y56F0ggsKAvd&fid=0x0:0x3d86d83dd9024c1f"],"When":"2022-9-12"},{"Name":"Sam Tavakoli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIC0PPQCpff9nOEKH2p2JT8Erj1N1qik_qoSwNlhMVLXQ9Srw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I really wish I had checked the reviews before placing an order with this HORRIBLE location. In the busy foodcourt in the middle of downtown, they always make a healthy, delicious and filling meal in under 5 minutes. See you next week!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Negin Rahimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4DUUoCWRf2VeIHKqwIhVGBDp6aPH06WL8KyLGIL_eC6FWBXb5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"While browsing in Pacific Center, Downtown Vancouver, I found myself feeling famished and in search of a healthy, low-calorie meal that was also incredibly delicious. After some consideration, we decided to try Edo, a Japanese cuisine restaurant. The prices were justified by the quality and portion sizes of the dishes. We ordered the shrimp and chicken teriyaki as well as the shrimp and beef teriyaki. The food was prepared quickly, and we only had to wait for about 2 or 3 minutes. Although I couldn't finish the entire meal, it was incredibly tasty and well worth it. The team at Edo did a fantastic job.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdJ6sqGzpY-bfKykKVhJcGG7rOwdjdaeERYQAx&fid=0x0:0x55eb36d67eb9de14"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Joey Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIncJBLfbVzRO24PRdfxE4-hovZn6C_s4RV_vqsGslULP8YEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Sushi is one of the foods that should be fairly consistent across restaurants, especially simple ones that I like. This place did all the right things.

The portion was quite big and the price was reasonable.

There was another place in the food court that also sold prepackaged sushi rolls, and I chose this one to try instead.

I enjoyed how clean and bright this food court was. I would come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGzYo2WcgimPru0-Wj_tKFTODskVRFDcnO8f94&fid=0x0:0x55eb36d67eb9de14"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Nacchan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb9RvKp4Kcf4Ku0M2LV4t-wyTu28-TZ8DIAR8nPq4U_IrHQNs4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I go to the Pacific City Center food court, I always order from here. My friend recommended Edo to me, and they go there almost every day. I was impressed. Edo is great and cheap! I love the Chicken Teriyaki with rice (it even has vegetables). The staff are nice too. Even though many chain stores here aren‚Äôt great for healthy options, let‚Äôs start a healthy diet together!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jenn E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYHGKr8tHHz75cKHTxSmDbo1dxTzMruC2jFQa233Os-zcL6KuE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Convenient location, love the Sushilicious combo/promo whenever I am craving affordable rolls. Cashier is nice and efficient.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_dqmC6zxX8mTA4y8fbrALwBUy3i4R5o4Qqos5&fid=0x0:0x55eb36d67eb9de14"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Neda Azouji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1OpJ5EhZSaK1WGnzAqdxZvi0cjoUlh_3CPHjtl9PuduJ1Gns3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourite Japanese restaurants in Vancouver!

[{"Name":"Iman Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY_It5dFbhJ3ahD3y8wnnvsyYECBdVwU0ipYiueTLf-0IgvGbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"[October 2024]
The service and staff are great. I always enjoy eating at Fatburger locations, and this visit was no different.

The Hawaiian burger was incredibly juicy and delicious‚Äîthe combination of pineapple, bacon, and the burger was so unique and enjoyable as a new experience. üçç ü•ì üçî

The mushroom burger was a classic, still juicy, and perfect if you prefer something without the sweetness of the Hawaiian burger. It's absolutely amazing. üçÑ üçî

My favorite part was the fried pickles‚Äîcrispy, a bit spicy, and so unique to Fatburger. I love them. ü•í ü•í

As always, it was a 5/5 experience. The store itself was classy and cozy, just like a true burger place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_Mjoy36gJ7OdDde04AL38tOhkIz5pze_hvWXu&fid=0x0:0x9c90436389022f45"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Jeff Bridges __","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtVlLKTd4RyKHbiBdT3FiG002D7yHnionCIXHvFpH38aYHdoKh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"personally, the prices are very high. You‚Äôre looking at spending up to $20 per person if you‚Äôre looking for making it a combo. The place itself was cool for a hot day and the view was nice for people watching, though people tend to watch you.

My service was fast and the people working there were nice and quick, letting me know about some things. I got the 4 taster chickens combo for $18.54 I believe, though it was pricey they gave me 2 extra tenders! Guess everywhere I go and order tenders I seem to get a little extra haha.

The food itself was fresh and the chicken was good, seasoned well and juicy. The fries are good but could be a little more salty but overall very delicious.

I recommend this place if you‚Äôre looking for some good fresh and fast food, for reasonable prices if it‚Äôs made up to date. Thank you, fat burger.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvEXVO58hbb7ccUuh5zBJOvCoWy93EuF7FZpG1&fid=0x0:0x9c90436389022f45"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Ponda Baba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB1Z_E00v52246I1gIoMBkczOxjQZj6Oq_4BUoL4Tw6wid095m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fatburger is delicious. I like this location. Juicy burger patty, crispy produce, great fries, even better onion rings. Friendly service at the till. Can't go wrong here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8V5dWhcLGVylhR2AbDyMJxUbvYP_5wWsWfABQ&fid=0x0:0x9c90436389022f45"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"R M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRwrQUk19VQ3LSJNCLFMT4Q-JbDk5KjEckQ8aqMEIy_jrG0CR5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff here have always been amazing. They truly go above and beyond with portions, packaging, and overall service. I find this to be true with both in-person dining as well as food delivery. Big hearts here and a genuine desire to look after their patrons. Always refreshing to see and I‚Äôm so thankful for all my positive experiences at this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"behgol Moazzami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8_0NfhvipMeg_pDiZrJWZpaHM8mQCtO4CdI96GlYL21pfppfE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The burger teast so good and fresh we went there for lunch and we really liked it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtR1Hb1qjVRyC60Ht9ahLRDbroqwx4rNQY2W2E&fid=0x0:0x9c90436389022f45"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Amy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjXHHF3vPFKXXTvrLI9L9GLLX-x9A-g0rYHpm8C9R04tRthXY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like what some reviewer had said, the beef patty has no bad smell or left any strong after taste. That is already a big difference from many other fast food outlets. I like how they freshly cooked everything including the fries to the order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIkf8zToR1dvZpXuIv5ArSDtEiRy2KrIEr93tD&fid=0x0:0x9c90436389022f45"],"When":"2022-5-6"},{"Name":"Nick B (Ajey S)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKM0twCInKU2mX7uJPxJLPFZNqcV5qNSYZKQxMIVPr1dWGecg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a take out regular large burger. The burger was juicy with good amount of cheese, pickle and lettuce. I ate it after an hour or so and was better than a $25 dine in burgers at other places.
Keep up the good work and I will return soon","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deana Horsman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuUrcswdBCfwz6kEO-c3X2riKFaTzKMq2JGGtqt1l4_o-VICqB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food is very terrible I thought it was good the first time I went there I got a burger and it was really good the second time I got food poisoning and they didn't really care the third time which was many years later our meal was awful the meat tasted like it had gristle in it it was a really awful meal and when I went to get the milkshake it was so thin I asked her to thicken it up and realized that they're only using vanilla ice cream and chocolate syrup it is disgusting and it is over $8 for it. When I asked to return it because of the price the whole staff in the store got really quiet and normally they yell whenever they get a tip or an order but I think a lot of people might be saying that stuff to them because it's a very expensive store it's become very greedy. Anyways I live in Olympic village and I love burgers and I will not go here.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Nia Ngola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9r2qJS75LmqGmzZlhJFLNRCFYD1-m0DV2vbJxXMmdR4e8_2FW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I was craving chinese today. Came in around half past three. It was dead, only one person ahead of me. They are really stingy with the food they serve and imagine getting only one packet of soy sauce‚Ä¶ crazy!

I got noodles and one side (chicken), no drink. The amount of chicken she initially added to the container wasn‚Äôt a lot, maybe around 5 or 6 pieces. I asked for a bit more and she told me it‚Äôs an additional $2. That‚Äôs fine ‚Äî but tell me why this meal was $16.68. For the amount of noodles I got? Unbelievable.

If I hadn‚Äôt asked for more chicken, it would‚Äôve been $14. That‚Äôs actually insane. Prices are unpredictable here. I‚Äôve noticed they rarely ever have a set price or portion size. They give you what they please. Panda Express fills it up to the brim. There is no way this was worth just under $17. They make up their prices. I was definitely ripped off. It wasn‚Äôt even hot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTt6uy_HHvIBpPlCuSnvMFqLt8o0lp2GzvzEz4&fid=0x0:0xe6ce862158b4fb1c"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW-DEvjr4ZK3xOsFIox8U1OL4J0JrzS9bTD5mRoPl4u2wXBqjc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was the WORST food I‚Äôve had in Vancouver.
I absolutely do not recommend this place.

The chicken was cold, hard, and soggy,
the rice was greasy and undercooked,
and the vegetables were wet and mushy.
It‚Äôs clear that there‚Äôs no proper food management here.

The staff‚Äôs attitude was also terrible.
I placed my order with a female employee with a ponytail, and she put a donut on my tray I didn‚Äôt order. She was so rude and yelled at me, asking how many donuts I want.

I‚Äôm shocked that a place like this is allowed to operate in a mall.

I usually don‚Äôt leave negative reviews ‚Äî if I don‚Äôt like a place, I just don‚Äôt go back.
That‚Äôs how bad this place was, and it made me so upset and ruined my dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpWh4B_oh0be84LczjJtBQQ_ZwBrmbOD9x4YPR&fid=0x0:0xe6ce862158b4fb1c"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Gurpreet B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBzI9wUbQjHyVnOUlJ3oOlyBOEz0cVGI04XTrmca4uD78Br-GM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could give no stars I would. Was there for the discounted food close to 6pm. The servers don‚Äôt listen they all started serving one customer all at the same time confusing everyone, they did not communicate well and on top of that they did not charge the discounted price. To be honest it seems like they were putting food in the containers for themselves.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J wico","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFLTpvMyLxVfHKit3ZJqPccY65Bl-YeNGA1wEu8pZSIRWpww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Sorry West Georgia Location, there is nothing for the New Westminster one so I'm writing it here. Didn't think I'd ever say it for fast food chinese food, but their food could probably use more salt?

Pro:
- I love overcooked mixed vegetables. They're flavourful.
- Decent sized portions
- Royal City Centre has character. Good people watching.
- If you're really desperate for Chinese food and you don't want to wait, it's here....
- Good if you live life on the edge and want to flirt with the line between food poisoning and satisfactory meal.

Cons:
- Price: just under $16. It's more expensive than Manchu Wok and Bourbon Grill, which are probably their main competitors.
- Service: the lady working the front was wearing an airpod and couldn't hear what I was saying. Take those damn things off. You're working...She may have been an owner, so I guess who cares for her.
- Their rice and noodles all look overcooked. Like they've been sitting in water for hours. I went with the least mushy option.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH7bkcbIDa_EnQrO4v4tOdc_l90KFZVWkFlZCv&fid=0x0:0xe6ce862158b4fb1c"],"When":"2023-8-26"},{"Name":"SA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJY6gvIa6u4BiPzyqC-IKc3Zyl1c4pwMCJp_-F6RMSJYO6IjyV8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Extremely rude worker. I did not leave a tip. I said order combo A and the lady added something on my food that has an extra charge. I told her I dont want it- and she just threw my plate on the counter and walked away. The young lady with long hair should not work in food service. Nothing special with the food. Would not support this business again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Homayoun khoshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRU6QEuoqmadpSC7fPysBUvHsQFaI5wRgp62on5vxHTkWW5Us=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst food court restaurant. They are lucky there is no other place like them or they would run out of business
Ordered noodle, chicken and beef and eggplant.
The noodles we all cut to pieces and couldn‚Äôt be eaten had to use a spoon.
