We had the salmon burger and vegan burger. Both were delicious - the salmon in particular. A low key local vibe. When we visited there were young kids, students, and old timers like us all enjoying the food. Good amount of seating outdoors and inside.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJawI80c4qwvuA-pWmht_nhIypwFKNS8vUDHnZIepoqs0gJvft7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I really wanted to like this place but unfortunately we didn't. Affordable prices but the food just let us down. I'm fine with basic but found the DICED burger lacking and the nachos were ruined by the corn chips. The fries, which were pretty good, and the biscuit were the only items I liked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2IuCEopmqKeJmI6RJiYC1Jx0nJYLnmSgbhl5z&fid=0x0:0x8724e7521984580"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbling upon this establishment was like uncovering Vancouver's best-kept secret. Critics of its operations might miss the bigger picture: this place is not just a restaurant but a cornerstone of the DICED Culinary School, which champions affordable and sponsored culinary training programs. With very reasonable prices, especially for its locale, the ever-changing menu keeps the dining experience fresh and exciting. The patio and the events hosted there add another layer of charm. More than just a meal, dining here supports a noble cause, making it all the more worthwhile to explore and endorse.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNY6bN7P2eB7zct_4A0kOI6o7FgWoR-H3d3oeSf&fid=0x0:0x8724e7521984580"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Adam Myhre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlloGTdin2BEFn5bg_e4KC9zJLJE3T-tVTT7t76H3j3mWQRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"DICED Discovery Cafe, tucked away near Jericho Beach, surpasses its seaside competitors remarkably. This establishment prides itself on prompt service and observant staff, showcasing an unwavering dedication to guest contentment. In fact, there were staff hovering near the entrance the entire time looking for tables to clear or anyone needing anything.  As a dog lover, the inclusive pet-friendly policy significantly enhanced our dining experience, contributing to the overall laid-back vibe of the place.

The outdoor seating area presented a slight hiccup, as only half the tables benefit from the shade, either natural or via umbrellas. However, after a short wait, we managed to nab a shaded spot for our meal.

A point worth noting is the slightly elusive location of the restrooms, hidden within the upstairs hostel. This required a minor search, but the overall experience outweighed this minor inconvenience.

The charm of DICED lies within its simple but well done menu. The irresistible Cuddle burger has managed to capture the hearts of many, including mine. The unbeatable combination of delectable flavor and affordable pricing make it a standout choice!

A crucial aspect not to be forgotten is the cafe's commendable work within the community. Functioning as a social enterprise, DICED invests in shaping the future of young adults in the culinary field. Every delicious meal served is a testament to their commitment towards empowerment and opportunity.

To top it off, we found free street parking just one block away, saving us the usual parking hassle. DICED Discovery Cafe is a great combination of delicious, wallet-friendly food, comfortable ambience, and admirable community engagement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSPfi0AwhrYBYvn8ORU8C3XN4mxY8m-1H40jSJ&fid=0x0:0x8724e7521984580"],"When":"2023-7-26"},{"Name":"Joshua Brodie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFib9zhnbuMwdZJxwP44egP7q34gwvfJ-Pyd_QVmgeuHQq0g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place and the concept. Unfortunately 2024 wasn‚Äôt as kind to Dice as 3023. Perhaps losing the liquor license for the patio?

However still a great place. And just wonderful people. Great prices.  What more could I want?","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Hassan Parsa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqI-yi5_g6jVvS56xjNyNhK2CpMhS24UMuxol4BdmDgUj7SkeS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I just went in on a random check for Indian food. I liked their food, the ambience and the service! The chef make an excellent job with the Naan! The lamb curry was also good. The only thing was the price of the Naan which was around $6 which I presume is a little too expensive for a Naan. I should admit it was garlic Naan and tasted really well! My overall say on that one experience is I liked it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHqQw9DT5wHsAfTuT9js_Bhcqb--Dvuz9hRL-4&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Rox Ortega","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkUL9-cUrc1IAVugY6nVrUBRia3eXMBadJsQlS4avQYHladfx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The oiliest "chicken" tikka masala. I'm not even sure that meat is chicken. It has the texture of pork but kinda tastes like fish. Literally the curry is drowning in oil. I couldn't even eat it, it's disgusting. I'm so pissed off that I spent $30+ on this thing I can't even eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyesUrRyMqQioSlPDycrqtiC30M2U3vho9p85A&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Peter Cross","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHmBXMXmX9-43PxxMc-vQWx8OaX3r8ByLsfhp1pyyCEQpdxmTkCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came tonight to celebrate a birthday. Group of six afforded us plenty to choose from with a variety of dishes for the table.  Service was great.  The room is nice with pleasant music.  The lamb is a bit tough as others have said. The rest of the meal was wonderful and we had a great time.  The dumplings were very tasty and the chicken tandoori was a bit bony and had little meat on the piece I got.  Sadly the waitress was very slow to clear our table after food and drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6TcXMa-VONcmC7arUP3EfLZ8vrqf0_4wHOqOj&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2023-5-21"},{"Name":"Johncy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNCcOOb16x--mvyjqmOGS_ekMiT8INhLzftV30QGSCPlNpdwog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good food and really good customer service; if you like spicy food, I would recommend you to tell them to make it spicy. I got channa masala and fish pokora, and it was really good. Also ordered for takeout for my friends and I got chicken & lamb biryani. My friends both liked the two biryani. Overall, I would rate this place a 4.5 out of 5.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvC2Q6n4xLACw457mAdsLrzye_N3KU3CkLTCfL&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2024-3-19"},{"Name":"Aradhana Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGF8FufGWhI_LiUSm1UrLVnUnsBxHi0EfHfM_Ofg_MXDH00w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I first looked at the restaurant online, I thought that people wrote fake reviews about it, but I was wrong!
The food was amazing and traditional, it reminded me of my mom‚Äôs food.
This is the perfect restaurant if you‚Äôre looking for vegetarian options.
The staff is really friendly and caring when it comes to the service.
We had the chance to personally thank the chefs and take a picture with them!
They allowed me and my group to play songs of our choice and also let us dance after dinner which was fabulous!

I‚Äôd definitely come back again and I highly recommend it to people that love Indian and spicy food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2exvTf2NYpDGKTU3HbA6Fwt4hpAqJJOSyV22r&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2023-7-15"},{"Name":"Sandra R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi4xFFLZJN-zPiYf-Lw1A86uAbB0_czMuoffJLUFjjC4hQyww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! Really great food, excellent value (huge take out servings), friendly service  and the atmosphere is cozy and warm in winter, open patio in summer. I love their gluten free offerings. One of our new favorites.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Holly Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8JUvONVzomd94Off1-k_EXXhwoErw-2ELquSGN4FCIVH78w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok... So lunch special is really a great price. <$15 for a complete combo. But, I didnt expect the portion to be that huge too.... It comes with 3 large pieces of naan. üò≥
All of their menu that we ordered were extremely tasty and large-portioned. Three of us ordered 3 main items (Paneer Muttar, Bombay butter chicken lunch special and bombay wrap lunch special.) We couldn't even touch the wrap and we were still too full. I really wanted to try their desserts too, I'm kinda sad by this..üò≠
Great service. I would definitely come back to this. Would've loved to try buddha bowl too, but they were out of Avocado at that time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM27jZ9359i688UVYwPYVaHaCvCX-HNldpOpkpN&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2022-3-30"},{"Name":"Daniel Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJawI80c4qwvuA-pWmht_nhIypwFKNS8vUDHnZIepoqs0gJvft7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyable Indian food if you're in the area. I appreciated the complimentary pappadam. They did a great job keeping the chicken moist in all our dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOec3R-wNLnUiI9yqV5PXbv4iU0Zv3zhvU70W37&fid=0x0:0x607c8163c4f26789"],"When":"2023-6-18"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jianding Bai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkwYHdLto-RxOlIAu_Ufsf991NZ4zcisCvY8HoRmEfBdR5NgW9tQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"When I walked into the restaurant, there were no servers, just a cook in the kitchen and a man busy on his laptop in the back. I didn't mind waiting as I wasn't in a hurry.

After I waited for about five minutes, the man helped with a pickup order, and then I realized that he was the one who should take my order. The service was not bad, but only when his attention was not on his laptop.

If that was only what happened, I wouldn‚Äôt be writing this review.

The same man was also helping with food preparing and packing. I witnessed him handling raw sprouts with his bare hands after touching his laptop, his face, and even handling cash. And he did it so naturally. ü•∫

I felt sorry for whoever would receive the dish that was prepared in this manner, and felt slightly desperate when it was brought to me. Despite my love for sprouts in pho, I didn‚Äôt touch them. The water cup was not very clean either. The pho itself was good in terms of portion and taste, and it was reasonably priced.

However, due to the overall experience, I wouldn't come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMN9kBf6lqqQHJ78Ko6hmaSiTLh8YKLccJCuo5D&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Josephine Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8UejeGdlCBXmq9iCj4KAfMFg31koNGe0fK1qhNtiuUpMoa3TL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw that many people recommended their lemongrass chicken rice, so I got it. The chicken was tender, juicy and flavorful, and it is already delicious without the fish sauce. The rice was also fluffy.
Good price for the food. Will definitely go again to try their pho.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyogRJQFVmVkoXf4ebFCKUBEhwYSrdlCyqRBIm&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2023-2-25"},{"Name":"Lillian McCallum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYAIDuDrgcv_SZk0pYq_mYhMkeYfUO_V1tNS0DitQjLAl3sqnzCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very well priced & yummy. Service wasn‚Äôt too great as the many uber/delivery orders were prioritized over the customers.

They only take cash or debit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNE--rz6L6OpOGm5SmWdo8P69IaZc7xzUkBrBvS&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2024-1-10"},{"Name":"Dee Dee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAdTA3NYeXm3u7zQoXQvtRlRCvWWXo4Ce0ebUZxo9GSSoYeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered take out and there was barely any meat on the dish which was $20.  Also the meat had no flavour.  Looked good when I first opened the container but was not good at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2_JPDEYhfu0dAXmUPnklLVLLtFoIj5oXovA4M&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2024-3-4"},{"Name":"MaVic CS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtTAd352JLEqWeP1XHORjOjSo_BcIs5WMf5gdMaF58KUDsJxvB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My all time favorite, only in Gold Train Thai Restaurant in West 10th Ave.. try thier chicken and pork lemongrass.. super delicious..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDv2nwKMog1bLeHoAtmz6tYSpav3RlkN6HotbN&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2023-10-27"},{"Name":"Tina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAKiC5J1ql1LsLTTfBwgvAj6sVGUusHXghumDKVG9ZTQ8QjcD_1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A no frills pho place with reasonable price. Large bowl was around $13. Too much noodles and not enough topping. But the soup was decent. Way better than the on-campus UBC pho place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhy3ipdhvBPEYboiNqi80iWczZB5h6dhQ7ALCz&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Dilana A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKn8AO31cnUh1tnJX9fpDWS1XBSTe9u1OYcAQVEqcCtBTmmwTC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pho and rolls were amazing. Great service. Too bad you can't pay with credit, but that‚Äôs alright.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN58zFiybH1Y0zmtmAW7QBRl9pMwuRkSTDKOSnR&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Madhumanti Mandal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGGhf5GWQXlVJl15HuKBDzE48CxrS0TRRAts1AZluTGEQOC9v5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A very good Vietnamese place, lots of space and quite cheap. I have been there multiple times, very close to UBC.. My favorite dish here is the lemongrass chicken with rice, which costs only $12, it keeps me full all day from lunch... Family run restaurant, the hosts are very nice and kind, they have fast service even in busy hours. They also have take out menus. Will go there again multiple times","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdOYJ9QJOSnR5GCdtXs7KWFaYOX8110yIVdWey&fid=0x0:0x80b78e6f6b1c3a4c"],"When":"2019-8-30"}]

[{"Name":"Cc Ww","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJP0q9EHP94EL2cwLaPuRzE2AdbyVVCVuiEsNIB2kBAGc4ZZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was AMAZING! We started with the trio de mezze appetizer and it was such a treat. The bread it came with was a great texture and even had a little hint of spice. Definitely the biggest surprise of the night. The lamb shank was tender and came with a ton of delicious sides. we also really enjoyed the seafood skillet. The atmosphere was so lovely here and I will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiJHdLuTbprlD8c6BxSDXT1aGnAK05UBhTekN0&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Hessam Dehqani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9_xTs6k7X3RgR-GYtpDaVcRhHZYvAkCWBCnak0FYwr9rofA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was a symphony of delight and pleasure dancing on my taste buds. Extravagant amounts of seafood in the seafood fettuccine. Sauce was perfect. The Chocolate Lava Cake was the perfect amount of fluffiness and chewy-ness all at once. The cake was the slightest bit warm and the giant scoop of ice cream served on the side was not too cold, making it the perfect combo. The friendly staff will make you feel at home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJ5stowouGaXpUeYE6xdnYk5tTw2UAhlZkDP0B&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Sarah H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW92qwsfx_pIiwt2DlNeJL21vsXcUQcWFFO0CrTDqGo7aSuEtvR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved this Greek spot in Kits! We chose to share a range of appetizers- all were delicious, including the four olives with focaccia, the mezzo trio with the best pita, calamari, and spanakopita. We also had the yam fries- so perfectly hot and crispy. Everything came out quite quickly and fresh. The service was friendly and delicious. Definitely recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOboR7reOpDZb_p0TsC_cSRvUDH0o3Bk4IppOyh&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Lister Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWbNvO55wOzkDRxCcJ-fMoCcdWyut5hlx-H_zUreRnwso9_V0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed lunch special with beet argula salad, lamb souvlaki, and ice cream. Everything made carefully and plated beautifully. Yummy salad and tender flavourful lamb. Lovely server and ample seating","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvil2aWBw9xvb1WEocpbSTu5qJKwNogPEJmVBG&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Isaac Trenton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcuG3EvRc-AAeKCn9g2ZfMQnNodo8xx3TwArbSevKXywtb2BIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A wonderful experience with family. Would recommend for both friendly outings and special occasions. Great food, personal service, clean ambiance. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMO--eXeeKqPcjAD_zKFBygtnPBJ296t7XWlMGx&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"andy a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7Y7rwHyjfulEA1YHdfgv-xt7-eGezTRedst5phEBEmPsbXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience, tried the four olives with the deep fried olives. If you enjoy olives I highly recommend them, you won't be disappointed.

The lamb shoulder was fork tender, and the Navajo bread was crispy fluffy and soft all at once.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPL8yvDzQrWpheoXTb2m_LsnPGF3AcaCpmykrT&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Yourstruly T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdAW_3mT95dnmWSH1jV5DzTjAp8VnRyKu5igqgCkvt_l-2XR77=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at this delightful Mediterranean gem, and the experience was nothing short of extraordinary. The ambiance exuded jazzy vibes, creating a perfect backdrop for a cozy and homely atmosphere.

The moment I stepped in, the inviting warmth enveloped me, making it feel like I was enjoying a meal in the comfort of someone elses' home. The restaurant's decor and lighting contributed to the overall cozy vibes, setting the stage for a memorable dining experience.

The main course portions were generously sized. Each bite was a burst of deliciousness. Appies were so flavourful. For the dine-out menu, I really liked the Mushroom Arancini and the Garlic Prawns. Ugh!! So warm/flavourful..

A special shoutout to the owner or manager, Amar, whose friendly and attentive demeanor added a personal touch to the entire evening. His passion for the cuisine and commitment to customer satisfaction were evident in every aspect of the dining experience.

The potatoes, a standout side dish, were a delightful surprise with their sourly delicious taste. I couldn't get enough of them. The chicken skewers were another highlight ‚Äì juicy, flavorful, and a true testament to the culinary expertise of the kitchen.

In conclusion, this Mediterranean restaurant is a must-visit for anyone seeking a jazzy, cozy, and homey dining experience. With mouthwatering dishes and a warm welcome from Amar, it's a culinary haven that I can't wait to revisit during patio season as well!!

xoxo,
@yourstrulyfoodie","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8hxYl3J7Guv437YZS_Uj8FCdYhvd9RqmOTMS1&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-1-16"},{"Name":"Daniel Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJawI80c4qwvuA-pWmht_nhIypwFKNS8vUDHnZIepoqs0gJvft7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I enjoyed everything we ordered. Portions were decent but not overly so. Definitely worth trying if you like Mediterranean food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODYFoK7X1vlNRzms1wWtQdlB7xQK729D7csvia&fid=0x0:0xdb1692f513539870"],"When":"2024-1-3"}]

The tofu had no sauce, no seasoning, and was completely dry. The rest of the bowl was mediocre at best. I've had good experiences at this location in person but this was really unappetizing and disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbRvzrKUDTlb38Dj0j0nkT3Tj7VQqAV7cEFG7r&fid=0x0:0x184dff507d14466e"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Al May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURsEKydI6yFDWfeEuJUm_zojUlbRJUnS2y7j3NZKmrARii_3iYLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have been to another Brown's location last year. It was my first time at a Brown's Social House too. I was unimpressed by the food at that location. It was bland, so I wasn't expecting much here. I thought I'd get just some drinks and appies to pass the time.
I was pleasantly surprised. The food here was actually pretty tasty. The crispy cauliflower came hot, fresh and flavourful. The fish and chips were tasty too, and the fish tasted fresh. The Smokehouse BBQ Burger was massive and juicy. The yam fries were perfect. The calamari was ok.
We loved the food.
Service was friendly. I wish it was a bit more attentive, though in fairness, it was a busy Friday night.

I'll definitely go to this location again if I'm ever in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhjo4mOyjivdC-bwwDWaPsJVx7rRhwHuICm3wO&fid=0x0:0x184dff507d14466e"],"When":"2023-3-12"},{"Name":"Leon Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPOnBvlGz2k_WzxOhCiURR3aRaAE5ffHXfUBJJ4GP7GBC5Wn8K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A solid Brown's with the classic menu selection. The menu options are bit limited, and the space inside is a bit squished, but the food is pretty good! The cocktails are quite nice too, and the atmosphere is what you would expect out of a bar-restaurant. I highly recommend their pastas :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkRhxX67sOh4p3XXoU-SbVEBbk0QOkVZoJWA43&fid=0x0:0x184dff507d14466e"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Turtlekeeper Designs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZmq2g731Yc8XnFSpBiniWaYnYNraL7GVOPNZyVCF5ChC8dro=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Impromptu dinner on a Thursday night. [{"Name":"Lisa Stewart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo79veLnsCvDCjha0TJoTathwJUFPajJepLVXdR9rXYCLOAi7D6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A varied menu of pure comfort foods!  Fish and chips, burgers and chicken tenders!  Burritos, wraps and salads!  My family of 4 tasted the chicken tenders and fries‚Ä¶delicious!  The burger and fries‚Ä¶also delicious.  And the falafel salad and the beef taco salad‚Ä¶both amazing!  The portions are big in my opinion! You get a lot of delicious fresh food for your money!  The staff are all so friendly and welcoming.  A few high top tables to sit at and one regular height table‚Ä¶all of them for 2 persons each!  It was really busy when we arrived, lots of people doing to go orders!  We enjoyed our meals‚Ä¶will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8mKZJQfIv2XVIcQz6u1vyhYNXkzSqeR09JLeV&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Nico Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzzG-P48bnnJBGquw-nbxNyOks1aLbPCnGOP7hraCNfYMEHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came across this restaurant the other day craving for crispy food, and I got to order their fish and chips. Literally, it‚Äôs the best fish and chips I have ever had.

The fish was fresh & the spices were so unique and go perfectly with the fish fillets. The fries were also flavoured with some unique spices - but not too salty.

The staff who served me were friendly and made sure the food was served when it‚Äôs right out of the stove.

I‚Äôm also appreciate that there are lots of free 2-hour parking spots in front of the store. Anyways, super happy about my visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaUCJFxd8jexMyDXMnWb_CoZ4vGv19y6g0IDuX&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Jenny Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWl8oo2mXw8xJvl6jSBW5DQKc9rDBoAZRoKyCjTBErOGVWosCxm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best burrito in my life - if you‚Äôre visiting, I highly highly highly highly recommend beef burrito. The spices are so unique and so good with the wrap perfectly grilled. I am ordering it at least once per week.

The staff were super friendly as well :) always having a great experience here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyF_lrfAj6CUWyhRsuANyx2OzwtS2Y7lR8b3Wq&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Khaled Saif","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXT9kwxHTC0uHGB4Gpgsy3rp29zqxoXLVvJksOs8Ce9O4_Hq8M0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food was pretty okay-ish. Nothing too fancy. I had the fish and chips. tbh the fries in compared to fish was too high in portion & the fries were a bit soggy to start with. I couldn‚Äôt finish it. On the other hand, the fish was cooked really well and it was very fresh.

The service wasn‚Äôt good at all. The staffs were mostly busy with online orders and the dine-in rush made them start to forget orders. They forgot to give my wife‚Äôs chilli cheese fries. Also the girl (asian girl with black hair) who took my order was extremely rude.

The menu in display is really confusing, the design itself is very hard to get.

I really hope the management sees my review and takes immediate action with their staffs. This restaurant has potential, but with poor customer service and food quality, it will shut down like other restaurants in Vancouver. :(","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmsAdc46fnES4MqXV-wQgYQ6zRNUsNiPjOGiH7&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Chef Hyve is a small little shop located on Kingsway that I've been meaning to try for a while. You order at the end of the counter and they have a few high top tables that you can sit at.

We ordered the chili cheese fries ($13.95) and the fish sandwich ($14.50) along with a tropical iced tea ($3.50). The fish sandwich has coleslaw and served on a cheese bun. The fried fish is flaky. I think I want to come back and retry just the fish by itself to really get a sense of it.

The fries are freshly fried and topped with a thicc and chunky chili. It's mostly meat and i kind of almost missed having more chili sauce to it. But the fries were also topped with a creamy sauce. Either way, this was a good meaty and cheesy fries dish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM20mZUjNAuo7X98dbKIV5aIHva1yOIYkXPqRN2&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Jason LeClair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpjmq51lZwEG86qhJ3vqiVZDKy6DmhPgN6Y280blqslTGbTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little place that makes quality real food. I will definitely recommend to friends. I had the burger and fries. Fantastic! They grill the patties fresh in front of you. It was fairly good

1. Fries was nicely seasoned
2. Cook through nicely
3. NO crispiness at all (wilted)
4. Food temperature was secured
5. Tar tar sauce and paprika powder was excellent

I would expect more with 10 dollars fries:
More of the crispiness on the outside while still being moist on the inside.
Everything is wonderful.

You made it. 10/10
I will leave the review here for reference. Come back for fish and chips. Well done!
Thank you for the food and sorry for ordering late.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPncETAYL6nKnkj6BBdjqKISTZenmG1sHy8YgAJ&fid=0x0:0xf871529c14fc71f7"],"When":"2024-3-26"}]

[{"Name":"Matt E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZQfEG_xmBLRy05xS6KbedGsdkDNhef508QuEhW06OHHHM7HPG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Popeyes Chicken offers bold, flavorful fried chicken with a perfect crispy coating and juicy inside. The spicy option is a highlight, pairing well with classic sides like biscuits and Cajun fries. However, the customer service at the Stafford location falls short, with unfriendly staff affecting the overall experience. A great meal, but service improvements are needed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9DQPLrOm8Cp2Q8ZWkNUermORNFsnWwJuYLeRy&fid=0x0:0x9f18b936a818f3e"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"sharuq mt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFqmaROv7E7S4L9EYco4i2wwB43BmVXDpMA-rKiMDKktSI_7qJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant, and I have to say, it was one of the worst takeaway experiences I've ever had. From the moment I walked in, I was met with staff who were not only unwelcoming but downright rude. There was no smile, no greeting‚Äîjust cold, uninterested behavior. Communication was terribly poor, and it felt like they couldn't care less about making the experience enjoyable.
